(10, 7, 'Let\'s Enter into The World of Beauty with Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy', 'let-s-enter-into-the-world-of-beauty-with-certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy', 3, 'The beauty industry has become a global industry that is progressing rapidly. The use of cosmetics nowadays has rather become an obligation to look presentable for a good impression on people.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">The beauty industry has become a global industry that is progressing rapidly. The use of cosmetics nowadays has rather become an obligation to look presentable for a good impression on people. Moreover, maintaining a proper, clean, and tidy lifestyle is a key element for sound health, mind, and body. It has also become an essential part of our daily life to take care of our skin. As good skin reflects our personality and our hygiene.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Humans have been grooming themselves in one form or another since they first arrived on the planet. The concept behind beauty therapy has links with the earliest civilizations. Although there have been alterations in styles and fashions, Cosmetic treatments continued to be prominent throughout history.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Enter The World of Beauty with Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy.jpg\" alt=\"Enter The World of Beauty with Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">What is Beauty Therapy?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Beauty therapy is generally known as the application of beauty treatments. Like any great career, beauty therapy starts with a robust educational foundation. It has been in practice for ages. With time and technical availabilities, beauty therapy has been modernized.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">In the context of Australia, the beauty industry is ahead of time. One of the RTO which avails <a href=\"../../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy</a> is Noble Training Academy (NTA). It is a privately operated Registered Training Organisation providing courses within Australia. It offers a range of nationally recognized qualifications from Certificate III to Diploma level in the beauty industry.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Beauty therapy training at Noble Training Academy (NTA) is developed to ensure that the graduates learn skills that are relevant to the needs of employers and clients in the beauty industry.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">All about Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy Course</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">The Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy course is nationally recognized training that maps the information related to Beauty Therapy and the essentials.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">In this course, students can learn from our team of professionals how to provide a range of beauty services including waxing, manicure, and pedicure, lash and brow treatments, spray tanning, and make-up.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">This course includes training in demonstrating and selling retail skincare and cosmetic products. The students can also learn about safe hygiene and work practices and environmental sustainability.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/All about Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy course.jpg\" alt=\"All about Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy course\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">It enables the students to learn through a combination of classroom and hands-on practical exercises, plus completing a practical placement in a salon of their choice. They can graduate with the technical and customer service skills needed to work as a competent beauty therapist.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">People who undertake this course, work independently, with limited guidance from seniors or mentors, to perform routine and non-routine activities, and solve non-routine problems. They put in and accommodate technical skills and knowledge, and use judgment within the provision of beauty treatments and services. These individuals are liable for their own outputs and supply limited guidance to others.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">People who possess the following attributes like reliability, are friendly and caring with a positive attitude and self-motivation also having no allergies to beauty products, well-presented with good communication skills, excellent time, and stress management skills are the best fit for this industry.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">This course comprises 19 units that must be completed in order to get the certification. Out of which, 13 are core units and, 6 are elective units.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'The beauty industry has become a global industry that is progressing rapidly. The use of cosmetics nowadays has rather become an obligation to look presentable for a good impression on people.', 'lets-enter-into-the-world-of-beauty-with-certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy.png', NULL, '2020-11-18 02:12:58', '2022-01-16 04:44:57'),
(13, 7, 'What is The Importance of Study Diploma of Remedial Massage Course in Australia?', 'what-is-the-importance-of-study-diploma-of-remedial-massage-course-in-australia', 4, 'Don’t we all need relaxation at least once a week to completely free ourselves from daily activities and stress which in turn affects the physical as well as mental wellbeing? Certainly, we do.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From the ancient time of Egypt, one of the famous physicians first invented the remedial massage practice back in 2330 BC. For getting a quick recovery of the soldiers, this technique was a popular one. In the middle of the 19th century, it was first introduced in the USA and UK. Over time, Australia also started to use this treatment technique in the early 1900s, and now it has become one of the registered professions for the Australian job market.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To get relief from muscle pain, remedial massage has a vital role to play in health sectors. Many people adopt this therapy at least once a week to turn off their stress and muscle pain instantly. Along with years of experience, massage therapists contribute to this therapy to provide the best outcomes with ultimate relaxation for their clients. But no one is counted as a <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">professional remedial massage therapist</a> unless they get a proper qualification and license in the therapist industry. Therefore, to bring a proper career line-up, studying a diploma of remedial massage course is one of the best ways to shape your career in the massage sector.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-olia-danilevich-9335993.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"727\" height=\"1091\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose you want to grow your interest or already have skills in body massage. Then, you can take one step further to develop your quality with the advanced diploma of remedial massage course in Australia. Now, you might wonder what are the benefits and why is it essential to study diploma in remedial massage? To clear your confusion, let\'s make some brief discussion about the importance of studying a diploma of remedial massage course in 2022.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is The Diploma of Remedial Massage? </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is an advanced course of massage therapy. This course teaches practical skills in remedial massage, including massage, stretching, and various associated techniques to <a href=\"../../blogs/importance-of-soft-tissue-remedial-massage-in-real-life\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">improve soft tissue dysfunction</a>. In addition, one will get to learn the theoretical knowledge required to provide treatment according to the client\'s demand. To get practical skills and alter the impartation of remedial massage knowledge, the diploma of remedial massage (HLT52015) is one of the best choices under a budget price for the prior learners. As a professional, you need to understand and utilize the massage technique as a form of applied remedy for human musculoskeletal ailments. To obtain this professional qualification, you have to be eligible as an experienced one in the massage industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Importance of Diploma of Remedial Massage Course </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From an Australian perspective, Remedial Therapy is considered a highly qualified certification for anyone involved in this field. However, few institutions provide registered remedial massage therapy courses, especially the Diploma of Remedial Massage Therapy for the experience one. The nationally accredited Diploma of Remedial Massage will take your career one step further. It will give you the essential practical skills and knowledge that you need to work as a remedial massage therapist. When you graduate with a Diploma of Remedial Massage, you will align your personal values with your career by helping people to live well and feel great. Now counting the part, let\'s talk about all the importance you may get from studying a diploma of remedial massage course.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Learn New Skills </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Through a mix of theory and practical coursework, learn to:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Provide, monitor, and evaluate remedial massage treatments.</li>\r\n<li>Adapt various remedial massage treatments to meet specific physical needs.</li>\r\n<li>How to layout, evaluate, and assess the remedial massage treatments.</li>\r\n<li>Perform to do remedial massage musculoskeletal assessments.</li>\r\n<li>Manage legal and ethical compliance of the body.</li>\r\n<li>Provide first aid and other relevant health factors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-koolshooters-6628600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Develop Your Talent </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Develop the attributes to help you get ahead:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Build strong communication skills and meet the communication empowerment.</li>\r\n<li>Grow your understanding of the concept of therapeutic relationships with clients.</li>\r\n<li>Good listening skills while asking appropriate questions and presenting them correctly.</li>\r\n<li>Along with communication skills growth, you will learn to obtain problem-solving skills.</li>\r\n<li>Fundamental marketing and business skills will develop under this course qualification.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Save Time and Money </strong></h3>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>The course costs much lower than any other accredited or professional training and qualifications.</li>\r\n<li>Even there are various discount prices you may get based on your experience or previous qualifications.</li>\r\n<li>Many registered training organizations (RTO) offers scholarship degree or free assessment eligibility test.</li>\r\n<li>You can save a tremendous amount of time within seven days or two weeks, and you can earn a <a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Recognition Prior Learning (RPL) certificate of remedial massage.</a></li>\r\n<li>No need to attend any traditional schooling or training center for a long training duration. Easily you can do an RPL assessment and get qualified.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Achieve Your Goals </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Completing this course provides you with:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Nationally recognized Diploma of Remedial Massage</li>\r\n<li>Skills and knowledge to start your own business or massage spa.</li>\r\n<li>Empower with the right blend of theoretical and pragmatic knowledge.</li>\r\n<li>The motive is to <a href=\"../../blogs/how-can-the-remedial-massage-therapy-effects-physically-and-psychologically\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">improve health</a> and also merely provide relief from instant body aches.</li>\r\n<li>The involvement in engagement with other medical and allied health professionals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Career Opportunities </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our graduates move into job roles like:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Remedial Massage Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Deep Tissue Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Massage Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Expert Physician</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Grow Your Career </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Take your career further with the following:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Self-employed as an independent remedial therapist and multi-disciplinary practice.</li>\r\n<li>Diploma of Remedial Massage Business and other <a href=\"../../diploma-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">relevant qualifications in the beauty industry</a>.</li>\r\n<li>The allied health practitioners, hospitals, aged care facilities, and other health organizations like gyms, sporting clubs, and health spas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Learn Medical Terms </strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The teaching approach is designed to train the therapist to understand the anatomical body under normal health status.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">This course will teach you the importance of using a blend of specific musculoskeletal appraisal techniques.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Learn all the initial tasks which are needed to become a therapist, especially for the physician.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">This course provides students with core practical skills in massage techniques used for massage, stretching, and soft tissue dysfunction.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, this will also help to develop a comprehensive treatment plan using the specialist massage method.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Get practical skills in running a massage business and practice while implementing injury prevention strategies for clients engaging in sport and exercise.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">This diploma course increases the ability to appraise backbone posture, <a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/muscle-imbalance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">muscular imbalances</a>, and mobility using recognized testing protocols.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Why Diploma of Remedial Massage Course is Important', 'Why Diploma of Remedial Massage Course is Important', 'Don’t we all need relaxation at least once a week to completely free ourselves from daily activities and stress which in turn affects the physical as well as mental wellbeing? Certainly, we do.', 'what-is-the-importance-of-study-diploma-of-remedial-massage-course-in-australia.png', NULL, '2020-11-18 03:01:14', '2022-01-16 04:34:49'),
(14, 7, 'Want to be a Professional STYLIST? Get Certificate III in Hairdressing!', 'want-to-be-a-professional-stylist-get-certificate-iii-in-hairdressing', 5, 'Hairdressing is an occupation that has intrigued both male and female practitioners. Dating back in time, male hairdressers (often called barbers) predominantly served the male customers and women served the female customers.', '<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hairdressing is an occupation that has intrigued both male and female practitioners. Dating back in time, male hairdressers (often called barbers) predominantly served male customers and women served female customers. But, lately, in modern times, such distinctions have become less rigid.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">In accordance with the Australian Government\'s Job Outlook, hairdressing skills are in demand with employers finding it hard to fill vacancies. The industry is currently experiencing vigorous development with more than 31,000 job openings anticipated over the next five years.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>What is Certificate III in Hairdressing?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">If someone dreams of being a hairstylist or owning their own salon or is simply enthusiastic about exploring a dynamic career in hairdressing that will enhance their creativity and accelerate their skills to perfection, the <a href=\"../../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\">Certificate III in Hairdressing course</a> is the right fit for them.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Established in 2016, <a href=\"../../\">Noble Training Academy</a> is a privately operated Registered Training Organisation. The courses are provided within Australia. They offer a range of nationally recognised qualifications from Certificate III to Diploma level in the beauty industry.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What is Certificate III in Hairdressing.jpg\" alt=\"What is Certificate III in Hairdressing\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dedicated to their duty as a nationally recognised training provider, they empower their students with the right blend of theoretical and pragmatic knowledge. The NTA hairdressing team is a cut above the rest and will help individuals pursue a career in this exciting industry.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">An individual can learn skills in designing and applying a wide span of technical hairdressing services including cutting, styling, colouring, perming, and straightening.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It is recommended that individuals set on the path to a successful career in hairdressing with this entry-level qualification. Students can earn the practical skills to confidently seek employment in a hair salon as a hairdresser.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It is also advisable to learn modern salon operations including colouring and lightening hair, providing shampoo and basin services, and designing and cutting hair. All of this will take place in the classroom and real functioning professional salon environments too.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Some talented individuals possessing good hands can fast track their way to a formal qualification by earning credit for the things they already know. Getting recognition for the skills that they have gained from the workplace or previous learning means less study time for them, and getting the paper to prove that they are qualified a whole lot sooner. Students can assess their skills by directly applying for credits from the previous successful study, and get advanced standing in their course.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This qualification equips an individual with practical skills in design and style, foundation colour, hair and scalp treatments, long hair design, protein treatments, and straightening, men&rsquo;s grooming, advanced cutting, and colour techniques.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This industry-standard solution is equipped with the newest equipment. The salon provides the ideal training environment to practise the student&rsquo;s acquired skills while expert trainers teach, supervise, and guide them. They can also gain valuable experience arranging bookings and in customer service as the qualified, industry experts will also teach students to consult with clients, promote products and services.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/How Long Does Certificate III in Hairdressing Take.jpg\" alt=\"How Long Does Certificate III in Hairdressing Take\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">On completion, individuals can have the confidence and skills to provide a variety of hairdressing services and begin their career as qualified hairdresser. They can also have the <a href=\"../../blogs/best-15-expert-hair-color-tips-to-apply-at-home\">knowledge to treat hair</a>, build confidence, and indulge their client, and create looks that will turn heads.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\">How Long Does </span>Certificate III in Hairdressing Take?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It varies among different programs, but certificate III is generally 12 to 18 months of hands-on work and study.<br />And the studies highlights highlights the importance of knowing what you need to know and be able to do when you get there.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There\'s always a lot that changes in the field, so the best experts in the world will tell you they need staff who are good at improvisation. The point is not to memorize procedures off by heart; it\'s about understanding them well enough that forgetting what they actually entail doesn\'t stop you from applying them on your own when called for.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Hairdressing is an occupation that has intrigued both male and female practitioners. Dating back in time, male hairdressers (often called barbers) predominantly served the male customers and women served the female customers.', 'want-to-be-a-professional-stylist-get-certificate-iii-in-hairdressing.png', NULL, '2020-11-24 03:18:43', '2022-01-16 08:52:18'),
(17, 7, 'Do You Want to be A Beautician Rather Than A Doctor? Know The Competition', 'do-you-want-to-be-a-beautician-rather-than-a-doctor-know-the-competition', 6, 'It might surprise you if anyone tells you about choosing to be a Beautician rather than a Doctor.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It might surprise you if anyone tells you about choosing to be a Beautician rather than a Doctor. Here, presenting some of the finest reasons why should an individual choose the career path of being a Beautician over a Doctor.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Importance of a Beautician</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. Fast Entry into the Market</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you enter into the beauty industry by getting enrolled in a related course, it doesn\'t consume much of an individual&rsquo;s time to get qualified and earn the certification. Moreover, individuals can get a license within the timeframe of one year or less. Whereas if an individual were a doctor, it requires them to first complete the mandatory 5 years long course then specialize in Dermatology for another 2 - 3 years.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Importance of a Beautician.jpg\" alt=\"Importance of a Beautician\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Work with People from Various Backgrounds</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauticians are not limited to just salons and therapy centers. If one has good hands-on techniques, they can work with famous celebrities. More or less every celebrity has their own beautician that they rely on. Celebrities like to consult with their personal preferred beauticians to toggle some of their features rather than getting an appointment with a doctor because getting an appointment with a good dermatologist is pretty time-consuming.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. One Can Earn a Handsome Amount</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauty is all about money in today&rsquo;s world. When an individual works as a beautician, the work context leads them towards successful career build up in the industry generating better income. Moreover, if an individual does a good job at work it open doors to repeat customers, referrals, and tips as well. Although a doctor&rsquo;s charge is more than compared to that of a beautician, people nowadays trust the beauticians and when they have repeated customer they can rather have a good amount of earnings.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. Fun Working Environment</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The job is rather fun with a relaxing working environment. To add on, individuals get to work in the field that they really love. The work allows the individual to play around toggling with different colors and textures. As well as permit individuals to sharpen their skills. Whereas Doctor&rsquo;s life is quite mundane and they need to apply only the taught skills, pretty restricted.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>5. Flexible Schedule</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The working schedules are rather flexible which allows individuals to work full-time, part-time, day shifts, night shifts, and on weekends as per their preferences. Thus individuals have the opportunity to work alongside their studies. This flexibility is not possible for doctors. They need to maintain their routine works and be on their duties or sometimes rush to the workplace if there&rsquo;s an emergency.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Importance of a Beautician Rather Than A Doctor.jpg\" alt=\"Importance Beautician Rather Than A Doctor\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>6. Work As An Entrepreneur</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A certified beautician has the freedom to set up their own business and enjoy being their own boss rather than working under another person&rsquo;s supervision after getting the certificate from a verified institution. In terms of medical studies, even after completing their studies, it is required for them to work under supervision for a longer period to earn the required training to set up their own chambers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Words</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the context of Australia, the beauty industry is progressing day by day. One of the RTO which avails <a href=\"../../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\">Certificates in beauty courses</a> is Noble Training Academy (NTA). It is a privately operated Registered Training Organisation that gives certificates within Australia in beauty-related courses. It offers a range of nationally recognized qualifications from Certificate III to Diploma level in the beauty industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The training at <a href=\"../../\">Noble Training Academy (NTA)</a> is developed to ensure that the graduates learn skills that are relevant to the needs of employers and clients in the beauty industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So, if an individual is still in a dilemma between choosing their career as a beautician and a doctor then they must give a thought to the abovementioned reasons which will help them to decide.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'It might surprise you if anyone tells you about choosing to be a Beautician rather than a Doctor.', 'do-you-want-to-be-a-beautician-rather-than-a-doctor-know-the-competition.png', NULL, '2020-12-17 02:08:40', '2022-01-16 04:48:32'),
(21, 7, 'Remedial Massage Vs. Deep Tissue Massage- Know Which is Better!', 'remedial-massage-vs-deep-tissue-massage-know-which-is-better', 4, 'Both remedial and soft-tissue massage techniques have different responsibilities and criteria to follow. According to the need, do your social media research to learn more about those before making a therapist appointment.', '<p>A good massage session can offer much-needed relief from stress and pain, whether an individual is feeling muscle tension, aches, and pains (acute or chronic) or just required to iron out those back-to-work knots. The only challenge needs to face is to choose the perfect offer as there are many different types of massage these days. People committed to physical exercises or playing professional sports are well acquainted with the terms <a href=\"../../blogs/how-can-the-remedial-massage-therapy-effects-physically-and-psychologically\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">remedial massage</a> and deep tissue massage, both of which assist with muscle recovery and soreness. Deep tissue massage and remedial massage are frequently mixed up with or thought to be the same, but in reality, they are very contrasting. Finding out the variation between the two can help people choose the right one for them under particular circumstances. So, here you will get to know all the facts about remedial massage Vs deep tissue massage and all the differences to know which is better.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>What Are the Differences Between Remedial Massage Vs. Deep Tissue Massage?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-anthony-shkraba-4599433.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"694\" height=\"462\" /></strong></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Remedial Massage&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A remedial massage is known as a form of complementary therapy that focuses on treating a specific problem area regularly caused by postural imbalance, muscle tension, and soft tissue injury. This type of therapy often starts with a complete assessment of the problematic muscles, ligaments, tendons, and posture.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedial massage can provide relief from a wide range of muscle and joint conditions. Oppositely, it can be used as a prevailing relaxation treatment. At the same time, it is perceived as an effective treatment option for particular musculoskeletal disorders/complaints. Accounted in the job responsibilities, let\'s define all the key benefits are to <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">becoming a remedial therapist</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-anete-lusina-5240677.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>What are The Health Benefits of Taking Remedial Massage?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regular remedial massage brings more blood supply and helps to release muscle tension and reduce the range of physical motions.</li>\r\n<li>This one is a proven massage technique that is beneficial for relieving from lowering neck and shoulder pain.</li>\r\n<li>Meanwhile, it <a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/bone-health/the-4-main-types-of-posture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">aids from postural issues</a> and makes body joints more mobilized and correctly as per the bone\'s positions.</li>\r\n<li>This massage method repairs damaged tissues and heal those unwanted, injured muscles from long ago.</li>\r\n<li>It improves the sleeping duration and improves neural health issues to reduce headaches, abdominal pain, and sciatic pain.</li>\r\n<li>Remedial massage is functional in reducing chronic back pain and assisting in restoring bone tone and accuracy from inside.</li>\r\n<li>Getting a remedial massage helps premature infants gain weight and let the mother sit or do chores comfortably.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Qualification Requirements</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Earn the year of the apprenticeship or internship experience from any spa or massage center for getting more preferences in this next step.</li>\r\n<li>The <a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Diploma of Remedial Massage- (HLT52015)</a> is nationally recognized and completes the intermediate level qualification for becoming a massage therapist.</li>\r\n<li>It also requires to have incorporated massage business practices and practical clinic hours for a long or short based on the qualification progress.</li>\r\n<li>You may prefer to join a professional association such as the Association of Massage Therapists or the Australian Traditional Medicine Society.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Earning Scale</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Screenshot_9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"237\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>The average <a href=\"../../blogs/what-is-the-importance-of-study-diploma-of-remedial-massage-course-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">remedial massage therapist</a> salary in Australia is $60,000 per year or $30.77 per hour. Entry-level positions, the range starts at $58,250 yearly, while most experienced workers make up to $97,500 per year.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Deep Tissue Massage&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This type of massage is directed at the deeper tissue structures of the muscles and fascia. Albeit it relies on many of the same movements and techniques used in Swedish massage, the amount of pressure exerted is generally more intense as the therapist works to release the chronic muscle tension or knots. This added pressure may feel uncomfortable on several occasions but is frequently known as a \"good pain\" by clients. It enhances the <a href=\"../../blogs/importance-of-soft-tissue-remedial-massage-in-real-life\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">therapeutic benefits</a> of the massage and helps patients recover from chronic pain and injury. Deep tissue massage is often an all-over treatment that is not focused on a specific issue but addresses the whole body. Other physical benefits include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-cottonbro-3997980.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"671\" height=\"447\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>What are The Health Benefits of Soft-tissue Massage?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Such remedial massage will help to lower the inflammation of joints and improve heart rate and oxygen flow.</li>\r\n<li>This massage technique will improve the range of physical motion and flexibilities and also releases endorphins.</li>\r\n<li>Soft-tissue massage is a powerful method against muscle spasms, cramps, and easing stiffness or pain in people with arthritis.</li>\r\n<li>This massage increases hemoglobin production very naturally and builds potential recreation on blood cells.</li>\r\n<li>Daily soft-tissue practices help to increase the enhancement in athletic performance and sportspeople.</li>\r\n<li>This massage provides and develops eases discomfort associated with pregnancy and menopause.</li>\r\n<li>One of the important roles of this massage is to reduce symptoms of fibromyalgia and other nerves.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Qualification Requirements</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To become a soft tissue massage therapist, it is obvious to have years of massage experience in the relevant industry.</li>\r\n<li>A Certificate IV in Massage Therapy (HLT42015) will need under this profession to bloom and count as a quality therapist.</li>\r\n<li>A higher degree or qualification is not mandatory to hold this position, but years of massage practice are required.</li>\r\n<li>This massage technique is a very professional term to earn a license from an association such as the Association of Massage Therapists (AMT) or the Australian Traditional Medicine Society.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Earning Scale</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The average soft tissue therapist salary in Australia is $117,000 per year or $60 per hour. Entry-level positions start at $117,000 per year, while most experienced workers earn $117,000 per year.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Screenshot_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"447\" height=\"214\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Which Massage is Best for You?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Counter that part, both remedial and soft-tissue massage techniques have different responsibilities and criteria to follow. According to the need, do your social media research to learn more about those before making a therapist appointment. As both massage techniques are used by the professional therapist so from the recommendation both, have a good impact on our body in a positive vibe and well health issues.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Final Draft&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In conclusion, deep tissue massage is ideal for those looking for a whole-body massage and the therapeutic benefits of firm pressure. On the flip side, remedial massage is a focused treatment and ideal for those with chronic pain and injuries that require proper diagnosis and specific treatment. Remedial massage is also covered under most people\'s private health extras in Australia, whereas deep tissue massage is not.</p>', NULL, 'Remedial Massage Vs. Deep Tissue Massage,', 'Both remedial and soft-tissue massage techniques have different responsibilities and criteria to follow. According to the need, do your social media research to learn more about those before making a therapist appointment.', 'remedial-massage-vs-deep-tissue-massage.jpeg', NULL, '2021-02-25 07:40:19', '2021-11-16 15:51:51');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(25, 7, 'How can the Remedial massage therapy effects physically and psychologically?', 'how-can-the-remedial-massage-therapy-effects-physically-and-psychologically', 4, 'You have any muscle pain or got any lousy back posture and have lots of pain. Then, you better go and counsel with a remedial therapist. You will get relief from both physical and psychological benefits from this massage technique.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">From the ancient time of Valley civilization, the practices of remedial massage and all other techniques of massages were invention eventually. The global healthcare system depends on old corrective massage techniques and becomes an essential part of medical science in this present state.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Now the World Health Organization (WHO) supports remedial massage therapy as those have some extent benefits and most reliable art for healing injured body parts. It also makes your mind and brain peaceful. Most of the massage facilities are provided by professional therapy Center to follow a key component as sports medicine. For any particular muscle pain, the doctor recommends taking remedial massage therapy, and it will gradually help recover from the suffering. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Still, those techniques are not commonly used in this era of technology. The various relaxation tools and gadgets are now available in the market at a high price. Those electronic devices may relieve you from instant pain but can\'t provide the ultimate peace of mind to gain from the traditional massage. Let\'s discuss some relevant topics about the effects of remedial massage on the physical and mental side.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What is a Remedial Massage.jpg\" alt=\"What is a Remedial Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">What is a Remedial Massage?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Remedial therapy is a former massage technique that applies to give the treatment of affecting body muscles, tendons, and ligaments parts under some conditions. The core key of this massage is to Improve back posture, show flexibility, relieve you from sore and weak muscles. Also, help to perform a great exercise to heal injured parts. This massage has different types of required positions to apply according to the body\'s needs. Many professional therapists provide these facilities and have their own therapy Center. Also, some RTO offers diploma courses in Remedial massage and RPL certificates under some conditions. Those courses are for experienced therapists and to learn more about physical assessments.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">What Can One Expect from a Remedial Massage?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">It is explicitly used for relaxation or to reduce pain and normalize the body\'s muscles and soft tissues. There is no need to have an injury to take any of the massages for your body. You can simply take any remedial massages for relaxing your body cells every day. It\'s better to monitor the change of your body capacity by time-to-time through this easy procedure. With this idea, you can always track your body posture and other muscle damages. Don\'t worry too much; this massage course doesn\'t have any particular point to get injured, or you will get hurt later.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Usually, those don\'t have any prior side effects. But, in some cases, a few massages technique can misbehave with your body tone and cause some initial pain, which can be a part of your worries if someone deals with osteoporosis or has cancer-related to nerves and bones. It will be wise to avoid such remedial massages because it can backfire, and the soft tissues can get harmed and contagious to spread.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What Can One Expect from a Remedial Massage.jpg\" alt=\"What Can One Expect from a Remedial Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The therapist wants to confirm your trouble areas before the procedure starts. A deep massage can draw to your entire body or just any particular based on your comfort. As you get ready to take possession of massage, they will take you to the massage chamber. You can keep the level of your private part as the contentment you prefer. But the area is prescribed for a massage needs to disclose for the therapist to work on. Don\'t worry; the therapists always professionally maintain their work line. Now the therapist will warm your body muscles by letting you inside of a candlelight room. Some therapists Centers have stem bath and other premium services for the clients. After that, the therapy patient will lay on the unique board, and the therapy doctor will examine your spots and gather information regarding this. Then he/she will start the steps of remedial massage in the constructed way. After the session, clients are asked to get dressed and let them relax in the restroom. With all the procedures done, clients can make any feedback with the services.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">What are The Mental Effects of Regular Remedial Massage?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">This massage proficiency improves your mental health to get relief from incredible stress and suffering from anxiety. Remedial massage can help cortisol regulate everything for better mental health. Sometimes after a good massage session, you will feel unique and refresh from up to bottom. The effect can be more immediate and quite powerful so that stress can melt away.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What are The Mental Effects of Regular Remedial Massage.jpg\" alt=\"What are The Mental Effects of Regular Remedial Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Along with that, you can check your day-to-day progress through the therapy\'s initial components. You need to know what is the demand of your body is required and how much relaxation massages are necessary daily. Thinking of that, a daily check-up of your posture and the proper build of the muscle can prevent you from the risk zone of many body pains. It will also give you some mental satisfaction and a confident mind for the regular activities. After a good therapy session, you will feel fresh and have a clearer vision of your eyes and breath. Some experts say, doing remedial massage and yoga are undoubtedly good for getting inner peace. Also, it helps to preserve a healthy lung, improve the Diagnostic system, and other more health issues. There are many other benefits and sound effects in regular remedial massage that brain stream and helps to improve psychologically.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Bottom Line</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">There are some fundamental differences between regular and remedial massage. Remedial massage is a very old and most relieve technique in this modern world. On the other hand, traditional massages help to reduce your pain from any particular side of your body for the short term. Though remedial massage is more professional and legit for treatment, a therapist should have proper skills assessment in therapy. From this article, you get the whole picture of the remedial therapy system and the working effect in both physical and mental order. In the end, it is clear that either way remedial massage is a perfect technique for our body and to take as a treatment for all kind of muscle construct problem and other. To read more information about Remedial massage therapy you can visit to our website.</span></p>', 'Remedial Massage Therapy', 'Remedial Massage Therapy', 'You have any muscle pain or got any lousy back posture and have lots of pain. Then, you better go and counsel with a remedial therapist. You will get relief from both physical and psychological benefits from this massage technique.', 'how-can-the-remedial-massage-therapy-effects-physically-and-psychologically.png', NULL, '2021-06-08 08:10:23', '2022-01-16 04:31:17'),
(26, 7, 'How to Start Up your Own Beauty Boutique in Australia', 'how-to-start-up-your-own-beauty-boutique-in-australia', 6, 'If you really want to open a new business of your own, and don’t know what to do next. Then you can click here and check out all the difficulties before opening a beauty boutique in Australia.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the iconic and most trendy businesses is now &lsquo;opening a boutique house&rsquo; in Australia. Most women are involved in this manufacturing industry because it is easy to start from their homes or small places. Even most of the housewives are also engaging in this business of their own territories. It has trouble-free opening terms and a simple structure with less effort to generate a shopping venue of various beauty items. If you research the nearby Australian marketplaces, indeed, you will acknowledge that most of the showrooms are well decorated but in a tiny space. They are conducting most of their trading activities online and doing digital marketing to promote the business.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Opening a small business has no hassle, but you still need to know the basic things one should consider before opening a beauty venture or a showroom in Australia. Simply, you can take advice from an expert person about the business plan, or you can get exclusive information from this article. Go through the rest of the parts and know-how to start your own beauty boutique in Australia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Types of Beauty Boutique Industries </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you want to start a business in the beauty industry, you must first set your mind on which sector will be best to start. Some begin with the single slot business, and some do trade in multi-niches beauty items. Here we categorize some of the companies in the beauty boutique industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Clothing Store </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The clothing store is one of the largest sectors in the beauty industry. Nowadays, people like to buy and sell clothes as it is an accessible and top-rated business in Australia. The clothing industry is doing well for all gender and ages. Especially designer clothes have an extreme demand in the clothing market.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Jewellery Store </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The jewellery field is also doing great in the beauty business. People are becoming more fashionable with the changes of times. Stylish and antique jewellery has a huge demand in the Australian beauty market.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Herbal Beauty Product </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">All women of all ages are now getting concerned about protecting their skin and essential parts. Even men are also conscious about their skincare. Herbal and organic beauty items are an excellent and profitable business in Australia. So, this business got a chance on the list.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Remedial Massage Center </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\">Remedial massage</a> makes a revolutionary change in the beauty industry and takes to another level of technique. In current days, remedial massage is counting as the natural art of beauty. So, the trend of this massage Center is having a significant influence in the beauty industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Beauty Salon &amp; Personal Care </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Many people are showing their interest in beauty care services in this recent time. Australian people love to take extra care of their hair and skin. So, the uprising business is the beauty salon and the personal care clinic in Australia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Beauty Craft Accessory </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the rising businesses is craft accessory sales in Australia. Mainly handcraft pieces of jewellery, makeup accessory, and related items are on the top list of the beauty industry. Other multiple items are included in this service, and Australian people love those items for their daily life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"1623923436.jpg\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/1624518099.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"626\" height=\"417\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Essential Things to Start A Boutique Store </strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Firstly, for opening a boutique store, you need to register for an ANB and get permission from the Australian government. Categorized businesses may differ the paper works of registration, but almost the process is the same as the other sectors. After getting the permission, all you need to set up a place for running your business.</li>\r\n<li>Later, choose a comfortable industry and pick a niche item according to your suitable business zone. It will not be wise to enter into the beauty market without having any knowledge and idea about the niche you want to deal with. Now it&rsquo;s time to draw a plan for the business and estimate a budget for setup the decoration and any construction works. You should have a proper plan to execute your dream business under the policies of the Australian government.</li>\r\n<li>Set up a dynamic business name and design an attractive logo with a bold tagged line. But make sure that the name and logo you create must not have any trademark or copyright issues and available to register from the Australian Securities and Investments Commission (ASIC).</li>\r\n<li>You may need to get approval from the local Council of Environmental Health Department (EHD) to provide any personal care services. Additionally, skincare, massages Center, herbal beauty products, and similar items relevant to the health or hygienic issues then those businesses need regular inspections to form the local council of EHD.</li>\r\n<li>Choose the proper structure whether you want to go for solo or partnership business. Depending on the business formation, make some options for reinvestments or bank loan services and do the rest of the paper.</li>\r\n<li>If you are holding the business under your property, there&rsquo;s no need to have an agreement or rental papers. On the other hand, must collect the rental documents on a rent space and check properly before signing the contract. Ensure to gather all the legal documents or hire a legal lawyer if you can&rsquo;t understand which are required by Australian consumer law.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Skills And Qualifications to Start up A New Business</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Must need customer service skills to serve the customers appropriately.</li>\r\n<li>An excellent conversation skill can build a good reputation for your start-up business.</li>\r\n<li>Your business portfolio should be detailed and fair with the terms according to the law.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledgeable skills and real-life experiences are needed to enter the beauty industry business.</li>\r\n<li>An RPL holder from the beauty industry has many different preferences to build their own beauty business in Australia.</li>\r\n<li>Some basic academic qualifications are essential to set up the legal papers for your own beauty boutique business.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Final Term</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Finally, we can say it is elementary for anyone to start up a beauty boutique store in Australia with some official procedures. People are enjoying these beauty industries as they can start up as an SME categorize business. The trend of small companies is giving massive support to the Australian economy. Find your perfect match from the industry and kick your career in the beauty business.</p>', 'Beauty boutique, Beauty, Australia', 'Beauty boutique in Australia', 'If you really want to open a new business of your own, and don’t know what to do next. Then you can click here and check out all the difficulties before opening a beauty boutique in Australia.', 'how-to-start-up-your-own-beauty-boutique-in-australia.png', NULL, '2021-06-17 07:43:27', '2022-01-16 04:28:49'),
(27, 7, 'Best 15 Expert Hair Color Tips to Apply at Home', 'best-15-expert-hair-color-tips-to-apply-at-home', 5, 'Want to get a perfect finishing hair color like a beauty parlor or a saloon at home. Click here to learn some of the expert\'s hair coloring tips and shine your hair with colors.', '<p>You love your beautiful hair and want to make them more delighted. So, your first thought will be to apply hair colors and have a more attractive style with your hair. But going to a saloon for making hair colors and other hair treatments can be pretty expensive. Sometimes it can be out of your league to afford such hair clinic services. But, you don\'t need to visit the beauty parlor to get flowless and quality DIY colors on your hair. Easily you can apply the color in your hair by yourself.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Following some easy steps, you can make your own hair color without having a helping hand. All you need to know which color form to apply and how to do the color brushing on the hair. Some more techniques have to consider in your account while you are mixing and using the colors. So, here we are, giving you an easy solution to becoming an expert on self-hair dye. Go through the rest of the part, and you will get to know some professional tips and tricks to do outstanding hair dye at your home.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/blobid2\" alt=\"professional hair color tips\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>15 Expert Hair Color Tips to Apply at Home</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Choose the color:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>First of all, you need to confirm which color you want to put on the hair. Like, fancy or delighted colors can be explosive and not suitable with your appearances. On the other hand, some prefer such a color combination. Whatever you applied, make sure to use the grade one hair color.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Don\'t believe in the advertisements:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you expect to get such hair color as a TV actress or a fashion magazine model, it\'s better to leave the dream here. Because most of them are well prepared and totally a setup framework to attract audiences. So, nothing is real here.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Apply permanent or semi-permanent colors:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For a temporary solution, you can put some semi- parament color for the hair dyeing. Those types of colors lasting for a year or two. Additionally, those who do the permanent colors are not able to change them. So careful to get to know your choice before trying.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/hair color tips for home.jpg\" alt=\"hair color tips for home\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Choose the powder according to the texture:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hair texture is important, and you need to realize the type of hair you have. For example, the surface of curly and frizzy hair is way too good to absorb the dark color. The result goes opposite for straight or medium texture hair and gives a slightly warmer tone of color.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Use two boxes of color:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Basically, the measurement of hair color powder depends on the length of your hair and the areas you want to do the coloring. If you have long hair and want to color the whole, you will need at least two boxes to markup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Perfect sectioning:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The sectioning is essential to maintain, and the hair line-up should be in the ideal formations to do multi-coloring in your hair at a time. All you need to focus on is avoiding the patches and do the color segments perfectly. Otherwise, the shades can mix.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Perform some touch up:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Some handy hints can be needed while you\'re doing the coloring. Using a toothbrush is the primary tool to apply the color. Along with that, for highlighting any section of your hair. Use a bold brush and finger thumb before the dry theme.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/professional hair color advice.jpg\" alt=\"professional hair color advice\" width=\"600\" height=\"535\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Do spot treatments:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Use Vaseline in the hair root to not getting damaged by the dye\'s chemical. Even you can do some spot-fixing while brushing colors in your hair with your hand. Use clips and hairbands can be helpful tools for such treatments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Protect your Skin:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is essential to use the safeguard for your eyes, ear, nose, and overall facial protections. You can use a towel or forehead band to stop the leak of the color and prevent skin damage from the artificial colors.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Apply oil before coloring:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>One of the best tips is to get the oil appeal before proceeding with the hair color. Using coconut or almond oil will be great to make a plea for preserving the hair\'s moisture under the layout of the shade. For the root touch-up, you can use deep conditioning masks.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Never experiment with multi-shades:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is not wise to use or do the gradian of the colors for inventing a new shade. Professional always suggest avoiding such experiments because the shade tones don\'t urge to turn into a new color with multi-colors. It will be a waste and can damage your hair.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Wear an old cotton cloth:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Find an old cotton cloth to use in the hair dyeing process. As the hair color is made of solid elements and the stain can be fixed. So, for safety purposes, the use of an old button shirt is the finest choice for this operation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Add warm water:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To mix the color powders, use some sparkle of water. Then, if you run out of color, you can add some warm water to make more quantity of liquid. With this technique, you can adequately use the color powder when you are at the low stack.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Hair Color at Home.jpg\" alt=\"Hair Color at Home\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Use shampoo to clean:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Always remember to wash your hair, neck, shoulder with shampoo and body wash. Just rinsing with water isn\'t enough because the color coats can remain in the hair only by the water splash. So, make sure to not clean with water. Instead, use warm water and then apply shampoo for better cleaning.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong><strong>Apply conditioner after Drying:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The final tip and trick for doing hair color are always to apply conditioner according to the hair tone you. Because hair dying is a very core process, and it can cause massive damage to your hair. So, the basic treatment after hair coloring is always carried conditioner whenever you want to make some bright hair tone.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To have a well and perfect look at your hair color, using those professional tricks and tips can solve your coloring issues. Just maintain with the procedure and read the instruction note carefully, which is given into the packet. Then, following some of those easy steps and do DIY hair color at your home like a saloon.</p>', 'Beauty boutique, Beauty, Australia, hair dressing', 'Hair color tips', 'Want to get a perfect finishing hair color like a beauty parlor or a saloon at home. Click here to learn some of the expert\'s hair coloring tips and shine your hair with colors.', 'expert-hair-color-tips-to-apply-at-home.jpeg', NULL, '2021-06-22 08:05:07', '2021-08-22 04:29:04'),
(28, 7, 'Top 10 Famous Celebrity Hairdressers with Biography', 'top-10-famous-celebrity-hairdressers-with-biography', 5, 'Nowadays, new and young hairdressers involve in this industry with technology and artwork. But it is not easy to become a world-class hairstylist and an iconic hairdresser in this competition.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose you follow the celebrity and get mesmerized by their appearances. Then remember all those eye-catching looks come from the effort of the makeup and hair artists. Nowadays, new and young hairdressers involve in this industry with technology and artwork. But it is not easy to become a world-class hairstylist and an iconic hairdresser in this competition.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olds are still standing in this list of fame at the top, and they have become prevalent in the celebrity world. So, we are going to talk about some celebrity hairdressers in this draft, along with their biography.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Biography of the Hairdressers.jpg\" alt=\"Biography of the Hairdressers\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Biography of the Hairdressers</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Oribe Canales</strong></h3>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Oribe Canales.jpg\" alt=\"Oribe Canales\" width=\"300\" height=\"401\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If we are talking about the most famous and worldwide known hairdressers, then the name of American hairstylist Oribe Canales comes in the top position. This Cuba hairdresser had 42 years of glory career in the American hairdressing industry. He worked with many top models, professional actors/actresses, and fashion houses (like Versace, Thierry Mugler, Calvin Klein, and Chanel) in his career. His shop (Orbe Saloon) is located in Miami Beach. Oribe was born in Jaruco, Cuba, in September 1956 and died at the age of 62 in 2018. Still, he is introduced as the most iconic and popular living American hairdresser in the 20th Century.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mark Townsend</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Mark Townsend.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Townsend\" width=\"300\" height=\"409\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mark is the most talented and well-known hairstylist in New York City. Nowadays, he got the attention of the most famous celebrities as their favourite hairdresser. Name of his brilliant work included Jessica Biel, Lea Michele, Cate Blanchett, Halle Berry, Natalie Portman, Drew Barrymore and Rachel McAdams. This man was born in 1970 in a small city. With many years of experience, he becomes the founder of Sally Hershberger Salon in New York City.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ted Gibson</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Ted Gibson.jpg\" alt=\"Ted Gibson\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The growing sensation of the hair beauty industry, Ted Gibson has put himself in line with the world-famous hairdressers. He was born in Texas, the United States, in November 1965. Within a short time, he proved himself to become a celebrity hairstylist and launched his own product lines. He also opened two premium saloons, one, Ted Gibson Salon, in New York City and Ted Gibson, Fort Lauderdale Salon in Florida. Some of her celebrity clients are Angelina Jolie, Zoe Saldana, Ashley Greene, Mila Kunis, Lupita Nyong\'o from the Hollywood industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Harry Josh</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Harry Josh.jpg\" alt=\"Harry Josh\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the young and successful celebrity hairstylists is harry josh in the modern Hollywood industry. He is an American hairdresser and an entrepreneur of his hair brand named Harry Josh Pro Tools. At the age of fifteen, he was curious to work in the fashion world, and he began his hair designing training in Canada. Later, he landed in the United States to accomplish his dream. He was born in Vancouver, BC (Canada). He also worked with famous brands (British Vogue, GQ, Allure, Teen Vogue) and cast with many Hollywood directors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Jen Atkin</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Jen Atkin.jpg\" alt=\"Jen Atkin\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the present day, Jen Atkin is a sensational name for all the young generation in the global hairdressing industry. She is the co-owner of a leading beauty supplements business called OUAI, which is situated in New York City. Also, the founder of the digital magazine ManeAddicts, and a columnist for Glamour Magazine. By born, she got the American nationality, and she is the 41-year-old famous hairstylist Instagram star. She did the project with Chrissy Teigen, Jennifer Lopez, Gigi and Bella Hadid, and the stars of Instagram with the Kardashians.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>David Mallett</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/David Mallett.jpg\" alt=\"David Mallett\" width=\"400\" height=\"286\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This renowned Parisian Hairdresser, David Mallett, is chosen as one of Paris\'s high-rated and demanding hair designers. He is undoubtedly got fame and become the most trusted hairdresser for his wealthy clients. He has two premium saloons in Paris, and one recently opened in New York City. In his 35 years long career, he made some excellent connections with many leading fashion executives, supermodels, stylists, and designers. He did some projects with flagship brands for Lancel, Dior, L\'Oreal, Sonia Rykiel, Givenchy, Pirelli, and La Perla.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hiro Haraguchi</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Hiro Haraguchi.jpg\" alt=\"Hiro Haraguchi\" width=\"400\" height=\"286\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Asian first awarded hairdresser with 30 years\' experience in the hair beauty industry is Hiro Haraguchi. He was born in Japan and got the quality knowledge and skills in hair treatment and become an expert in hairstyle. He has his hair treatment spa and saloon in the country\'s capital, Hiro Haraguchi Hair Salon. Many celebrities are huge fans of his outstanding hair solutions, and they even call him the Hair Doctor. Some prominent designers and television stars like Vera Wang, as well as the actress from Friends. \'Lisa Kudrow\' is his regular client.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong><strong>Serge Normant</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Serge Normant.jpg\" alt=\"Serge Normant\" width=\"400\" height=\"304\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This English hairdresser and hairstylist, Serge Normant, is well-named in the tv series industry. Many known tv actresses are his beloved clients Julia Roberts, Sarah Jessica Parker, Jennifer Connelly, Rachel Weisz, and Gwyneth Paltrow. Along with that, supermodels like Gisele Bundchen, Christy Turlington, Linda Evangelista and Miranda Kerr are also frequent customers. He has a leading role in the fashion industry and top fashion magazines, including Harper\'s Bazaar, W, Allure, Elle and Vogue; regularly book Normant for cover sittings and fashion and beauty stories. Serge got his first publication named \'Femme Fatale\' in 2001, and the next one was Metamorphosis in 2004 about celebrity hairstyle and transformation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tracey Cunningham</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Tracey Cunningham.jpg\" alt=\"Tracey Cunningham\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tracey Cunningham is a famous colorist in California and owned a beauty salon named Byron &amp; Tracey in Beverly Hills. She always has a busy schedule to maintain massive customers and works for many celebrity clients like Jessica Biel, Jennifer Garner, Rosie Huntington-Whiteley. This beautiful hair colorist is 50 years old, and she was born in Seattle, WA, in July 1969. In her generous career, she also got the chance to meet with Jennifer Lopez, Cameron Diaz, Drew Barrymore, Emma Stone for on-request hair colour services.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chris McMillan</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Chris McMillan.jpg\" alt=\"Chris McMillan\" width=\"400\" height=\"247\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For three decades, Chris is involved in this hair art industry. He is known as the most stylish and very influential hairdresser among female celebrities. In his whole career, he has been worked with Jennifer Aniston, Courteney Cox, Cindy Crawford, Reese Witherspoon, Nicole Kidman, Hilary Swank, Michelle Williams, Anne Hathaway, Olivia Wilde, Sarah-Jessica Parker, Diane Lane, Jennifer Garner, Jennifer Lopez, Julia Robert and the list goes on. Chris McMillan is a pure California as he was born in Huntington Beach and never left Southern California. The Chris McMillan Salon was opened in Beverly Hills in July 2002. He was the true mastermind to make more out lashed beauty of the red carpet in the 1990s.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Lines:&nbsp; </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not all can become good hair specialists or hair influencers in the celebrity industry. Those hairdressers are the most experienced and working in the industry for a long. So, you can\'t deny the outstanding work lines of their hand magic into celebrity\' hair. Most of them have their own saloon and hair treatment Center. So, you can visit them but have to wait for a long to get an appointment as they are super busy with the model and working schedule.</p>', 'Famous Celebrity Hairdressers with Biography', 'Famous Celebrity Hairdressers, Hairdressers with Biography,Hairdressers Biography', 'Nowadays, new and young hairdressers involve in this industry with technology and artwork. But it is not easy to become a world-class hairstylist and an iconic hairdresser in this competition.', 'famous-celebrity-hairdressers.png', NULL, '2021-07-11 07:14:40', '2022-01-16 08:54:54');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(29, 7, '5 Best Beginner\'s Guide to Skincare for Men', 'beginners-guide-to-skincare-for-men', 6, 'As a man, you should not be ashamed to look for such beauty tips. A smart man always tries to look good and grow confident with his looks. So, we have listed some beginner\'s guide tips and ahead with the information about body and Skincare for men. ', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Every skin is not the same to take care of. Especially for males, a totally different tone and a different treatment should adopt for better Skincare. As a beginner, you might be thinking, why should a man take care of his skin and do body polishing? Is it necessary to do daily Skincare for men? What are the easiest steps for a beginner? And how to apply them without getting any side effects?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are looking for those answers, then all the answers are here. You will get to know more about male Skincare in this article. As a man, you should not be ashamed to look for such beauty tips. A smart man always tries to look good and grow confident with his looks. So, we have listed some beginner\'s guide tips and ahead with the information about body and Skincare for men.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why Should a Man Do Skincare and Body Polishing?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Why Should a Man Do Skincare and Body Polishing.jpg\" alt=\"Why Should a Man Do Skincare and Body Polishing\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Begin a man or having a non-posture look isn\'t your fault. You might feel shame or uncomfortable doing such Skincare, but to be honest, it\'s an open zone for everyone to look dashing and fresh. Maybe you are at the age of late 30 and thinking of making some changes in your skin. But you don\'t know where to start; the following steps will help you track the regular body and skin polishing.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Some Easiest Guidelines for Beginners to Start Skincare: </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Start using facewash: One of the easiest ways to take care of any face is using facewash and apply warm water to clean. Most men don\'t use face wash; they just sweep the facewash and only use regular water after returning from work. It may clean your skin but not give a deep wash of your tissues. As a result, the rising of pimples and the face becomes rough than a woman. So, always try to mop your face with face wash and warm water immediately after you step into your house.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. Maintain a Regular Routine:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To make a regular habit of cleaning, use wet tissues or an excellent organic facewash according to your skin tone. You can try some of the man\'s beauty products available in the market and fix your suitable care items for regular use. Also, you can end up going to the men\'s parlor a week or twice a month according to your need for full-body care. By this, you can maintain good management of your body polishing and a good habit of taking care of your skin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Skincare at youthful:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You should have known; it is essential to have a skincare regimen at your young age. Some of you may think it is good to start Skincare at a late age because, at a young age, you couldn\'t get any rug under your skin. But if you can begin to this habit from your youth, and you may not suffer from unwanted skin diseases or any other skin-related issues at your very old age. So, start glowing and make sure to adopt some skincare from a young age.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Guidelines for Beginners to Start Skincare.jpg\" alt=\"Guidelines for Beginners to Start Skincare\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. Apply face moisturizer:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hydrate your face with recommended moisturizer to avoid wrinkles and a dull-looking face. In general, a man\'s face got dehydrated quickly and left the skin tissues tight and dry. An oil-free face moisturizer needs to apply twice a day To restore the moisture of the skin. It is best to use at night and after your regular shower because your daily face soup dries the face to moisturize. To get rid of your early wrinkles and conserve the fine lines, using a good face moisturizer is a great solution.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. Keep things simple:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you want to contribute your skin, you don\'t need to push harder to achieve a good result. Some simple effort will help you shade your face and body\'s upper skin by doing regular maintenance. So, making some time for your productive care won\'t cost much time, and keeping the daily practice will make it easier to maintain. Trust me; you don\'t need to follow a ten-step routine that will hold you for hours and hours. All you can just do is face moisturizing, use face tone, exfoliate with face scrub and always use warm water.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>5. Natural Food habit:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A good food habit can change your whole life, including the excellent care of your skin. Some food like vegetables, a considerable quantity of meat, and reproduction foods can provide you an adjustable amount of protein and vitamins to store healthy skin. Very oily and fast foods can make your skin uncomfortable growing and don\'t let your skin tissues breathe properly. In that case, consuming more healthy foods will lead to a better conclusion for a man\'s health and let your skin Smolder from inside.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Why Should Men Take Care of Their Skin Daily.jpg\" alt=\"Why Should Men Take Care of Their Skin Daily\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why Should Men Take Care of Their Skin Daily? </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are fundamental differences in the physiological aspects of the skin in both men and women, which is very interesting to take care of. Men\'s skin tends to be about 25% thicker than a woman\'s coat. Men skin got higher collagen density, and it causes more skin oil. By considering the general skin issues like acne, the breakout tends to be exacerbated and lasts longer for a man. So, a daily mount of Skincare prevents such matters, and we need stuff that is more adapted to our skin. It may vary from person to person that needs to consider in your account, but it\'s not wise to apply female beauty products for your daily Skincare.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Terms: </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Following the upper context, we get to know some skins are sensitive, and some can be more reactive skin to apply by available products. So, maintaining all those things and guidelines, our recommendation is to use suitable and gentle products are needed to appeal to beginners. Don\'t rush with the product selection. Take your time, read all the product details, and know whether the elements are giving comfort or not. Applying natural ingredients can also be an excellent choice for any skin.</p>', NULL, 'Best Beginner\'s Guide to Skincare for Men', 'As a man, you should not be ashamed to look for such beauty tips. A smart man always tries to look good and grow confident with his looks. So, we have listed some beginner\'s guide tips and ahead with the information about body and Skincare for men. ', 'best-beginners-guide-to-skincare-for-men.png', NULL, '2021-07-27 08:26:39', '2022-01-16 08:14:54'),
(30, 7, 'The 10 Best Beauty Essentials Products Everyone Should Have in Travel Bag', 'best-beauty-essentials-products-everyone-should-have-in-travel-bag', 6, 'You should bring those things. Here, we list some of the best beauty essentials products everyone should have in their travel bag collections. Let\'s briefly discuss those items that, why those products are essentials to put in your cart.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Going on a foreign visit? Or you just got a call from your friends for an uncertain beach trip. Now you might be wonder that what are essentials need to be carried with the bag. You can\'t just put everything into your bag and step out from home. Considering the list of your items, you should take only the necessary things. Even for the cloth\'s items, there should be a limitation to carry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are differences between the man and the woman\'s beauty items. But some of the standard beauty products need to be inside of everyone\'s travel bag. No matter where you go, you should bring those things. Here, we list some of the best beauty essentials products everyone should have in their travel bag collections. Let\'s briefly discuss those items that, why those products are essentials to put in your cart.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Best-Beauty-Essentials-Products-Everyone-Should-Have-in-Travel-Bag.jpg\" alt=\"Best Beauty Essentials Products Everyone Should Have in Travel Bag\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">10 Best Beauty Essentials Products Everyone Should Have in Travel Bag</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. Face wash: </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nowadays, without the tube of a facewash, it is impossible to move around. You can carry one of your regular facewashes inside a small bottle or buy a mini tube for the trip. As journey means great tiredness of your face skin and you badly need to wash them clearly. So, every time, having a deep facial will let you look good on the whole trip.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Nourishing Hair Mask:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Usually, boys don\'t carry nourishing hair masks on their tours. Those items are beneficial for the girls to protect hair from dust and sun dryness. A day tour can be too much bothersome for a girl. Maintaining the hair is one of the reasons. So, girls should keep a hair nourishing mask in the suitcase.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. Sunscreen cream:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Landing on a beach trip, and you forget your sunscreen cream. Now, if you don\'t want to get burned in the sun, never forget to bring the sun-protected cream inside your backpack. Even going to dry areas, the sunscreen cream always needs to save your skin from burning from the heat of sunray.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Face Wash.jpg\" alt=\"Face Wash\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. Deodorants:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You may not allow yourself to keep your underarm sweaty and body odour while you are outside or having a long flight. Applying a deodorant will keep the underarm dry and won\'t let you get sweated and itchy for hours. Then why shouldn\'t it be on the list as your travel partner? Here, one of the essential items is deodorants spray to place in the bag.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>5. Hair Shampoo and Conditioner:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It won\'t be wise to neglect to take care of your hair. Your hair is also needed a proper wash and manageable setup. Cleaning your hair won\'t be enough. Use of shampoo is kind of mandatory for all, and let your scalp clean and get pumped by the conditioner. Rinse-out conditioner is used for detangled and to style the long hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>6. Body Cream or Moisturizing Lotion:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To keep your skin soften, moisturize and soothe for the whole day, you don\'t need to visit a spa before you head for a trip. Simply make some room for the body cream or lotion based on your preferences in your luggage. To get relief from dry and rough skin, using once beauty experts highly recommend a daily.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Body-Cream-or-Moisturizing-Lotion.jpg\" alt=\"Body Cream or Moisturizing Lotion\" width=\"600\" height=\"256\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>7. Lip balm:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are heading to Norway or to a very warm place like the desert, you will definitely need lip balm in your pocket. Those non-friendly places atmosphere can dry your lips and caused the lips to chap. Seasonal change can also be a matter of carrying a lip balm with you. So, don\'t leave your cream if you are going out.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>8. Shower Gel / Bathing Soap:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the important beauty items is shower gel or bathing soap. Usually, those are very handy to carry and also available anywhere. But why take the risk? Fetching one of the items with you can save you from humiliating unwanted stingy smells. Keeping travel bath soap or mini shower gel will help you to take a fresh shower.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>9. Makeup Box:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This beautiful piece is for women. To draw the emergency glow, girls never forget to take the mini makeup setting spray with them. Especially when there is an excellent place to click photos, and you really need to take a quick makeover. This small makeup box will give you an instant solution and give you the confidence to look good.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>10. Body Spray:</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can\'t smell bad, or after a long journey, your body deodorant won\'t deliver the perfect result. So, as your concern, carrying a body spray will give an ultra-belief from the inside. When you apply body fragrance to smell good, it will cover the areas of body parts. So, this beauty product should be on your travel list.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Why-do-Beauty-Essentials-need-to-Carry-in-a-journey.jpg\" alt=\"Why do Beauty Essentials need to Carry in a journey\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why do Beauty Essentials need to Carry in a journey?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Most of the items are belong to use every day. Some are used apparently but very useful for long day trips. Each item has a different purpose to use, and you can\'t leave those while you are on a journey to unknown places. Especially when you go climbing mountains, or near to a lake picnic or safari of the jungle, you can\'t get those necessary items to buy instantly. Even for an abroad visit, buying those beauty goods can be much expensive. So, getting a smooth and hassle-free trip, carrying those essentials is really helpful. But remember to take only the vital things along with you and, if possible, maintain a small pouch for those items to keep them arranged.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Last Words:</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a regular traveller, one may carry those beauty items with them for care for yourself. Almost all beauty elements from the above list are essential to hold as a caring partner for you. So, when you are going somewhere, you can keep those items on the priority list.</p>', NULL, 'Best Beauty Essentials Products Everyone Should Have in Travel Bag', 'You should bring those things. Here, we list some of the best beauty essentials products everyone should have in their travel bag collections. Let\'s briefly discuss those items that, why those products are essentials to put in your cart.', '010821-110828.jpeg', NULL, '2021-08-01 03:59:28', '2021-08-22 03:03:31'),
(31, 7, 'Importance of Soft Tissue Remedial Massage in Real Life', 'importance-of-soft-tissue-remedial-massage-in-real-life', 4, 'Here, we describe some essential information about remedial gentle tissue massage and why soothing tissue massage is important for human life.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Remedial massage is beneficial to repair dysfunction of the soft tissues or musculoskeletal imbalance for any age. This massage technique is mainly used for athletics and to get quick recovery from minor injuries like muscle pain, sore legs, shoulder execution, and more common body aching. There are plenty of categories in remedial massage; one of the most effective and most commonly used massage skills is soft tissue therapy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This is a common form of massage that improves the muscle immunity system and helps heal the reserved body tissues under the sessions. It is reasonable to take the soft tissue remedial massage on a fixed schedule under the limitations and body requirements. Here, we describe some essential information about remedial gentle tissue massage and why soothing tissue massage is important for human life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Importance-of-Soft-Tissue-Remedial-Massage-in-Real-Life.jpg\" alt=\"Importance of Soft Tissue Remedial Massage in Real Life\" width=\"600\" height=\"589\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is Soft Tissue Remedial Massage?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Soft tissue therapy is a former remedial massage technique used to treat the strained body muscles, sports injuries, and ligaments parts under some conditions. The core idea of this massage is to enhance the deep tissue of musculoskeletal balance and help to perform minor injured healing sessions. A deep tissue massage targets the deep layers of muscle nerves and the surrounding cells. This massage therapy gradually gives relief from back posture, nerves flexibility and helps recover from the sore and weak muscles. The technique has a different perspective and requirements to apply based on the body\'s demand. Many professional therapists provide these facilities and have their own therapy Center. Also, some RTOs offers diploma courses in Remedial massage and RPL certificates under some conditions. Those courses are for experienced therapists and to learn more about physical assessments in a particular segment of deep tissue massage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What-is Soft-Tissue-Remedial-Massage.jpg\" alt=\"What is Soft Tissue Remedial Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Benefits of Soft Tissue Remedial Massage</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Soft tissue massage has an outstanding advantage to keep your physical and mental health in the proper lines. There are several technologies available for different purposes and requirements according to the receiver\'s prescription. Here some of the real benefits are given below.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Stress Relieve:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From a soft tissue massage, one can get great relief from the whole day\'s stress instantly. This massage will help to control cortisol levels and increase the oxytocin amount in the body. Also, this massage shuts down your head pain and helps to relax the tight muscles.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Reduce Body pain:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To relieve instant pain, one can apply this massage technique from any massage center. Using soft tissue massage will give assistance to reduce bodice pain and any kind of muscle injured as a plain solution.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Benefits-of-Soft-Tissue-Remedial-Massage.jpg\" alt=\"Benefits of Soft Tissue Remedial Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Lowers Blood Pressure and Heart Rate:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A soft massage will help to release the body tighten and allow the body cells to balance good blood pressure. It will comfort the body tissues, especially for low blood pressure patients, and increase a good monitoring heart rate.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"4\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h3><strong>Reduces of Arthritis Symptoms: </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Soft tissue remedial massage is very effective in reducing arthritis from thew diseases, stiffness, particular joints pain, and common sleep issues by alleviating pain. Deep tissue rub can moderate the pressure to lower the arthritis pain and tension to make it easier to move around.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"5\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h3><strong>Rehabilitates Injured Muscles:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For recurrent injuries, stretching tight or twisted the muscles can also make smooth the movement of toxins from the muscles. The practice of deep tissue massage will assist the rehabilitation of injured muscles and release the pain to heal quickly.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"6\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Pregnancy:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">At the time of pregnancy, women need lots of exercise to overcome the consequences of the pain and a smooth going for delivering a baby. To deal with prior labor pain, prenatal soft tissue massage is a great form to take rest and let the muscle relax due to pregnancy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"7\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Sleep Improvement:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When one gets a daily massage and does the proper exercise on soft tissue development, it will give great feedback on sleep. It will also improve the sleep amount and provide a healthy outcome over time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"8\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h3><strong>Improve Oxygen Flow:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Applying soft tissue massage will improve the inner strength to breathe more. It will open the tissues to balance oxygen inside the body cells and let all the body function to work fluently.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"9\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h3><strong>Improved Flexibility:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boosting more body flexibility and making an outstanding result in improving lymphatic circulation and drainage to improve flexibility and range of motion in the area of the scar tissue. It will furnish the body cords and stretch the muscle fiber to promote more flexibility.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"10\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Chronic Muscle Strains:</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Soft remedial massage helps improve body tissue development and is a helpful way to get relief from chronic muscle strains. This massage therapy gives more elasticity and stimulates the tendon issues to re-establish the proper function.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/side-effects-of-Soft-Tissue-Massage.jpg\" alt=\"side effects of Soft Tissue Massage\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Are there any side effects of Soft Tissue Massage?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the age, body establishment, physical conditions, or any other body injuries can hit some unusual incidents or physical difficulties. In most cases, people don\'t meet any significant issues from soft tissue massage, but neglecting this part can be a serious problem. Basically, everybody doesn\'t have the same growing anatomy, and sometimes body parts can refuse to accept this technique under the circumstance. Though this therapy is generally safe and has a low risk of harm to implement by professionals, it may not be safe for everyone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>List of Side Effects in Soft Tissue Massage</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Blood clotting disorder can have nose bleeding.</li>\r\n<li>The risk of injury, such as bone fractures.</li>\r\n<li>Serious nerve injury for low stem body.</li>\r\n<li>Serious injuries can hit older age people.</li>\r\n<li>Any recent surgery or chemotherapy should avoid</li>\r\n<li>Big wounds or skin conditions can backfire.</li>\r\n<li>It can cause a hernia or any trauma inside the inner organs.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Bottom Lines</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In research, deep tissue massage also helps people with Sports injuries, Reduction of fibromyalgia, Plantar fasciitis, High blood pressure, Sciatica, joint pain, Decreases muscle spasms, and cramping too. Before heading towards the therapy center, experts say it is good to make a doctor appointment for a general check-up. Otherwise, there might cause careless accidents and let you lay on the bed for months.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Importance of Soft Tissue Remedial Massage in Real Life', 'Here, we describe some essential information about remedial gentle tissue massage and why soothing tissue massage is important for human life.', 'importance-of-soft-tissue-remedial-massage-in-real-life.png', NULL, '2021-08-02 12:33:44', '2022-01-16 08:56:31'),
(32, 7, 'Top 11 Modern Makeup Trends for Your Preference in 2022', 'top-11-modern-makeup-trends-for-your-preference-in-2022', 3, 'Considering your trendy demand, we listed some of the most iconic and recent preference makeup creations for you.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In this current generation of style and beauty appeal, women are becoming much more attractive with trendy makeup ideas. They are using various types of beauty products to look bold and stunning with the trend. They even spend hours doing those makeovers and spring the money to buy those required items. To look outstanding on social media or for self-integration with the flow, girls are now adapting multi-experiments on their looks and giving shots on creative makeup ideas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a girl, if you want to go with the present trend and change your makeup appearances, you better have the acknowledgment about the newest forms of modern makeup trends. So, considering your trendy demand, we listed some of the most iconic and recent preference makeup creations for you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Modern-Makeup-Trends-for-Your-Preference.jpg\" alt=\"Modern Makeup Trends for Your Preference\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Some Modern Makeup Trends for Girls</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Smoldering Eyeliner </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Girls are finding more interest in their eye art as a trend of the makeover. Especially, smoldering the eye make with eyeliner to shade or give a smoky filter in the upper part of the eye. This kind of art is now really ongoing swing instead of taking only the traditional black eyeliner look. Some use wet-lined color eyeliner to have a supreme look depending on the tastes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Topsy-Turvy Eyes </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Most female celebrities are now including Topsy-Turvy Eyes as the trendiest and fun-looking makeup. This cross-eye makeup is now very popular among teenagers and models. In this form, two eyeshadows are included for your upper and lower eyes lids. Flipping and reversing the colors on opposite eyes gives a gradient look or chooses contrasting tones like professional outlooks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Light Glow Skin </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nowadays, a new trend is not to use any artificial makeover on facial skin. For a quick setup and to get ready, most girls are now contracting with this latest flow to use a light makeover or no makeup. Focusing on having a fresh and glowing look, they apply facial massage, natural glow creams, sun-protected masks, and many related beauty products to cover a natural shine.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Multicolor-Eyes-girls.jpg\" alt=\"Multicolor Eyes GIrl\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"4\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Multicolor Eyes </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the most combined arts of makeup is Multicolor lashes and liners to bold your eyelids. People are accepting this rainbow art as the most ironic trend of 2021. But you can&rsquo;t just apply this as regular makeup because it&rsquo;s too flashy and over highlights. Using the lavender and technicolor on the eyelids are one of the kinds of Multicolor trend among girls.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"5\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Classic Cat Eye </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The classic cat-eye makeup is the oldest eyelids artwork from the 90&rsquo;s trend, but recently this format got a new platform among today&rsquo;s generation. Using a black liquid liner, strip a line, draw a long dash to the upper lids, and bold the brows with the extra-long color lashes. Some use deep colors to make it more vibrant and neutral-color to visual a glam appearance.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"6\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Colored Mascara </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You may have seen color eyebrows, Multi hues of eyeliners, and different shades of eye lens also. But in 2021, one of the newest experimental makeups forms is using colored mascara to your eyelashes. With your open eyes, you can&rsquo;t notify those quickly, but those are now the most trendy eyes makeup on Instagram and other popular media.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"7\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Cherry Red Lipstick </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before the &rsquo;90s, there was a popular trend among the female fashion icon to wear dark cherry red lipstick. Now those trends are again rephrasing into the modern beauty world. Not only red shades but also multiple colors lipsticks get the chance to perform. These bold terms of intense lipstick shades give formatting looks without putting any gorgeous makeup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"8\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Stained Lip Color </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Totally a new version of lip art for applying shadow color on your lips. The terms of stained lip designs come from the Chinese lip technique. Girls from Europe and Asia are getting used to using this fashion from the last years to now. Though it is still trendy without professionals, you can&rsquo;t make it perfect. Always regular and bold colors don&rsquo;t match the skin tone as a thing of beauty.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"9\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Starry Lids </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From the trend of cosplay, many girls now involve in such starry lids. This makeup trend has a vibe of cosplay and creates a unique eyelid look with a DIY star or glitters. Using bright shining stars to the inner and outer corners of the eyes. But be careful while you are sticking those tiny loads up to your eyes; any misconduct can cause you seriously injured.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Glossy-Eyes-and-Lips.jpg\" alt=\"Glossy Eyes and Lips\" width=\"300\" height=\"450\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"10\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Glossy Eyes and Lips </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Some girls are entirely obsessed with the newest makeup trend of glossy eyes and lip makeovers in 2021. Just using neutral cream color on your eyes lid and let the lips with wet lip gloss. Often those light shades are pretty expensive, but girls find them more convenient to apply. Even you can use them on your cheekbones for a more top outlook.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"11\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Dolphin Skin </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dolphin skin is known as the alternative to glass skin and wet skin. For bare-faced makeup, adopting a soggy foundation reflects your skin tone, and it helps to glow your cutis. Without having the proper practice, you can&rsquo;t do it at your home. Only professional and makeup artists can give a great result on Dolphine skin makeup. Moreover, with a dewy highlighter, the rest of your look can consist of simple makeup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion: </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the following list of makeup trend, you can choose any of them and try at your home. But make sure you got expert tutorials from YouTube and learn the techniques accurately. Make some research on them to know whether any of them is harmful to you or not. Apply professionally recommended products and always check the date before buying.</p>', NULL, 'Modern Makeup Trends for Your Preference', 'Considering your trendy demand, we listed some of the most iconic and recent preference makeup creations for you.', '040821-070855.jpeg', NULL, '2021-08-04 11:02:55', '2022-01-30 05:45:12'),
(33, 7, '8 Best Haircutting Tips for Women and How to Practice the Haircut at Home', 'best-haircutting-tips-for-women-and-how-to-practice-the-haircut-at-home', 5, 'Here, you will learn some of the basic tips and details about haircuts at home without any expert hands.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getting a haircut at a saloon in this Covid pandemic is a callous decision. Moreover, most of the beauty salons are now closed because of current health issues. So, you cannot visit the parlor and make a perfect haircut from professionals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">By staying at home, your hair heads are getting longer and not growing in a perfect shape. Thinking of a haircut at home can bring a miserable situation. It is not easy to cut your own hair or from any unprofessional person. Even trying at Home from YouTube tutorial or without a haircut course can be troublesome to adjust your hairstyle.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Primary while, you may end with the worst nightmare with a haircut experiment. But don\'t get upset too soon. Having a great and perfect haircut at home, you can follow up on some cutting methods and tricks. Here, you will learn some of the basic tips and details about haircuts at home without any expert hands.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Best Hair Cutting Tips for Women at Home </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Depend on Face Shape</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering your face shape and contrast of the head size, you may choose your haircut. Google for some of the trendy haircuts according to your face size and color tones. You can put a round, square, or straight hair cut on what you feel like doing. By observing your chin bone, and face structure, go for your suitable cut.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>For Sports Woman</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are a sportswoman, you need to remember that having long hair will be great trouble for participating in-game. It can distract you in the field. Having a short haircut or a round bang cut will be the perfect choice for you. Don\'t worry about an expert cut; you can do a round neck cut with a trimmer at home.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/How-to-Practice-Haircut-at-Home.jpg\" alt=\" How to Practice the Haircut at Home\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Depending on Age </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don\'t adopt any kind of hairstyle which may not be appropriated according to your age. For a schoolgirl, having a color hair or undercut hair won\'t be very acceptable. A simple square cut is best for them to apply while they are at their limited age. Up to that, you can restyle anything that you want to do with your hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Texture And Hair Types </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are different hair types and textures that may not be acceptable for choosing any hairstyles. Like, wide straight hair, dry curly hair, tightly curled, wavy, or pumped hair. By understanding your type, you need to find your ideal style. It is not wise to add verities haircuts every time you shirk your hair at home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Section Your Hair </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you have long hair, then separate the hair into sections according to the hair cut goal. It is always best to section no matter what cut you are performing. Even at home, you will need hair clamps to hold your hair sections for adjusting the hairstyle. Now chop the parts step by step according to the form.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cut Vertically </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After doing the parallel cut, you may find it challenging to make some vertical hair chopping off your own. One of the easiest solutions is to comb out with small sections and clamp it with your two fingers for taking some upright shots. You do not require to cut much with just a few light snips will make you look good.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ask for Styling Advice </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You are staying at home and looking for a haircut to look good on you. But the covid situation is not allowing you to have a visit to the saloon. Now you are just thinking to give an outstanding hair look all by yourself and not demolish the look. Then following expert tips or professional hairdresser advice will provide the best preferences on styling haircuts at home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Forehead Length </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Measuring your forehead length, you should select your hair design. If you have a large forehead, then giving a bang cut will hide the upper area. Also, for a small head, let the things go lighten and soft. So, the bangs do not completely cover your face and make a face look smaller.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Basic Hair Cutting Essentials Needed at Home</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Spray bottles</strong>: At least one spray bottle needs to keep containing fresh water on the desk.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Combs:</strong> It is best to have three different lengths of fine-tooth combs and use them according to the need.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Scissors</strong>: For best haircuts, you should hold 2/3 scissors based on the hair length and shape.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Two Mirrors:</strong> You will need one mirror for the front side and one portable mirror for back observation.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Blow Dryer:</strong> Use a blow dryer after you shampoo your hair, and don\'t remain your hair wet.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hairbrush:</strong> After cutting hair, you have to swape your head with a fine hair brush to clean your remaining hair.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hair Clamps:</strong> There, you may need several hair clamps to clip your hair for the best structure to hold your hair.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><strong>How do you give a woman a haircut? </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ans: Rely on the hair art, always prefer an expert hairdresser for a woman\'s haircut because styling a woman\'s hair is not a joke.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Is it better to cut women\'s hair wet or dry? </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ans: It is always best to have a cut while the hair remains wet or dry, depending on the hair types and tolerances.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Do women cut their hair at home? </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ans: Usually, they don\'t do any exclusive experiments at home. But every three months, most of them give a slight touch-up at home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Which hair cutting is best for the girl? </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ans: Round faces are suitable for chubby and round faces. Also, if you have an oval face, you can pull a straight cut considering your chin bones.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Summing-Up</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you think you want to apply some celebrity haircut at home, please stop there because you can\'t make it like them as those are forged by highly professional hair stylizes. But you can make some simple moves to style your hair from the house. Maybe it will take forever to perfect the haircut, but maintaining some basic stuff will help you to reduce the efforts. Some up-trending hair designs can be applicable at home if you make some reasonable attempts and practice the following tips for the perfect results.</p>', NULL, 'Best Haircutting Tips for Women, How to Practice the Haircut at Home', 'Here, you will learn some of the basic tips and details about haircuts at home without any expert hands.', '090821-060824.jpeg', NULL, '2021-08-09 10:32:24', '2021-08-12 08:20:36');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(34, 7, 'The 10 Best Beauty Tips and Recommended Products to Take Care of Dry Skin', 'beauty-tips-and-recommended-products-to-take-care-of-dry-skin', 6, 'Let\'s discuss some best beauty tips and recommended products by experts to take care of your dry skin every season.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As time passes, global warming and the greenhouse effects are affecting the natural collision and caused human skin dryness at a high rate. The changes of nature let you struggle with your skin problems and moisture losses. As the climate got a variation in temperatures, your healthy skin can actually get a non-suitable position under the circumstances, which result, skin dryness, facial dull, lips cracking, hair damage, eyelids complexity, and the worst situation arises over time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the environmental changes, you have to work hard with your skincare and need to take a proper treatment based on the skin tone. Naturally, your skin produces oil to moisturize and help to protect from skin dry. Based on the season, you have to understand your skin need and let them recover with some extra efforts at home. Because skincare treatment at a beauty clinic is very expensive, so, following the context, let\'s discuss some best beauty tips and recommended products by experts to take care of your dry skin every season.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Top Best Beauty Tips To Take Care of Your Dry Skin</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use Warm Water </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Always try to use warm water to wash your face and the outer part of the body. Applying lukewarm water will keep your skin hydrated and give a refreshing line into the facial pigmentation. But the water shouldn\'t be hot as it burns the skin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Apply Moisturizer to Skin </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Make moisturizing exercise a part of your daily skincare routine. There are plenty of options to moisturize your skin with artificial moisturizing cream or via natural ingredients to apply. Especially, switch to an oatmeal moisturizer when you have dry, itchy, and sensitive skin.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Best Beauty Tips.jpg\" alt=\"Best Beauty Tips\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Care for Morning and Night </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maintain a proper routine will help you out from dryness from the facial skin. Like, you are applying a suitable night care cream or your everyday beauty essentials before step out from home will let you glow if you can do a daily practice.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Avoid Using Anti-Aging Products </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anti-aging products can be harmful to use at your pick ages. Without a beauty expert recommendation, it is best to avoid ultra-drying products containing high radical elements and non-suited chemicals for all ages.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Care to Take Sun Protections </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In summer, applying sunscreen or a heat-protected mask can be dangerous for soft and Sensitive Skin. From getting rid of such heavy extension of sun heat, you can adapt any suitable skincare products or facial masks according to the need.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use a Light Exfoliating Scrub</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lots of people think scrubbing is a great solution to remove oil, dust, and pollution. But scrub with rough fabrics or body scrubber can damage the facial tissues as those are very soft and sensitive. So, always use a exfoliate scrubber for gentle nourishing.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Keep Lip Balm into Bag </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dry lips can be pretty much bothering in the summertime and also in winter. Suffering from lip crack pain can be a big deal to bear. To prevent this, using lip balm with hyaluronic acid can be a good solution. So, never leave your cream or lip gloss at home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use skin formulated Makeup</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In many cases, beauty makeup items do not blend with the facial condition, and it became harsh for the skin. Radiant finish makeup units are good for dry skin. So before applying any makeup goods, read all the cautions and about the products whether it goes with your skin or not.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Drink plenty of water </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boost your inner body cells and help them to hydrate naturally according to the body\'s capacity. The natural hydration process can assist the body skin more moisturizing from inside of the skin layers. So, drink a minimum amount of water to keep the right nutrients and antioxidants to protect and nourish.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Best Products to Take Care of Dry Skin.jpeg\" alt=\"Best Products to Take Care of Dry Skin\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Some Other Important Rules </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Check out eye repair complexity or allergenic issues.</li>\r\n<li>Get some modern exercise or facial massage daily.</li>\r\n<li>Consume seasonal fresh fruits and vegetables following a diet chart.</li>\r\n<li>Change the shower Time to less and use quality body shampoo.</li>\r\n<li>Avoid products with salicylic acid and hard chemicals.</li>\r\n<li>Cover your skin appropriately during Winter and Summer seasons.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Best Products to Take Care of Dry Skin</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Aloe Vera Gel.jpeg\" alt=\"Aloe Vera Gel\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aloe Vera Gel </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Applying aloe vera gel to your face after toning will help soothe and nourish your skin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rose Calming Cleanser </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The transparent rose cleanser works on the skin with its gentle formula, calming and nitrifying.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Apply Hyaluronic Acid Serum </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">keep your body skin hydrated, upper-plump, and more luminous by using a hyaluronic acid serum.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Creamy Avocado Mask </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Avocado masks are packed with vitamin E, a potent antioxidant and moisturizer which improves skin health and reduces dryness.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Natural Olive Oil.jpeg\" alt=\"Natural Olive Oil\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Natural Olive Oil and Sugar Scrub </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Use olive or coconut oil daily to moisturize before heading for bed. Also, gently rub the sugar scrub into your skin, and then wash it off to reduce dark/white cells.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use Oil-Based Makeup </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dry skin can\'t afford to take the heavy glumes of Makeup. It\'s best to use oil-laminate Makeup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Take Omega-3s And Vitamin E </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Omega-3 fatty acids and vitamin E supplements are loaded with anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use Milk Compresses for Irritated Skin </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Applying milk compressors for 5 to 10 minutes at a time on your skin is very helpful for improving the irritation of itchy skin.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Homemade Oatmeal Honey Mask.jpeg\" alt=\"Homemade Oatmeal Honey Mask\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Homemade Oatmeal Honey Mask </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can create an easy oatmeal soak with honey and rice powder. Oatmeal moisturizers mask lend to soothe and calm inflamed skin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Summary </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Extra care is needed for your sensitive skin to keep it youthful and more moisturized as you love your skin and do not want to get dry, chapped, and rash skin. Then you can go for a daily schedule to do some beauty therapy all by yourself at home. With some easy steps, you can protect your soft and glowing skin at its best. Besides, modern pigmentation treatment can be very hassle and inconvenience. So, following the beauty tips charts, cleaning the top layer of dead skin cells will make it easier to expose newer healthier-looking skin. All the mentioned tips are from professional beauty therapists, so you can go through the dry skin process and shine with your confidence.</p>', 'Best Beauty Tips To Take Care of Your Dry Skin, Best Products to Take Care of Dry Skin', 'Best Beauty Tips To Take Care of Your Dry Skin', 'Let\'s discuss some best beauty tips and recommended products by experts to take care of your dry skin every season.', 'best-beauty-tips-to-take-care-of-your-dry-skin.jpeg', NULL, '2021-08-19 03:43:54', '2021-08-23 03:54:27'),
(35, 7, 'How to Develop a Good Career as A Beauty Therapist in Australia?', 'how-to-develop-a-good-career-as-a-beauty-therapist', 6, 'Let’s get to know more about those exciting areas of beauty therapy where you have a long and how to develop a good career as a beauty therapist.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Are you thinking of becoming a beauty artist in your area? Well, there are plenty of sectors where you can improve your skills as a therapist in the beauty industry. However, you might be wonder which career sector will be very proficient according to your passion for the beauty industry?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In Australia, one of the demanding and promising careers is a beauty therapist. Now, if you have such qualifications or work experience then, you have already moved one stair ahead from the others. But before this, you need to understand whether you can be a successor or not. Some common facts that arise about what are the essential components/ skills need to consider? And what are the available section opened for you to grow your career in the beauty industry?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Along with the proper study and training, you can bloom this passion to your best-growing career easily. So, let&rsquo;s get to know more about those exciting areas of beauty therapy where you have a long and exciting profession.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Skills Require to Become A Beauty Therapist.jpg\" alt=\"Skills Require to Become A Beauty Therapist\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Top 10 Reasons to Grow Your Career as A Beauty Therapist </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Variety of Options</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Presuming you have a minimum work experience in the beauty sector, you will get alternatives to choose your best interest. Now, about 8% of total women in Australia are adapting this career for a full-time job. Over time, you don&rsquo;t want to be in the same position and may not wish to carry the same thing over and over. Then you can choose different categories for a perfect career choice at any time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>People are The Clients</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a beauty therapist, you have to be cautious about beauty services. Because all the clients are adult people, and most of them are women. So, giving the best benefits is your prime responsibility under conditions and terms. You don&rsquo;t need to worry about the income result as people are showing interested in taking such beauty services.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Choose Your Profession</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As we get to know, there are various options to blend yourself into the beauty industry as a therapist. Nowadays, lots of people are opening their own therapist spas and beauty salons in Australia. So, not just to look for a therapist job, you also have the most considerable option to build a career as an entrepreneur of a beauty therapist Center.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wages Earning</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Usually, a full-time Beauty Therapist earns an average of $650 per week, and over the year, it may turn around $33,800 on average per year. The wage varies depending on the job location/state, employer position, current experience, and overtime issues. But you can income a good amount of fixed salary or earn more than average over the growth of relevant industrial experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Job Outlook Statistics.jfif\" alt=\"Job Outlook Statistics\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>*Source: </strong>Job Outlook Government website.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Work schedule</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You may get hired as part-time assistance in most places if you don&rsquo;t have much experience in this section. But the work schedule is very comfortable and relaxing, including 9-5 working hours, two days of the weekend, evenings, and out-of-hours work lines under the company\'s policies. Around 39% of people are doing a part-time job and have an excellent opportunity to add in the remaining percentage as a full-time job in Beauty Therapy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/What are Beauty Therapist Responsibilities.jpg\" alt=\"What are Beauty Therapist Responsibilities\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Job Security</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Like, all the other job modules, employees always keep worried about the job provision. But depending on the estimations, the beauty industries are growing fast, and the workers expect better shelter as their job security. Even the previous experience will lead you to a good position from one beauty zone to another one.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Job Excitement</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">What if you have a great chance to carry out your passion into your career. It is possible to pursue your beauty interest and earn an RPL qualification in Certificate III in Beauty Services or a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy at any RTO institution. It might be best to get employment in any beauty specialist center.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Minimum Skills range</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Excellent interpersonal skills are necessary to develop your career line as a beauty specialist. Also, communication expertise needs to be broader for personal attribution. Administration skills are including appointment framework, record-keeping, and bill handling, are advantageous in the job.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>No Gender Discrimination</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">About 97% of females are engaging in these career prospects. Rest is considering the male involvement in this demanding job area. With the accomplishment of the required eligibility and qualification, anyone can get the golden opportunity to start a career in the beauty industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Upgrowing Industry</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Overall, the number is enormous, and there were approximately 31,000 Beauty Therapists in the prior ten years. Also, the number of workers is expected to grow moderately over the next five years is likely to reach 33,400 holders by 2025 in Australia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/ABS Labour Force Survey.jfif\" alt=\"ABS Labour Force Survey\" width=\"521\" height=\"347\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>*Source:</strong> According to ABS Labour Force Survey, seasonally adjusted data to November 2020 and National Skills Commission Employment Projections to 2025.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Skills Requirements: </strong><strong>How to Develop a Good Career as A Beauty Therapist?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To become a beauty therapist, you should have some qualifications or either have to complete training courses on beauty therapy and RPL certificates or a relevant BTEC or NVQ license.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Related skills </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Communication</li>\r\n<li>Interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Patience development</li>\r\n<li>Administration skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Related subjects </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Art</li>\r\n<li>Business studies</li>\r\n<li>Any relevant beauty courses</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Essential qualifications </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>RPL Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy (SHB40115)</li>\r\n<li>Apprenticeship in beauty therapy BTEC or NVQ license.</li>\r\n<li>Diploma in Beauty Therapy (SHB50115)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Sector for A Beauty Therapist.jpg\" alt=\"Sector for A Beauty Therapist\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><strong>What are Beauty Therapist Responsibilities?</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Related job responsibilities and tasks;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>As a therapist, you need to discuss client needs, analyze skin characteristics, and advise proper skincare procedures and make-up application.</li>\r\n<li>They have the responsibility to apply the general cosmetic and perform the facial or remedial massage.</li>\r\n<li>Also, you have to perform manicures and pedicures, including decorative nail art, adding artificial nails, broken nail repairing, and other specialized body treatments.</li>\r\n<li>To Remove the facial or body hair through safe techniques of bleaching, tinting, depilation, waxing, or electrolysis.</li>\r\n<li>Need to evaluate beauty therapy processes and products on client demands.</li>\r\n<li>Keep the bookings, arranging appointments, financial transactions, and maintaining client records.</li>\r\n<li>They provide consultants and advice on recommended cosmetic products.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'How to Develop a Good Career as A Beauty Therapist', 'How to Develop a Good Career as A Beauty Therapist', 'Let’s get to know more about those exciting areas of beauty therapy where you have a long and how to develop a good career as a beauty therapist.', 'how-to-develop-a-good-career-as-a-beauty-therapist.jpg', NULL, '2021-08-24 10:58:53', '2022-01-16 10:07:34'),
(36, 7, 'How to Become a Successful Hairdressing Teacher in Australia? ', 'how-to-become-a-successful-hairdressing-teacher-in-australia', NULL, 'We try to cover all the essential information about the hairdressing teaching profession and the vital requirement that may need to become a good hairdresser instructor.   ', '<p>Are you in a hairdresser profession? And you are just doing great in your hairdressing career. Loving this occupation now, you might want to expand this profession into something big, like opening a hair art academy or become a hairdresser instructor. Well, thinking of such a dream, first, you must decide what you want to become as a hairdresser? An independent HairArt educator or a brand ambassador for a product company? Or just build a hairdresser academy on your own.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you think you are ready and eligible to cover all the responsibilities under a solo act. Then you need to know what the requirements and qualifications are essential to becoming a hairdresser teacher or instructor. This article also acknowledges how to become a successful hairdressing teacher and commit to corporate culture\'s perks and limitations. Let\'s get started with career requirements.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/How do I become a hairdressing teacher in Australia.jpg\" alt=\"How do I become a hairdressing teacher in Australia\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Career Requirements as A Hair Stylists Instructor&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For a professional hair styling proctor, post-secondary training in hairdressing or cosmetology is highly recommended. Along with that, the local authorized licenses are also required to build a smooth line in the hairdresser profession as they need to be creative and should have good communication and relational skills to attract clients/ students. Also, one should have the ability to run the business under any circumstances. To expect hair expertise, the required candidates should know about manual hair equipment and be capable of handling multi-electronic items that are regularly used for hairdressing purposes. Of course, as a professional hairdresser, you may need to understand the customer\'s demands and serve them according to their preferences and requests. Other necessary courses and qualifications are mandatory to acquire the instructed certificates, and following some steps, you may count as one of the best hairdressers in your area.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.payscale.com/research/AU/Job=Hairdresser_%2F_Hairstylist/Hourly_Rate\">PayScale</a> data, the average annual salary is almost AUD 56,000 plus for a professional hairdresser instructor in Australia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>What are The Basic hairstylist and Cosmetology Instructor Tasks?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The essential required or assigned tasks are not the same as a hairstyling teacher. Each profession has a different criterion to follow, but, in most cases, you can become a cosmology instruction from being a hairdresser. However, to become a successful hair instructor, you may do all the hairstylist jobs and add other additional tasks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>As a Hairdressing Teacher, you have to,&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Coach students about basic hairstyling methods and ins-outs of the hairdressing industry.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Build new followers and polish quality service standards into the batch of your academy to teach them hair arts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Monitor, review and assess candidates regularly to meet the conditions of awarding and funding bodies and ensure learners make progress expected.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Plan individual learning to meet learner needs and ensure lesson plans and resources are prepared before learners attending.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Contribute to the \'Self-Assessment Process\' by working within the standard inspection framework guidelines like assisting them with inspections, tests, and evaluations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Check out student levels by understanding and adjusting the instructions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Teach students standard procedures and maintenance of their space and equipment base on the hairdressing processes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What qualifications do you need to be a hairdressing lecturer.jpg\" alt=\"What qualifications do you need to be a hairdressing lecturer?\" width=\"600\" height=\"509\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>How to Become a Successful Hairdressing Teacher in Australia?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://study.com/articles/Become_a_Professional_Hair_Styling_Instructor_Requirements_and_Info.html\">Source:</a></span><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Complete An Approved Cosmetology Program&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On the first step, all you need to confirm about your regular hairdressing program. In general, an associate degree or qualified certificate is required to earn from a community or technical art school. Like many states in Australia, there is a high restriction of age counting. But some open courses are available for high school students or equivalent qualification programs. Within two or less time, you can complete an entire method of cosmetology program where you will get hair expert lectures and practical on-campus training with multiple skills developments in hair design and treatment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Get A Cosmetology License&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Although in every state of Australia has additional verifications and authorized systems. Maintaining those hairdressing programs, you need to spend some time during the training season daily. After completing the cosmetology license program, you must attend a mock test and successfully pass the license exam. You have to participate in exams in a written format and also including practical or oral presentations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Get Work Experience&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to the policy, the functional requirements are mandatory to get qualified as an instructor. Usually, 3-5 years of experience are mandatory to apply for the position. Once you got the hairdressing license, your portfolio needs to attend some of the work experience in the hairstyling industry as you are a licensed hairdresser, so it will be a significant step for you to become a hairdresser instructor.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Complete a Cosmetology Instructor Program&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Generally, most organizations don\'t hire a cosmetology artist as a hairdresser instructor, just considering the working experience. They are also required for the permitted license of the cosmetology instructor qualification program. The curriculum for an instructor program includes courses adjustments such as teaching theory, class management, motivation, evaluation methods, practical teaching, and fair curriculum design.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Get a Cosmetology Instructor License&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Finally, get the cosmetology proctor license after finishing the instructor program. Here you need to entail to complete an approved education program and lead a successful exam operation. However, few organizations don\'t require an experienced instructor. With just a cosmetology license and prior hairdresser experience, you can continue as a fresh cosmetologist and instructor or open your hairdressing academy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/What qualifications do you need to open a hairdressing academy.jpg\" alt=\"What qualifications do you need to open a hairdressing academy\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>What qualifications do you need to open a hairdressing academy?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://ctccourses.org/help-advice/what-qualifications-do-i-need-to-open-a-hairdressing-academy/\">Source:</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Level 3 Award in Education &amp; Training (PTLLS)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Level 3 Certificate in Assessing Vocational Achievement Qualification (CAVA)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Award in the Internal Quality Assurance of Assessment Processes and Practice&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>RPL Certificate III in Hairdressing (SHB30416)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusion&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To bloom in the hairdressing profession, becoming a hairdressing teacher is a respectful and most successful career. Experienced instructors may seek opportunities for advancement as senior educators or hairdressing school managers. Some may think to open their own cosmetology school too. But becoming a lecturer or guest proctor as a hairdresser instructor is not easy at the initial stage. So, here, we try to cover all the essential information about the hairdressing teaching profession and the vital requirement that may need to become a good hairdresser instructor.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', 'How to Become a Successful Hairdressing Teacher in Australia', 'How to Become a Successful Hairdressing Teacher in Australia', 'we try to cover all the essential information about the hairdressing teaching profession and the vital requirement that may need to become a good hairdresser instructor.', 'how-to-become-a-successful-hairdressing-teacher-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2021-09-05 10:27:59', '2021-09-05 10:36:43'),
(37, 7, 'Top 7 Reasons: Why is Beauty Therapy a Good Career in Australia?', 'why-is-beauty-therapy-a-good-career-in-australia', NULL, 'Considering the overall employment demand on beauty therapy, you may wonder to know, what is beauty therapy? Or what is a beauty therapist\'s salary? And why is beauty therapy a good career in Australia?', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose you are obsessed with beauty proficiency and ready to make your passion into a promising career in Australia. Then becoming a beauty therapist is an excellent option for you to shine. Nowadays, the beauty therapy industry has gotten an extreme career choice to set a safe and secure living profession. Especially in this beauty industry, there is a massive demand for creative beauty artists and professional individuals who have the proper knowledge and qualification degree in beauty sectors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Even you can become a beauty advisor with your working experience if you have any. To have a kick-start career, women are adopting these job opportunities in many states of Australia. Also, some are starting their beauty therapy Centers and saloons to offer hair treatments and beauty services.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the overall employment demand on beauty therapy, you may wonder to know, what is beauty therapy? Or what is a beauty therapist\'s salary? And why is beauty therapy a good career in Australia? Let\'s go a little extensive to understand more about a booming career in the beauty therapy industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/What is Beauty Therapist.jpg\" alt=\"What is Beauty Therapist\" width=\"511\" height=\"346\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is Beauty Therapist?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A cosmetology or therapist is a person who has specific knowledge and specialties on the application of beauty therapy treatment. Branches of specialty include hairstyling, skincare, cosmetics, manicures/pedicures, non-permanent hair removal such as waxing and sugaring, and permanent hair removal processes such as electrologist and intense pulsed light (IPL). All those job responsibilities should be maintained to grow or become a beauty therapist. They are well trained and certified to perform cosmetic treatments to the hair, skin, and nails.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Career Opportunities in </strong><strong>Beauty Industry:</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the beauty industry is dynamic, growing, and recession-proof career, so thinking of the career growth, the beauty industry has multiple access in the specialized sector. From personal beauty specialists to various therapy counsellors, all are part of the beauty therapy industry. Also, they are experts in skincare and open to performing best practices on beauty treatments. Here is the list of some available career growth opportunities in the beauty therapy industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100.513%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 49.4253%;\" width=\"301\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Personal Stylist/ Assistance&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Makeup Artist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Fashion Show Stylist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Film, Theatre, Television&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Editorial/Advertising Stylist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Educator/Platform Artist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Medical Aesthetician</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 110.181%;\" width=\"301\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hair Removal Specialist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Beauty Blogger/Influencer&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Spa Aesthetician/Manager/Owner&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Eyelash and Brow Specialist&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Cosmetic Counter&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Artistic Director&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Hair, Makeup and Skin Specialty Retailers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why is Beauty Therapy a Good Career in Australia?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Growing Industry</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauty therapy is a growing industry in Australia. Overall, the current number is immeasurable, and approximately there are 31,000 Beauty Therapists added in the last ten years. Also, the number of workers in the beauty therapy industry is expected to grow over the upcoming five years, reaching up to 33,500 holders by 2025.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Source: According to ABS Labour Force Survey, seasonally adjusted data to November 2020 and National Skills Commission Employment Projections to 2025.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Statistics.jpeg\" alt=\"Growing Industry Statistics\" width=\"501\" height=\"501\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Part-Time Facilities</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This industry has the facilities to take participated in part-time or full-time job schedules. You can choose any of these career terms based on your need. Basically, most teenagers find more comfortable in part-time facilities as assistant members of a beauty therapy Center. Some are doing periodic internship programs in the beauty industries to suppress their beauty passion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Vast Opportunities</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are many different sections to explore in the beauty industry, such as makeup artistry, skincare, nail care, hair styling, and more. Assuming your capabilities, you may get a favourite interest as your best career in the beauty sector to reach the ultimate goal. Like, the steps of a successful beauty industry career, you will have to face many phases of working lines. About 9% of people in Australia are adapting this career for a full-time job. Over time, you don\'t wish to be in the same position and may not want to carry the same thing. So, you will get vast opportunities to sharp your reach, status, and job security.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Self-career Orientated</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are many opportunities for self-employment with this career path as there are various options to blend your working experience into the beauty industry as a therapist proctor. Recently, many people are starting their own therapist Center, spas, and beauty salons in Australia. So, if you are capable, you can have the most considerable option to build a career as a beauty therapist center entrepreneur.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Career Opportunities in Beauty Industry.jpg\" alt=\"Career Opportunities in Beauty Industry\" width=\"557\" height=\"371\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Job Security</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This industry\'s jobs are cheerful and delightful, considering every therapist unless you do anything disrespectful. By maintaining the health law and authenticated qualifications, the skills of beauty therapy are intangible. So, the value of a skilled therapist has a positive demand for the people. Even there is less possibility of losing a job because the demand for therapists is rising day by day. Adding your job more protection shield by getting the RPL Certificate III in Beauty Therapy from an RTO in Australia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Fun Loving Career</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Definitely, you will love this passionate job and never get bored because you will constantly learn new things about your job lines and operating different tools. That beauty industry career has a different module of working schedule. So, there is a flexible timing for the therapists and has a reassuring role to play for full-timers and part-timers. This career allows you to be creative and supportive under limitations. Still, you can put your best ideas to make good care of the clients.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Well-Paid Salary</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The earning per month counts as per the professional parameter for a beauty therapist than the regular job. The average beauty therapist salary in Australia is $57,525 per year or $29.50 per hour. Entry-level positions start yearly at $53,625 on average, while most experienced workers can income up to $67,969 per year. Even it is possible for you to earn more to pursue your beauty interest. Additionally, an <strong>RPL qualification in <a href=\"../../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy</a> will help to secure your job</strong>. The demand price is high for an RPL holder. The RPL certification is one of the best ways to get employment in any beauty therapy center.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Statistics of Salary In Beauty Industry.jpeg\" alt=\"Statistics of Salary In Beauty Industry\" width=\"600\" height=\"203\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>**Figure: </strong>Average $57,525/ Annual Based on 31 salaries following</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Words</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We cover all the possible reasons and information regarding a promising career in the beauty therapy industry in the border discussion. Most women are engaging, and a few numbers are male-oriented in the therapy industry. So, developing a blooming career in beauty treatment and therapy centers is a good choice for the specified skilled persons without looking for non-professional jobs.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Considering the overall employment demand on beauty therapy, you may wonder to know, what is beauty therapy? Or what is a beauty therapist\'s salary? And why is beauty therapy a good career in Australia?', 'why-is-beauty-therapy-a-good-career-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2021-09-09 07:35:59', '2021-09-09 07:41:11');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(38, 7, 'How to Become a Remedial Massage Therapist in Australia? - Complete Guide', 'how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia', NULL, 'From all those queries, we structure this article with the essential ideas about the profession of a corrective massage therapist step by step. So, let\'s find out the procedure of becoming a remedial massage therapist in your area.', '<p>Want to start a promising career as a remedial massage therapist? Then it is important to understand the industry in the first place. You can\'t deploy in these job lines without having the proper qualifications and degrees. For that, some of the basic things will need to consider from your side. Additionally, it will be best if you have adequated massage training, professional certificates, registered documents of myotherapy, and most importantly, the passions into you. Those are great sources to become a good remedial massage therapist.</p>\r\n<p>Thinking of growing the massage therapist career, you just need to know the basic requirements necessary to earn and how to become a remedial massage therapist in Australia? From all those queries, we structure this article with the essential ideas about the profession of a corrective massage therapist step by step. So, let\'s find out the procedure of becoming a remedial massage therapist in your area.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>What is Remedial Massage Therapy? And Who are the therapists?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedial massage therapy is a massage technique used to treat certain conditions on affected muscles, tendons, ligaments, and various injured parts of the body. Basically, athletics and sports players regularly take such massages to get rid of body pain and other muscle injuries. This method is a quick process to heal the damaged areas of the body, and those massage therapies don\'t have any significant side effects too.</p>\r\n<p>A therapist who is registered with Massage &amp; Myotherapy is known as a remedial massage therapist. A remedial therapist is appropriately trained. The person has the functional qualification of formed massage where the aims are to work on the physical pain reduction and inflammation in the muscle and soft tissue recovery.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The remedial massage therapist\'s roles are to evaluate and apply suitable massage techniques in the muscle\'s recovery. Some important functions of a remedial massage therapist that you must know, </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Deep tissue massage &amp; trigger point therapy method.</li>\r\n<li>Strengthening &amp; stretching exercises method.</li>\r\n<li>Joint mobilizations and myofascial release method.</li>\r\n<li>Assisted stretching technique.</li>\r\n<li>Cupping and dry needling method.</li>\r\n<li>Hot and cold therapy system.</li>\r\n<li>Thermotherapy and cryotherapy method.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>How to Become a Remedial Massage Therapist?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Learn New Skills</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To become a good remedial massage therapist, learn new things about massages and body nerves connecting with the muscles and tissues. That will help you to broader your remedial therapy knowledge. The more you acquire your skills in this industry, the chances of getting a brilliant career will arise in the massage industry.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Develop Your Talents</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Suppose you are well acknowledged about the industry and have the proper qualifications for remedial massage. Then try to improve your skills and develop your talents in the massage sector with home or institutional practices. Initially, without having experience or real-life workflow, you may not be able to blend yourself into a good position in this industry.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some basic skills that you can improve to get into your dream job, </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Develop strong communication and management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Grow your understanding skills and the concept of therapeutic bonding.</li>\r\n<li>Improve your listening skills and note down all the questions from clients.</li>\r\n<li>Learning new things and adapting skills to handle any uncertain situations.</li>\r\n<li>Fundamental marketing, financial, and administration skills.</li>\r\n<li>Problem-solving and business supervision skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Grow Your Career with Training and Education</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s focus on the main terms and the requirements to consider your talents into a professional therapist. By gathering some of the educational degrees, and qualified certificates you can apply to merge into this career easily,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Education and Training Requirements </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To work as a massage therapist in Australia, you have to complete a full qualification of massage training and vocational education. Like other job qualifications, a higher degree is essential but initially not that mandatory for this position. Some advance or diploma courses can cover your educational pathway process.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Earn RPL in Diploma of Remedial Massage (HLT52015) </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The nationally accredited qualification RPL in Diploma of Remedial Massage will polish your career in massage therapy. It will help you step further and give you the essential practical skills and knowledge to conduct as a remedial massage therapist. After graduating from a Diploma of Remedial Massage course from a renowned RTO, you will forge a great personal value and have a booming career.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Self-interested</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Along with the proper educations and training, you can have an outstanding career in this employment sector. But having a self-interest in this industry will lead you to a good position based on your earned skills. To become a remedial therapist, you need to focus on the self-loving thing about the job tasks and enjoy the job loads. Determine and conclude your attention to this and get completed all the vital things to grow your interest more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Good Salary Range</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>An entry-level person with less than 1-year experience as a massage therapist has an expected earning of AU$26 hourly based on 11 salaries. Additionally, a mid-level massage therapist with 5-8 years of experience has average compensation of AU$30 based on 75 salaries. An experienced massage health therapist has an average wage of AU$32-35 based on 42 salaries. In their late-career lines, every employee has average pay of AU$28 per hour depending on the skills.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/Remedail Massage Therapist Average Salary.jpeg\" alt=\"Remedail Massage Therapist Average Salary\" width=\"800\" height=\"319\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Vast Opportunities</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To be eligible for this career, the candidate must be interested in and well trained in the massage side and should meet the national legal acceptance criteria from the Australian Health Assurance Acts (AHS). So, here are some respective job positions are given below to start a career in the remedial massage therapy industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Remedial Massage Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Sports Massage Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Clinical Massage Therapist</li>\r\n<li>Soft Tissue Allied Health Assistant</li>\r\n<li>Registered Massage Assistant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusion </strong></h2>\r\n<p>Nowadays, the demand for massage therapists or counselors is rising tremendously. So, suppose you are really interested in such a profession to become a remedial massage therapist. In that case, getting the proper qualifications, massage skills, and knowledge-based training will lead you to reach your ultimate goal. Many Australian therapist centers are well-organized and famous for massage or spa services. So, they might require someone with more qualified and professional as physiotherapy, massage, and natural medicine practitioners.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'How to Become a Remedial Massage Therapist in Australia', 'How to Become a Remedial Massage Therapist in Australia', 'From all those queries, we structure this article with the essential ideas about the profession of a corrective massage therapist step by step. So, let\'s find out the procedure of becoming a remedial massage therapist in your area.', 'how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2021-09-15 09:46:11', '2022-01-16 10:12:20'),
(39, 7, 'How to Set up a Mobile Hairdressing Business in Australia?', 'how-to-set-up-a-mobile-hairdressing-business-in-australia', 5, 'get to know how to set up a mobile hairdressing business in Australia? And some key facts about mobile hairdressing businesses that prefer the comfort and convenient services starting from your home.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nowadays <a href=\"../../blogs/how-can-hairdressing-be-more-advanced-in-the-future\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hairdressing business</a> is growing so fast that the collective number of hairdressers is also rising. Even the structures are less hassle-free, so anyone with adequate qualifications can apply to open a hair styling business to serve in their own place. The best way to start a hairdressing business is to <a href=\"../../blogs/top-10-benefits-of-rpl-qualification-in-hairdressing-industry\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">get trained</a> and join cosmetology institutions to earn proficiency as a hairdresser.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Initially, you can set up your business considering small budgeting. The ideal model for a beginner is a mobile hairdressing business. If you think about the job satisfaction where you can flexible with your work. At that point, the best choice would be a mobile hairdressing business to unleash your expertise. Later you can improve and go further for the prominent places based on your experience and financial ability. Now let\'s get to know how to set up a mobile hairdressing business in Australia? And some key facts about mobile hairdressing businesses that prefer the comfort and convenient services starting from your home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>How to Set up a Mobile Hairdressing Business in Australia?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-cottonbro-3992875.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Choose a Name for Your Business</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before you login into a place to start your hairdressing business, you just need a name to register for the saloon. Now choose a short and particular name under your services. The title will introduce your business module, so be more creative as this will be your pattern name for the rest of the business activities. Your business name should differentiate your business from the other hairdressing parlors.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Create a Logo for Your Business</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, you will need an attractive and exclusive logo design to make your saloon identity more unique. Some use atelic logos and only use iconic symbols to create an identification in the business market. You can choose best on your preference but remember that it should be dissimilar and new because it will use in everywhere as the company\'s figure and for the promotional posts.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Register for Mobile Business</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To get registered as a mobile hairdresser, you have to understand the country law\'s and then collect all the requirements. Those will entail applying for the registration process and let you learn all the legal procedures for this industry. Don\'t get worried because the system is simple, and anyone with proper documentation may obtain a license for a particular zone. Just apply for an ABN number from the Australian Taxation Office (ATO).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gather the Instruments</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-nataliya-vaitkevich-8468019.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can\'t just start a business without the hairdressing instruments. Formerly, you will need to buy most of the essentials to operate hair styling services. There are many professional items for a big saloon or hairdresser center, but some important things must be arranged in your dressing desk for the mobile salon business. Before the verdict part of this article, you will find out what are the essentials needed to open a mobile hairdresser business.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Decide The Types of Hair Service</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Let\'s say you are good at haircuts and coloring; now, you can\'t offer your clients hair treatment services. So, you have to decide the main hair services based on your skills and professional training for the hairdressing business. Later, you can add some hair service features to your business by hiring specialized individuals for hairstyling and extensions service lines.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Start-up Plan for Mobile Hairdressing</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No matter what is the size and investment of your business contains, you must follow a schedule plan. A proper plan needs to structure before you begin with a new business. You need to determine the start-up costs, rent charges, decide the location (If Any), business types or services, financial supports, and overall, the promotional expenses too. Everything should be written, and the draft must include total forecasting of the upcoming schemes and budgeting.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Promotional Activities for New business</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">While you will start a new business, you may find it challenging to get customers. For that, you can start with your family and friend supports; later on, you can go for online promotion by opening online platforms which are less expensive and easier to reach massive people around your zone. Finally, promote some of your best hairdressing content and videos to attract more visible customers through digital marketing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why Goes for Mobile Hairdressing Business?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Working in a running hairdresser industry may give you the thrill to work hard, and the average pay is good in those sectors. But working that much can give you a thrive in your daily life. So, some prefer to work as an independent hairdresser and open a mobile hairdressing business of their own. In Australia, there are three types of options for mobile hairdressers,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Working from Home</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-anthony-shkraba-6599036.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"791\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Start your saloon business from your home space and let your clients visit on your flexible schedules. You can make your house as your service center and get comfortable with your work. All you have to offer your services and collect the appointments from the clients. Remember, you have to prepare for your daily meetings before the day starts and clean all the mass at the end of the day.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Visiting Clients\' Homes</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the significant benefits of being a mobile hairdresser is visiting your clients based on their demands or requests. This is the best way to reach many clients within a short time, but before that, you have to be specialized and expert on your services. This form of business is very cost-efficient as you don\'t need to rent a place or work on your house. Also, you can provide hair cutting services to customers on the campaign programs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Renting a Chair</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-cottonbro-3993133.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The most popular option to start a mobile hairdresser business is to rent a chair in a hairstyling salon. You don\'t need to rent a whole place in the initial stage of the company. It might be costly to afford an entire salon, for that most freelancer hair experts rent a room for their customers inside a hairdressing center. You may be lucky to find more customers beyond your appointments when there is a tied working schedule. On a percentage, you can work for the salon, even other facilities like place environment, air-conditioner, hairdryers\' machinery, water lines. Those will help to reduce your burden to manage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>If you think that the only tasks are to cut and style the hair, you must be aware of your other initial charges. You\'ll also need to be responsible for: </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Dealing with customer\'s inquiries and booking issues.</li>\r\n<li>Offering client consultations for better outcomes.</li>\r\n<li>Managing all administrational jobs such as products purchasing, cleaning, and decorating.</li>\r\n<li>Along with that, you have to be in charge of banking, accounting, and other expenses too.</li>\r\n<li>Hiring employees and training them is your job to accomplish.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Essential Things to Open a Saloon</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To open a mobile hairdressing service, basically, you may require to use the right tools for the haircutting job. A self-employed hairdresser must need some essential equipment, which should be the best quality under the license code. Now let\'s check out what are essentials need to arrange for your mobile hairdressing saloon. As a barber, you will need,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>A dressing instrument carrier box.</li>\r\n<li>A set of scissors and combs</li>\r\n<li>Standard electrical hairdryers.</li>\r\n<li>Quality straighteners (At least two sizes)</li>\r\n<li>Hair clippers and Razors.</li>\r\n<li>Curling irons and Grip Rollers</li>\r\n<li>Bleach-resistant salon towels</li>\r\n<li>Trimmers and edgers instruments</li>\r\n<li>A stock of grade hair products (shampoos, conditioners, styling products, colors, etc.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Drafts</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You have to find out what licenses and permits are needed to operate in your state or country before you head to construct a hairdressing business. Next, determine how much money you\'ll need to start up and run the business. For all that <a href=\"https://articles.bplans.com/what-makes-a-good-plan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">developing a good plan</a> is a fundamental and prime concern. With <a href=\"../../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sufficient skill</a> and knowledge and determination, you can end up building a famous hairdressing saloon by starting a mobile hairdressing business in your state.</p>', 'How to Set up a Mobile Hairdressing Business in Australia', 'How to Set up a Mobile Hairdressing Business in Australia', 'get to know how to set up a mobile hairdressing business in Australia? And some key facts about mobile hairdressing businesses that prefer the comfort and convenient services starting from your home.', 'how-to-set-up-a-mobile-hairdressing-business-in-australia.png', NULL, '2021-09-21 09:56:50', '2022-01-16 08:53:56'),
(40, 7, 'How can Hairdressing Be More Advanced in The Future?', 'how-can-hairdressing-be-more-advanced-in-the-future', 5, 'In advanced methods of the hairdressing industry, many things need to be considered and making your business progress; those will help to bloom your business.', '<p>In this modern era, everything is changing, and the adaptability of advanced technologies is rising tremendously. Even the modern beauty art and hairdressing services have gotten revolutionary changes in their businesses. The use of technologies is expected in this beauty industry, but having more advanced equipment has made it much easier for people to adopt. By applying advanced applications, virtual reality and artificial intelligence can offer the best services for the users by the hairdressers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In advanced methods of the hairdressing industry, many things need to be considered and making your business progress; those will help to bloom your business. As a hairdresser specialist, you may wonder how hairdressing can be more advanced in the future and what are the impacts of applying those techniques for good? So, here we are presenting some of the futuristic components which will change the meaning of the hairdressing industry\'s scenarios.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why is Advance Hairdressing Important? </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>More Hair Art </strong></p>\r\n<p>With the help of modern techniques, people are now getting more options for experiments with their hair designs. Using various apps and software, people are getting the outcomes of the unique hair arts instantly. Even you can make your own hair designs and customize the ins and out of your preferences.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Leaser Treatment </strong></p>\r\n<p>The traditional formats of hair treatments have gone long ago. Nowadays, people prefer modern hair therapies and laser treatments to sophisticate the hair problem. Thinking of that, those are costly but take less time to resolve your hair difficulties and complications. Even those are safe, and experts recommended.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://image.freepik.com/free-photo/female-hairdresser-making-hairstyle-blonde-woman-beauty-salon_176420-4458.jpg\" alt=\"Female hairdresser making hairstyle to blonde woman in beauty salon Free Photo\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Ultimate Creativity </strong></p>\r\n<p>With the assist of advanced technology, anyone can mirror their hair outlooks from the smart devices to understand the results after compiling. Let&rsquo;s say, for example, you are thinking of adopting a new haircut or hairstyle. Now by using AI software, you can see or apply virtually to check back how are you looking with the new customization? Easy to pick any design best in your interest.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Easy Appointments </strong></p>\r\n<p>In those recent days, using management tools are very easy going for most of the business. Even for a hair spa or salon appointment, you can set the meeting with the hairdressers online. Many parlors are providing these services for customers satisfaction and making the growth of the businesses with easy management tools.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accuracy and Cost Efficient </strong></p>\r\n<p>To make more accuracy in the work lines, many organizations now depend on those modern technologies to provide the best services under the best budgets. Even the long terms traditional session is over for most of the beauty solution hairdressers. Moreover, the hair business unit costs are reducing much and become more cost-efficient for clients and the owners.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>How can Hairdressing Be More Advanced in The Future? </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Use of Artificial Intelligence </strong></p>\r\n<p>People are using many Beauty Perfection Mobile apps and AI software to align the forge of your hair spot. Even the use of digital technology in the hairdressing business is also part of Artificial intelligence. Many hairdressers are now taking advantage of AI technology to meet up the client\'s demand.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mobile Applications </strong></p>\r\n<p>Through your smartphone, you can process the hair looks completely different owing to well-developed applications. Many software companies are making user-friendly mobile apps to conduct according to your hair design for a trail to customize hair colors and designs that how you will look after your desire hair artworks get applied. The management software also plays an advanced role in modernizing the business by considering the overall hairdressing industry.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Augmented Reality </strong></p>\r\n<p>With the modern innovation of Augmented reality, you can set up your hair designs with the help of a VR set. It will give you a realistic vibe and let you understand the ultimate result of your hair color experiments. Later you can pick any style from the interest of hair models. Moreover, Virtual Hair Changing Rooms is one of the ideal examples of augmented reality tools.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advance Hair Cut Machine </strong></p>\r\n<p>Nowadays, there you will find many advanced haircutting machines and modern hairdressing tools. Approaching those tools makes it easier to implement and lets the users give a comfortable haircut without any ragged. But through professionals, those advanced hair cut machines should be operated and have the proper maintenance under conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hairdresser Bots </strong></p>\r\n<p>In few places, there are getting the replacements of hairdressers to the artificial robots for easy solutions for hair styling. People love the idea of hairdresser bots as those are easy to use, and no need to make awaited appointments. All you just need to visit any nearby hair Booths or mobile hairdresser\'s stalls and make an instant hair cut or color according to your need.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hair Treatment Lab&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<p>In the modern facilities of hair treatment labs, you will find many effective hair spa sources or hair treatments procedures that allow you to make some changes in your hair management and available shades as those labs are containing with full of electronic devices and ultra-modern hair treatment facilities. Those hair treatment labs are highly restricted and very expensive to organize; still, the numbers are growing in this latest world.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>How Will The Changes Affect the Industry? </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Growth of business</strong></p>\r\n<p>The hairdressing industry will bloom business as people become more confrontational and modernized by heading for advanced technology.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Less Number of Employees </strong></p>\r\n<p>With modern science and technology, the hairdressing industry is now replacing humans with robots and which is a matter of unemployment at a high rate.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Easy Managements </strong></p>\r\n<p>As all things are getting mobilized and automatic, the hairdressing industry may confirm the easy management procedures. It will help to conduct accessible communication with customers in the upcoming days.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>High Maintenance </strong></p>\r\n<p>Advanced hairdressing methods are developing rapidly along with the growth of modern science. Still, those are under construction as well, as they need high maintenances and professional expertise.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>To Wrap Things Up </strong></p>\r\n<p>In the upcoming days, the growth of the hairdressing industry has formed with the hi-tech. Furthermore, people are getting more interested and embraced in such practices to use the hairstyling method. Now or then, the hairdressing industry will be standing on a new generation of automation systems without having any real humans.</p>', 'Hairdressing, Hairdressing Future', 'How can Hairdressing Be More Advanced in The Future', 'In advanced methods of the hairdressing industry, many things need to be considered and making your business progress; those will help to bloom your business.', 'how-can-hairdressing-be-more-advanced-in-the-future.jpeg', NULL, '2021-10-04 07:38:36', '2021-10-18 09:33:39'),
(41, 7, 'What are The Qualifications Do You Need for Beauty Therapy in Australia?', 'what-are-the-qualifications-do-you-need-for-beauty-therapy-in-australia', NULL, 'Are you interested in making your career into a promising one? Well, thinking of that, you may see lots of people now have great paying in the beauty industry as a therapist.', '<p>Are you interested in making your career into a promising one? Well, thinking of that, you may see lots of people now have great paying in the beauty industry as a therapist. In this career, there is a mass number of chances to grow your future from this industry. Even top beauty therapists have more job lines than any other sector in Australia. Above all, the work factors have a more fun-loving and secure career in the long term. Perhaps, you can also become an owner of a beauty salon or spa with the qualification of a beauty therapist.</p>\r\n<p>Getting the opportunity to become a beauty therapist isn&rsquo;t easy, and you must wonder what qualifications you need to become a beauty therapy? And why do you want to become one of the successful hairdressers? If you really want to become a professional beauty therapist, you must go through the lines and get to know the steps in order to qualify as a beauty therapist in your chosen specialism. Here, we are providing you with a complete guide to become a therapist in the beauty industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Steps by Steps: What Qualifications Do You Need for Beauty Therapy? </strong></p>\r\n<p>Some specialized courses and training are required to become a therapist in the beauty industry. Like, other job requirements, some qualifications need to follow and get a recognized certificate in beauty. In Australia, there are specific bindings for beauty therapy and esoteric qualification in particular beauty sectors. So, let&rsquo;s discuss the qualifications which are needed to get a job in the beauty therapy industry.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/graph.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"877\" height=\"570\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Education &amp; Training for a Beauty Therapist</strong></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"237\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You have to complete a VET qualification degree in the beauty remedy sector to become a beauty therapist.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>Earn high-level skills and become a trusted beauty expert with a Diploma of Beauty Therapy SHB50115 from any renowned RTO in Australia.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Gain hands-on work experience, either during a practical component of beauty courses or external to diploma study under any authorized institution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Explore opportunities for higher study, such as a Diploma of Beauty Therapy under the specialize in a particular term, or consider moving into a management role for this industry.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>To become an entry-level beautician in Australia, you can achieve a certificate III level qualification in beauty therapy. For more advanced courses of study available like certificate IV qualifications or diplomas which are very high-level courses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>According to the training process, a well-known institution needs to choose based on the subjects, including the obligations that may differ from one to another.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You can also become a beauty therapist through an apprenticeship or internship. Most beauty centers require high professional individuals; still, there are chances to go along with your current position.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Having a college or high school degree is a must for beauty treatment therapists as they need to operate beauty equipment and tools according to the need. <br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>A counselor must have a professional degree in the beauty industry and a certificate as a long-term skin health care provider.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Soft and Interpersonal Skills</strong><br /><br /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Personal requirements for a beauty therapist need to have a shaped appearance full day long and shouldn&rsquo;t have any allergies to beauty products.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Interpersonal skills must be adaptable with pleasant and tactful behavior when dealing with customers or clients.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Administration skills, including appointment setting, record-keeping, and cash handling, are advantageous in this beauty job sector.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Detailed attention is also important. Having good hand-eye coordination, along with that, be attentive to the taste of your customers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Show interest in people and improve your communication skills on the most warming level.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You should keep updated on trendy things around the world because you never know what your customers may demand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Be more careful and more responsive when dealing with clients for body and facial treatments that are related to their skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities of a Beauty Therapist</strong></p>\r\n<p>Beauty Therapists need to be qualified to perform a variety of treatments as the beauty industry is a big platform with hundreds of responsibilities. Though as a therapist you don&rsquo;t have to go through any typical duties. But internees or assistants are assigned for every possible task under limitations and they also do administration jobs too. So, here we have listed some of the common job responsibilities of a beauty therapist below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Typically, a beauty therapists responsibilities include:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Specialized persons are assigned to give different engaging duty based on the specialization of their experiences and skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Beauty therapists are appointed to train juniors and even many organizations arrange beauty therapist courses to provide certified degree.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A beautician does perform various treatments such as facials, tanning, hair removal, manicures and pedicures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Performing facial or body massage and treatments and removing facial or body hair through waxing or electrolysis.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attend the phone calls and make booking for client&rsquo;s appointments and greeting clients with a coordinate while they come into the center.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Advising clients on the make-up and cosmetics treatment best on their preferences is also the part of a beauty counsellor jobs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Helping with administrative tasks such as paperwork, checking and ordering supplies, and keeping records of client&rsquo;s treatment programmes and medical histories.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Providing the skin care services are the one of the prime responsibilities. Moreover, therapists are up to give suggestion on beauty products.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Provide advice and support to clients with cosmetic surgery, recognise problems and refer clients to medical practitioners such as dermatologists, plastic surgeons, endocrinologists, podiatrists, chiropractors and physiotherapists</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Doing hair art or hairdressing are also the essential part of the beauty sector. So, it is mandatory to have best skill and idea about creative hair design.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>There are other exercises that a therapist needs to perform like, massages, make-up application, and lash and brow treatments &ndash; such as shaping and tinting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Final Terms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Till now, we have gotten to know the basic job requirements of beauty therapists and the job responsibilities under conditions. Now depending on your suitable terms, choose many courses on beauty therapy qualifications and get cover for those conditions to become a successful beauty therapist in your state.</p>', 'Beauty Therapy, Qualifications for Beauty Therapy, Need for Beauty Therapy', 'What Qualifications Do You Need for Beauty Therapy', 'Are you interested in making your career into a promising one? Well, thinking of that, you may see lots of people now have great paying in the beauty industry as a therapist.', 'what-are-the-qualifications-do-you-need-for-beauty-therapy-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2021-10-18 10:07:50', '2021-10-18 10:07:50'),
(42, 7, 'What Can Beauty Therapists Do During Covid to Re-Open Businesses?', 'what-can-beauty-therapists-do-during-covid-to-re-open-businesses', NULL, 'Here, we covered some of the best tips for what can you do to re-open your business as a beauty therapist during Covid?', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">From the prior year, everybody has been going through the unforeseen circumstances of Covid-19 and still trying to overcome those difficult times. Not only that but we were also hampered because of the coronavirus pandemic in our daily lives. Those unwanted situations had gotten worst scenarios in the following years of 2021, and every business was affected by the term of lockdown and health issues around the world. As a result, <a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/blogs/how-to-develop-a-good-career-as-a-beauty-therapist\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">beauty businesses</a> were also getting dimmed and floating with tough times. Even many beauty salons and spa or mobile hairdressing businesses were forced to shut down. Because of financial losses and the client&rsquo;s discreet visiting, the beauty therapists were dropping down, which was totally unacceptable. <br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">But now, the situation is getting stable while everybody is vaccinating under the government&rsquo;s maintenance. Moreover, many <a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/blogs/why-is-beauty-therapy-a-good-career-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">beauty industries are re-opening</a> their businesses onwards under conditions and maintaining the safety guidance from coronavirus. So, here, we covered some of the best tips for what can you do to re-open your business as a beauty therapist during Covid?<br /><br /></p>\r\n<h2><strong>Best Tips for What Can Beauty Therapists Do During Covid? </strong></h2>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Be Vaccinated First </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is important to get yourself safer from your clients or customers. For that, make sure to get vaccinated before you head to re-open your business. Even it is good to check the client&rsquo;s vaccinated status before you climb to provide any treatment services.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Limit Your Customers </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To avoid gathering your customers, you can limit the number of customers visiting your place at one time. For that, you can arrange to schedule your client&rsquo;s daily visit at particular times, or you can make online sessions to consult with your customers.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Ensure to Wear Mask</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You should always be protected with a safety shield, and it is mandatory to wear a mask. It is counted as the easiest way to keep yourself and the mirror one to spread the covid virus. Also, strictly maintain the &lsquo;No mask, no service&rsquo; policy.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Keep Your Premises Clean</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Always keep your salon or spa center cleaned and sanitized. No matter what, after leaving any client, make a quick spray of sanitizer all over your place, then allow another one. Perhaps, you can arrange a weekly cleaning program one or two times.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Practice of Sensitizations </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To provide client satisfaction, keep liquid sanitizer or soap water to rub their hands and other external parts of the body. It will help to prevent your place from covid and other virus. In addition, make your parlor more secure and safe from the danger of Covid.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Make Safe Distance </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don&rsquo;t just roam around extensively while you have excessive customers into your therapy house unless you have any follow-up tasks to complete one by one. If not, then it is best to keep a safe distance from your clients and also instruct your visitors to maintain a safe distance from each other.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Follow Country&rsquo;s Rules </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maintaining the government&rsquo;s rule is one of the essentials to follow up strictly. Under any circumstance, you have to keep updated with the current flow of Covid situations. If there is an emergency situation that breaks out, you must follow the instructions provided by the government.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Use Germfree Tools </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Never miss keeping your regular useable tools after getting used or touched by anyone. So always wear gloves and cleanish your daily items what is used frequently. It is your high responsibility to make your working materials germ-free for use widely.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Check Products Validity </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">By the time of the Covid breakdown, many <a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/blogs/beauty-tips-and-recommended-products-to-take-care-of-dry-skin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">beauty products</a> companies couldn&rsquo;t make the delivery on time, which caused a low configuration of the validity of products. For that, there is a chance to receive expired products which may not be wise to use for your clients. So, always check the validity of the products and choose the best on the preferences.&nbsp; <br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Start Online Reservation </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rather than counting the reservation physically, one of the easiest ways is to make the booking system online much easier and more manageable. Most of the beauty therapist centers depend on the <a href=\"https://www.planyo.com/\">online platform</a> to make a reservation and provide consultations. </p>\r\n<h1><strong>Final Words</strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In this covid situation, everyone was worried about re-open their old businesses. By that time, everything is just getting back to normal. Still, you may need some bindings to follow up and continue <a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/blogs/how-to-start-up-your-own-beauty-boutique-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">your beauty therapist chamber</a>. From the upper discussion, you can adopt those essential tips to make yourself relax and get back to your daily job. No matter what, safety should be the priority above all the other factors during Covid.</p>', NULL, 'What Can Beauty Therapists Do During Covid', NULL, 'what-can-beauty-therapists-do-during-covid.png', NULL, '2021-10-27 11:14:42', '2022-01-16 08:59:48');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(44, 7, 'Top 13 Beautician Interview Questions And How To Nail Them', 'top-13-beautician-interview-questions-and-how-to-nail-them', NULL, 'You must get to ask about your beauty qualifications, training, skills, ability, trendy update and most importantly, your best interests.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To get a job in any industry, the candidates must go through an interview session. Sometimes the interview takes a few minutes, or in some cases, it takes too long to get the final decision. As a <a href=\"../diploma-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">beauty therapist </a>or beautician, if you apply to get a job in a renowned saloon or therapy centre, then you must prepare yourself to face all those intellectual questions. Even the interviewers also need to make preparation for the candidates who are attending the program.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In an interview, the essential thing is facing the questions and presenting them appropriately, which is a big challenge. Though you will never know what are the questions you may need to answer? Besides, when you\'re interviewing for the beautician position in a beauty salon, it is essential to prepare to answer the questions. You must get to ask about your beauty qualifications, training, skills, ability, trendy update and most importantly, your best interests.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the facts, here we review a list of frequently asked interview questions for the beautician post or the candidates who are seeking to start their career in the beauty industry. Go through the rest of the section and get to know the key beautician interview questions, and nail your interview more delighted and smoother.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Key Beautician Interview Questions and Preparation Guide</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-edmond-dant&egrave;s-4342496.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apart from your basic introduction, you may have to meet some questions that the interviewers often ask. So, if you really want to nail your interview table with your presentable skills, then you can line up those questionaries in your list. We have covered most of the commonly used and possible queries that your interviewer might ask you while sitting in the interview sessions. So, let\'s not waste time and find key interview questions along with the preparation guidelines below.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tell me about yourself </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Always start your answer with thank you with a smile. Then introduce yourself with your name, living area and last profession that you were doing. Tell them about you with some catchy words but in short, as they don\'t want to waste time with your living stories.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What did you like best about your last job? (If Any)&nbsp; </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You will be beneficiary if you have experience in similar or any relevant industry in your resume as the last employment. An interviewer always gives the extra position for the last job to measure whether you have the competency or not. So, give your best answer about your last job. What do you like about them and some success stories too?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why did you leave your previous one? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It will be wise to answer the key point without telling a story. Be honest with your answer and add some good points about your previous job rather than bad-mouthing about your boss or working environment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Do you consider yourself a team player? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If an interviewer questions you, consider this your best opportunity to prove your self-confidence and leadership skills. Be gentle and present your top volunteer and event covering works along with the time and date. Don\'t rush with your answer. Just point out the best 2/3 core team leading jobs that you have done previously.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What are your greatest strengths/Weaknesses? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose you have asked any terms from this question, and the interviewer wants to know about your weakness. But remember always focus on the strength part, and minimize your weakness into your strength while answering.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Are you aware of your job responsibilities? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before applying and attending the session, you must go through the job description at least 3 or 4 times to make sure you know the job responsibilities that the saloons or parlours are asking. Some add to ask about the services that the parlours are providing to the participates.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What additional skills do you have? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Be confident about the skills and knowledge that you have been developed over time. Show your additional knowledge about the beauty industry and fuse your interest in beauty products and creativities. But don\'t overreact too much it may backfire your self-esteem.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Describe a situation to solve </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You may be given a situation to draw the conclusion in the proper manner. Be intellectual with your responses with a positive and possible case. You can\'t make it complicated with your answer as fair and easy tricks are acceptable by the hiring authority.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why do you think you can be a good beautician? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Obviously, you have to make it through your answer like how can you make people feel good, and your client looks more beautiful with your makeup touch. Tell some tips and tricks that are involved in showing that you are a knowledgeable participant in this job post.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What are requirements do you think you need to become a beautician? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Such questions usually don\'t ask frequently, but if your interviewer wants to observe yourself learning skills. Then it is highly recommended for all to do some study before heading for the interview about the <a href=\"../blogs/what-are-the-qualifications-do-you-need-for-beauty-therapy-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">basic requirements and qualifications </a>needed under this job position.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Who is your idol beautician? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you have any favourite beautician in your head, you usually like to follow their works on social media. Then don\'t hesitate with your answer. They will be happy to know that you are into this profession seriously and more passionate about the beauty industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why should we hire you? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This is the commonly asked question at the end of the interview for most of the cases. This mean company wants to see your confidence level and interest in this profession. When you pinpoint the topic or subject, don\'t conflict between your working process and expectations. Show more interest in your beauty passion and working lines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is your expectation? </strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Usually, this question comes at the end part of the interview. This question is very critical and very tricky to answer. Like you can\'t ask your surveillance to offer you something that is not feasible or beyond your experience level. Make some market research with the salary scale of a beautician and regarding the previous job experience make the negotiable procedure with the beauty salon owner.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Verdict </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Those are the most precious and commonly asked critical questions for a beautician interview. Here we try to give the possible consequences and guidelines on how to face those questionaries and impress the interview members. So far, you can make your <a href=\"../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">career starting preparation</a> by practising all those topics and facing those key beautician interview questions to <a href=\"https://au.reachout.com/articles/how-to-build-self-confidence\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">build self-confidence</a> in you.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'beautician-interview-questions-and-how-to-nail-them.jpeg', NULL, '2021-11-11 03:39:08', '2022-01-17 08:27:39'),
(45, 7, 'What Are The Differences Between A Beauty Therapist and A Beautician?', 'what-are-the-differences-between-a-beauty-therapist-and-a-beautician', NULL, 'A beautician and a beauty therapist are the persons who help to enhance beauty. They are skilled people, work on making every personal appearance good.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The main difference between a beauty therapist and a beautician is not so big. Both of them work on polishing human beauty. But, there are certainly some distinctions. In the past, the human look was not an important fact to think about. But, with time and modernization, views changed. People got different perceptions of self-look. Now, everyone wishes to look good and enjoy nice compliments. And, they became more conscious than before. Again, the beauty salon has become a popular place for people. Just a few years ago also only youngsters were more serious about looks. But, those days are gone now; almost everyone is beauty conscious today.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A beautician and a beauty therapist are the persons who help to enhance beauty. They are skilled people, work on making every personal appearance good. People visit salons to do facial, waxing, hair-cut, body massage, etc. So, those beauty experts are multitaskers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What Are The Difference Between A Beauty Therapist and A Beautician?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A beauty therapist and beauty beautician both bring joy through magnifying beauty. Yet, there remain some differences to know. Sometimes people say that it goes to show the differences in different countries. Let&rsquo;s see what those are-</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Who Is A Beautician?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-george-milton-6954163.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /><br /></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauticians mainly perform general, popular, and quick beauty services. Their tasks include-</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Hair-cut, straighten, curling</li>\r\n<li>Hair removal and waxing</li>\r\n<li>Makeup application</li>\r\n<li>Spray tanning</li>\r\n<li>Eyelash &amp; eyebrow tinting</li>\r\n<li>Lash extensions</li>\r\n<li>Manicures, pedicures, and nail art</li>\r\n<li>Simple facials</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Some beauticians also do body treatments and massage with the suggestions of an expert therapist.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauticians usually learn things, gather experiences, and provide services. There are different parlors for both men and women. Again, there are some variations in the role of beauticians. For example-<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Hairstylist<br /><br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-cottonbro-3993320.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The beautician who does hair styling is called a hairstylist. They do color, curl, straight, etc., according to customers&rsquo; demand.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Makeup Artist</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The beauticians who do makeup is known as a makeup artist. They do wedding makeup, party makeup, everyday makeup, etc. These artists do other creative works also.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-tatiana-twinslol-5368636 (1).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Nail Artist or Technician</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nail technicians do nail cutting, grooming, removing calluses and dead skins. Their tasks also include attractive nail paintings, manicures, pedicures, and so on. They are often known as nail artists too. Beauticians can provide service and run salons without any specific qualifications. But, beauticians with recognized certificates get value nowadays. In many countries, the demand for a qualified beautician is identified. To advance as a beautician, you have to be proficient enough. Also, an approved qualification plays a vital role in spreading your name in the business and marketing fields.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">However, the difference between a beautician and a beauty therapist also depends on the country. Moreover, the courses show clear differences also. For instance, in Australia, to become a certified makeup artist, you have to pursue-</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>SHB30215- Certificate III in Make-Up</strong></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>SHB30416 - Certificate III in Hairdressing</strong></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So, as an RPL qualified makeup artist, you will be equipped with many professional skills.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Who Is A Beauty Therapist?</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A beauty therapist does a broad range of works. Some of the treatments take more than one session to complete also. Their responsibility includes-</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Facials</li>\r\n<li>Examine skin types</li>\r\n<li>Consult with clients</li>\r\n<li>Suggest beauty treatments and therapies</li>\r\n<li>Doing face and body massage and treatments</li>\r\n<li>Educate clients and provide suggestions</li>\r\n<li>Sell skincare and makeup products</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Compared with beauticians, therapists need to do <a href=\"../blogs/what-are-the-qualifications-do-you-need-for-beauty-therapy-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">more study and research</a>. They study human skin and hair problems, risks, and well-being. Again, we can also notice variations in beauty therapists&rsquo; roles. Some therapists like to work in medical clinics. Some serve as consultants, and some start their own salons. Let&rsquo;s see the different tasks and names of them-</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Facialist<br /><br /></strong><strong><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-anna-shvets-5069465.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The job involves testing and diagnosing skin types and issues. Some look-conscious people hold a demand for flawless skin and beautiful faces. So, a facialist examines these faces and gives treatment and solutions accordingly. The therapies include facial, cleansing, exfoliating, microdermabrasion, and so on.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Waxing Therapist<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/hair-removal-g0e0f44e65_640.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unwanted hair removal from different body parts is a part of beauty therapy. Waxing is a popular way of doing it. These therapists usually follow two methods- hot wax and strip wax.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Massage Therapist<br /><br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/massage-g05f0ed9e9_1280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"673\" height=\"449\" /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A massage therapist performs different types of massages according to clients&rsquo; needs. Popular names are- relaxation massage, joint massage, massage for medical conditions, etc. So, this role is more physical than other therapists.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As we said earlier, the qualifications are different for beauticians and therapists. Here to remember that beauty therapists must have approved training to serve people in big countries. One cannot get a good job in a well-known therapy center without qualification. For example, in Australia, two Recognitions of prior Learning (RPL) qualifications for beauty therapy are-</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><a href=\"../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SHB40115 Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"../diploma-in-beauty-therapy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SHB50115 Diploma of Beauty Therapy</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">These courses also indicate a difference between a therapist and a beauty beautician. But, these all have <a href=\"../blogs/why-is-beauty-therapy-a-good-career-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">value in the beauty industry</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Beauticians and Beauty Therapists- Difference in Work Stations</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-delbeautybox-705255.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The beauty industry is wide. The tasks, duties, and qualifications have made a beautician and a beauty therapist two different professionals. Moreover, we can see that their working places are also not the same.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauticians usually work in salons or parlors. Almost every service is available in regular or high street salons. Also, some beauticians do freelance works. People also call it mobile salons. That means if you need a quick service at your home or hotel, then it is possible. A beautician can come to you and serve. But, these experts are generally specialized in one field. So, you can get one service from one beautician at a time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Besides, spas, hotels, large salons, or medical clinics are for beauty therapists. You can seek your beauty treatments in these places. They always try to use different centers such as,</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Massage center</li>\r\n<li>Skin treatment center</li>\r\n<li>Waxing center and so on.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In brief, both a beautician and a beauty therapist play a role in making people beautiful. But, if you want a specific service or treatment, you should know where to go. And, of course, to study a specialized course in beauty, it is also required to understand these small differences.</p>', NULL, 'Differences between a beauty therapist and a beautician', 'A beauty therapist is a big term, but a beautician is not.', 'differences-between-a-beauty-therapist-and-a-beautician.jpeg', NULL, '2021-11-21 07:47:18', '2021-11-30 10:08:15'),
(46, 7, 'How To Get Healthy Hair- 6 Professional Tips for Hair Treatment', 'how-to-get-healthy-hair-6-professional-tips-for-hair-treatment', NULL, 'To get an outstanding result for a good layer of hair, you can have the practice of some essential treatment of your hair just to look rock and shine with silky hair.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are worried about hair fall or loss, then you might decide to chop off your long locks for that stylish short look, but later, you may regret the decision. Even you can&rsquo;t do your own hair cut professionally just by looking at the mirror. It may cause, unfortunately, only if something goes wrong while deciding to cut own bangs. But only cutting hair won&rsquo;t add so many benefits to getting healthy hair. To get an outstanding result for a good layer of hair, you can have the practice of some essential treatment of your hair just to look rock and shine with silky hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose, you think all those treatments might cost you a lot, then let us assure you of one thing. It is very easy to do all those beauty procedures at home in an organic way. There is no need to pay a visit parlor to make your hair treatment. Here are some essential tips about how to get healthy hair with professional treatment? Suit yourself with those tips and get the best possible way to grow healthy and fast hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Best 6 Professional Tips to Get Healthy Hair</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is always best to adopt natural elements and techniques to beautify your natural body tone. Nowadays, many artificial beauty hair products are replacing those natural components to use. It is a kind of blessing and also very threatening to our natural body to adjust in the main time. Those chemical or unnatural techniques will not always give full proven results, but having natural treatment will always make your hair healthier and let you style whatever you want to do with your hair. Let&rsquo;s define the best hair treatment tips that might help you find a solution as a professional hair therapist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use Natural Vitamins</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (6).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"705\" height=\"383\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We all apprehend those vitamins are suitable for an individual&rsquo;s body. So, thinking of the idea, why wouldn&rsquo;t they be great for the hair? Usually, a working mom can&rsquo;t maintain an enriched food chart loaded with vitamins while they need to grow their hair, then one of the best options is to use some hair vitamins. Among various available nutritious, Hum nutrition hair sweet air is vegan gummies. It includes vitamins and minerals such as <a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/biotin-hair-growth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">biotin</a>, b12, and zinc, which are essential for quickly growing that luscious hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Getting Hair Trims</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (7).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"645\" height=\"370\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you keep your damaged hair on and don&rsquo;t cut off from your vibrant hair, it might be a length problem for healthy hair. In comparison, it&rsquo;s a myth that hair will grow faster with trims, where the hair will grow stronger with each trim. By avoiding <a href=\"../../blogs/best-haircutting-tips-for-women-and-how-to-practice-the-haircut-at-home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cutting the hair</a>, the ends of the hair will split like tiny branches, making the length at the bottom look almost see-through, making the hair have weak ends. Definitely, you might want long and shiny hair, where healthy and strong hair results from getting trims often by professionals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Put Hair Mask</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (8).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"294\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Most people use a mask for their face to give their skin that extra pampering. So why not do the same for the hair? Using a mask can moisturize and strengthen your hair, which will help an individual&rsquo;s hair grow quicker and healthier. Therefore, if anyone notices their hair starting to fall flat after using a mask, they shouldn&rsquo;t get bothered. Instead, they should just spread the mask out a bit more. Moreover, if an individual is looking for a natural or more DIY style mask, like having coconut oil will moisturize the hair in no time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Follow Healthy Diet&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (9).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"336\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For growing long and strong hair, following a healthy diet is essential. What an individual puts in their body reflects outside their body, too, so a nutrient-rich diet leads to super healthy hair. One will want to eat foods with plenty of biotin, protein, and vitamins, particularly A, C, and E. Foods that comprise these aspects have been reliably shown to promote hair growth and strength! Foods like eggs, spinach, fish, and nuts should be the new food staples on a person&rsquo;s hair growth journey. Such protein will treat you from the inside till then wait for a tremendous result in hair growth.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Apply Coconut Oil</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (10).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"662\" height=\"387\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You need to take some serious steps to make your hair comfortable based on your hair and scalp. Coconut oil is an extremely multifaceted beauty and healthy product that people use for all sorts of natural treatment and cleaning to moisturize their skin and remove any hair gel. Even others often use coconut oil to help improve the shape and healthy condition of their hair. Coconut oil gives a long, straight structure hair, which is more easily absorbed deep into the hair shaft, and rubbing oil on your hair before or after washing helps prevent temporary hair damage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Maintain Hair Hydration</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Avoid heating your hair one of the best hair care tips, but also one of the most often scorned is using a heat-protective spray on your hair before using hot tools like blow dryers and straightening and curling irons. Now you&rsquo;ll still love how your hair looks even after the styling wears off. It is recommended to use a hair masque and shampoo on your scalp once a week or 3-4 times to get the ultimate long hair. Less is more when you are learning how to maintain healthy hair. Apply conditioner hair end, do comb your wet hair, dry hair with a blow-dryer. Always best to use <a href=\"http://www.haircaremanual.com/washing-hair/right-temperature-for-washing-hair-hot-cold/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lukewarm water for your hair wash</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Final Words</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Till now, you get to know all the essential hair treatments. After following these tips, there&rsquo;s no doubt that the hair will grow fast and constantly. Still, suppose an individual is suspicious about these tips. In that case, it is suggested that one should take professional certifications from a reputable institute to get vast knowledge and academic certificates in hair beautification. In Australia, you can apply to get Recognition Prior Learning (RPL) qualification of <a href=\"../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Certificate III in Hairdressing (SHB30416)</a> to settle a registered license to open a hairdressing business and know more about how to get healthy hair.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Professional Tips for Hair Treatment', 'How To Get Healthy Hair,  Professional Tips for Hair Treatment', 'Professional Tips for Hair Treatment', 'professional-tips-for-hair-treatment.jpeg', NULL, '2021-11-29 17:30:57', '2021-12-01 16:16:48'),
(47, 7, 'What Are The Differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists: Dissimilarity and Similarity', 'what-are-the-differences-between-hairdressers-and-hair-stylists-dissimilarity-and-similarity', 5, 'We will provide the differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists in this blog. So, let\'s move forward and clear your confusion about those two components.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You may be surprised to know that the terms of hairdressers and hairstylists hold different positions in the beauty industry. Like, both of the professions have to perform individually where the prime task is to perform in hair designing and cutting. Still, the job responsibilities are quite the same along with another task. However, many high-standard saloons recruit both <a href=\"../../blogs/how-can-hairdressing-be-more-advanced-in-the-future\">hairdressers</a> and hairstylists under special abilities and qualifications. Even there is a slight difference in salaries and facilities between a hairdresser and hairstylist.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Main while, you can\'t get to catch the prominent hairdressers and hairstylists as both get the same platform to perform. But for your broader idea, we manage to do some differentiation between those two professions. Making the contrast of salary, job responsibilities, types, limitations, and career paths, we will provide the differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists in this blog. So, let\'s move forward and clear your confusion about those two components.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Who is Hairdresser?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Core Importance of Digital Marketing (12).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A hairdresser is an individual hair maker or artist assigned to do hair art to change or maintain the person\'s outlook. Even they do hair cutting, coloring, and suitable hairstyles based on the client\'s demand. Some countries use hairdressers as a hairstylist and other names. Hairdressers are well trained and very professionally skilled in hair cutting, processing, and texturing in many ways. They also serve customers in washing, shampooing, curling, treating hair, and doing straightening. They are even qualified to provide essential advice for hair-making jobs and offer various suggestions according to the face shape and length. Hairdressers are professionally recognized to do endorsements depending on local qualifications and experience. Hairdressers also stay up-to-date on the modern trends in haircuts and styles.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Who is Hairstylist?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Core Importance of Digital Marketing (11).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The term a hairstylist is just another form of a hairdresser. This is the most popular and usable word in the beauty industry. But depending on the work performance and duties, hairstylists are meant to be much specified and qualified professionals in the hairstyling sector. Doing various tasks in high-end saloons like curls, perm, updos, creative hair designs, and the list is long. Hairstylists help clients to decide the look they want and assist in creating a perfect haircut for special occasions. In some cases, they are appointed to visit the celebrity as celebrity hairstylists where they can show their creativity.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists: Dissimilarity and Similarity:</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>The similarity of Hairdressers and Hairstylists&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before discussing the differences between hairdressers and hairstylists, we will get to know all the similarities. Perhaps, both professions have a widespread number of similarities where you can\'t define any core dissimilarities. Additionally, we compress the expected points for those hair styling professions below,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Both of the hair apparel jobs have widespread units to work in, and those refer to an occupation that involves cutting and styling hair to make an incredible result for clients\' satisfaction.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From both side services, they offer paid washing, shampooing, cutting, coloring, curling, straightening, and treating hair to their clients. Even the materials and tools are the same to use where there is no need to add anything extra.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition, to perform in haircut, both of the job lines should have skills and abilities to present their creativities, good communication skills, focus attention in details, good interpersonal capabilities and most importantly well-management qualities.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Both titles need proper education qualifications and years of experience in apprenticeship. Even a higher degree in equivalent subjects of hair design will give privileges for both positions in the beauty hairdressing industry.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Dissimilarity of Hairdressers and Hairstylists&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As the dissimilarities between hairdressers and hairstylists are very low to count but still, here, we will cover some critical differences between hairdressers and hairstylists for your better understanding. So, let\'s get started with the idea about dissimilarities of hairdressers and hairstylists.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Salary Range </strong><a href=\"https://www.payscale.com/research/AU/Job=Hairdresser_%2F_Hairstylist/Hourly_Rate\"><strong>Source</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An intermediate hairdresser with 1-4 years of experience gets a total average compensation of AU$ 22 as per the conditions. A mid-level hairdresser with experience of 5-9 years can earn an average of AU$ 23.53 based on 63 salaries, and a higher experienced hairdresser gets the compensation of 24.50 based on 114 salaries by having 10-15 years.<br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Core Importance of Digital Marketing (7).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Note: Those rates include tips, bonus, and overtime pay for each category of hair expertise.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the other hand, an introductory hairstylist with 1-4 years of experience gets an average total compensation of AU$ 21.50 based on 17 salaries. Where a mid-level hairstylist earns AU$ 23 based on 48 salaries, and a higher-experienced with 10-19 years experienced hairstylist gets AU$ 25 based on 42 salaries.<br /><br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Core Importance of Digital Marketing (8).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /><br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Note: Those rates include tips, bonus, and overtime pay for each category of hair expertise.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Qualifications&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For a hairdresser, having a minimum high school degree and advanced qualification is a must. Like others, having an <a href=\"../../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\">RPL (Recognition of Prior learning) certificate III in Hairdressing</a> will make your career smoother. Hairdressing may be obligatory to have a cosmetology license from the state authority.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Oppositely, a hairstylist refers to having high schooling or college degree to get internship or apprenticeships opportunities. At least, you need to have an <a href=\"https://itecounsel.com/SHB50216/course\">RPL Certificate I &amp; II in Saloon Assistance</a> to get qualified as a professional hairstylist. Usually, training and qualities development is necessary, and there needs no license to acquire to become a hairstylist.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Job Responsibilities&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hairdressers,&nbsp;</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a professional hairdresser, you\'ll be qualified to offer any of the following services:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Washing and blow-drying hair;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Semi-permanent to permanent hair dyeing;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Artificial hair extensions and weaves;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Haircutting in extensive creations;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chemical relaxing and straightening;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hair plugs, wig fitting, and wig styling;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Braiding and styling hair on demand.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hair Stylist,&nbsp;</strong></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cutting and washing hair;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating volume and adopting hair designs;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating the various haircuts illusion through techniques;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Styling hair for special occasions.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Braiding hair and giving an artificial vibe;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating popular styles, period hairstyles, etc.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Become a celebrity hair expert or counselor.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So far, we have had a brief discussion about the key differences along with the similarities between hairdressers and hairstylists. Though the work patterns are almost the same for both job positions, still those minor dissimilarities are not neglectable in real life.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists', NULL, 'differences-between-hairdressers-and-hair-stylists.png', 'Differences Between Hairdressers and Hair Stylists', '2021-12-09 15:56:36', '2022-01-11 17:48:42');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(48, 7, 'How to Become Beautiful from Head to Toe- Step by Step Guides', 'how-to-become-beautiful-from-head-to-toe-step-by-step-guides', NULL, 'It is known that beauty remains in the eyes of the beholder. Thereby, you no need to toggle God\'s creation. It might be a good practice to abide by such a statement but not always implementable.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is known that beauty remains in the eyes of the beholder. Thereby, you no need to toggle God\'s creation. It might be a good practice to abide by such a statement but not always implementable. It is always required for everyone to be presentable at home and also, in the workplace or for personal outlook maintenance; Considering the take care of your body and skin is key for a healthy mind and body.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this growing age of technologies, there has been a rapid proliferation in the Cosmetic Industry. Beauty therapy is associated with the provision and application of well-trained beauticians of a wide range of treatments and cosmetic methods. The early research proves that the concept of beauty therapy dates back to ancient Greek and Egyptian civilizations, wherein beauty treatments were carried out. The application of skin creams and oil treatments was conventional, while these eras were evidence of their usability, as suggested by archaeologists. Both males and females used to wear cosmetics during this time, including facial treatment.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to the Australian Government\'s Job Outlook service, the Cosmetic industry is growing exponentially, with around 25,000 vacancies expected over the following five years. Companies are looking for professionals who are responsible, well-groomed, and communicate well with others. So, let\'s talk about how to become beautiful from head to toe- step by step guides.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>How To Be Beautiful from Head to Toe?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Beauty therapy training is developed to ensure that the graduates learn skills relevant to the needs of employers and clients in the beauty industry. Even you can be more efficient while you have the qualification of Recognition of Prior Learning (RPL) in Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy (SHB40115) and Diploma of Beauty Therapy (SHB50115). From all those professional courses, you can apply those techniques to be beautiful from head to toe. So, let\'s talk about all those nursing facts of your beautification operation and get enlightened with a different charm.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hair Care&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the most important facts about your beauty is to make sure you are taking good care of your hair. Hair is very sensitive and reactive like you can\'t use anything that doesn\'t suit you. Make a routine for doing shampoo, trim and other caring components daily. Click and learn more about how to get healthy hair with professional tips for hair treatment.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Dry Skin Protection&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your skin tone might be different, and it varies from person to person. Especially for dry skin, you can\'t pick and apply any of the beauty products without just examining them. There are some healthy tips given below, and get to know some of the best beauty tips and recommended products to take care of your dry skin.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advance Beauty Therapy&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nowadays, you will find many advanced beauty treatments that will give a natural vibe to your look. Many beauty industries are paying more attention to the mix of modern technology and natural ingredients. You will find many beauty therapists around you; they offer multiple packages to achieve your ultimate beauty goal.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Beauty Essentials&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can\'t carry all of your beauty products along with you while you are out of your house. Even the parlours are also very expensive to visit daily. So, it is best to put some of the essential products into your carrier and add a list of beauty essentials that everyone should have in their travel bag.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use Light Make-up&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The use of gorgeous or more focusing makeup has gone a long ago. In this modern era, women are becoming more skin protective and getting more comfortable putting light makeup on all events or parties. Moreover, once light makeup was just a trend for working women, and now every woman is adopting this old form just to look natural.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Right Foundation Color&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the internet, you will find various makeup arts on famous celebrities or models. But in reality, you can\'t maintain those artificial colours tones according to your skin. Even those need professional hands to draw and expertise to remove. Those trendy makeups are only used for glamourous programs and magazine photoshoots. So, it is always best to prefer light makeup or natural foundation shades that suit your face tone.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hairdressing and Hair Art&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can be more pretty when arranging your hair or design to look beautiful than regular looks if you want to experience something innovative with your haircut or hairdressing. Then it is best to follow those haircutting tips for women and learn how to practice the haircut at home. Rather than to go an expensive salon, you can trim your hair easily by following those guides.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Shape Lips Color&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the attractive parts is your lips. Perhaps, you can apply dark or light lipstick shades matching your dress and facial tone. It is not always preferable to use dark colours rather than to use any natural lips hue. Lips art is also a part of your beautification. Using any of the colours can\'t express to look good where matte lips are always best.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Hand Care and Nail Design&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Having regular household chores can destroy your hand by moisturizing continuously. Taking some regular moisturizing cream or glycerine can heal those damaged cells and help recover your soft touch. Even doing manicures and pedicures is a great solution to bring your hand and feet to the natural form. You can also make some aesthetic vibe by making nail arts and polish dry faster. Actually, professionals are pretty much good at those from hand treatments to nail polish removal is easier for them.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Get Soft Feet and Smooth Body Skin&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide some extra care to your feet and body skin. Applying hair removal cream can destroy your soft skin, and over time, it can cause trouble with rashes and itches. Always feel comfortable for soft and smooth body skin with a razor or natural waxing. It is good to apply to soften lotion or Vaseline all over the body before heading for bed. Give your body tissues some rest or relax circulation pressure with natural ingredients or oil massages. &nbsp; </span></p>', NULL, 'how to become beautiful from head to toe', NULL, '6d86cc8b-6ff1-42fe-b049-35f06f35fb3c.jpg', NULL, '2021-12-20 17:28:27', '2022-01-17 08:21:34'),
(49, 7, 'Holiday Makeup: How to Glow at Your Next Party', 'holiday-makeup-how-to-glow-at-your-next-party', NULL, 'During holidays, parties and events are frequently arranged. And, women try to follow such popular tips for their special looks these days', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thinking about </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">how to glow at your next party</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? For women, this may be a concern, especially on holidays. Women generally like to wear makeup and try different looks in various seasons. So standing out with glow at any festivity is a desire of almost all females.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many makeup ways, styles, and tips nowadays. Again, modern makeup artists experiment with many looks on models. Those become famous among people and new trends.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During holidays, parties and events are frequently arranged. And, women try to follow such popular tips for their special looks these days. Even those who normally do not put makeup on their faces also do at parties. Certainly, there is nothing wrong with using a bit of extra sparkle and color to enjoy a party.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today we are going to discuss some ways and tricks of makeup. It will give you information to glow at your holiday parties.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Holiday Makeup: How to Glow at Your Next Party</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Begin and Finish with a Healthy Skin</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (35).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Having healthy skin is always a blessing. Before any party, maintaining a fixed routine for fresh skin is equally important. And expert makeup artists highly appreciate it. A clean, poreless, and smooth skin supports any type of makeup look to give it a more amazing look.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you are in your 20s or 40s, it is necessary to know how to keep the skin firm. Below are some tips for healthy skin-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keep your skin clean and mosturised.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Avoid cruelty-free makeup products.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sleep well.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Eat fresh and green vegetables.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Drink enough water daily.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These regulations are for all who want good makeup at a party.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Perfectly Completed Face-Makeup</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (36).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is nothing glamorous than a polished yet simple look. Choose your type of foundation, face powder, blush, and all other things for a neat party face. You can select your own style or follow any favorite recent trend. Whatever you choose ends it giving it a flawless finish. Makeup tutorials are also available on the internet. The basic steps and tips maybe like this-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clean your face and moisturise.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make a base on the face.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don&rsquo;t forget neck areas.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Avoid a heavy layer of foundation.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Conceal blemishes or dark circles.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose every color according to your skin tone.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Eye Makeup</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (38).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Eye makeup is the most important part of attending parties. It gives an appealing look to grab people&rsquo;s attention. A nicely highlighted eyes can bring you all the superb compliments for your makeup. Especially if you attend a party on holiday, you must give time for this makeup section. Many people believe that we should do eye makeup after creating a face base.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wear fake eyelashes, eyeliner, kajal, everything to make it complete. But a few things to focus on are-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Start using an eye cream if you have dark circles.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to change your eye color, wear contact lenses.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don&rsquo;t hesitate to avoid any makeup step or product if you have an allergy.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Full-looking Eye-brows</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Eyebrows complete a face, and humans have different types of eyebrows. Keeping it shaped and highlighted is necessary to glow at an event. There are many tools and treatments nowadays to keep it beautiful. Beauty-conscious ladies take care of eyebrows regularly. But it is not a time-consuming process. You can easily trim your brows just before any party. A few tricks for eyebrow makeup are-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trim eyebrows according to your face shape.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use a brow comb to set them in a place.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fill eyebrow color by pencil or brush.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do eyebrows arch around the eye for a sharper look.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Colorful dyeing can give a fancy look.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Lip Makeup</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (39).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lip makeup or lipstick is very important for any purpose of outgoing makeup. A perfect shade of lipstick can give an instant gorgeous look. Again, you can consider lipsticks as a savior of diminished makeup. Taking care of lips is also important, especially if they are dry. Apply lip masks, scrubs, and balm to enjoy smooth lip skin. Tips for lip makeup for a party include-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose lipstick color according to weather, time of day, and dress.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is good to apply a thin layer of foundation on the lips.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use liner before putting color.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Try to buy long-lasting colors with vitamin-e.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also make glitter lips, as it is a recent trend.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Setting Hair</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (40).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A good hairdo can make you confident to head out for any party. This part of makeup helps you to catch a notch style easily. But, like other parts of the body, the hair also needs extra care and treatments. That is why we should regularly look after our hair. And, at any holiday party, giving a little bit extra effort can set our hair amazingly. Some useful hairdo tips for you-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do shampoo well; if possible, apply a hair mask before it.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before styling, dry and brush your hair well.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pick any easy and comfortable style.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can straighten and curl your hair. Also, you can select any stick hair color for a fancy look.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To end up the topic, let&rsquo;s look into a few overall tips for your next party-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After selecting a dress, focus on choosing the best makeup products.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While doing party makeup, remember it doesn&rsquo;t mean you need to go overboard with makeup.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose festive colors.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use good quality and waterproof makeup.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don&rsquo;t forget to give a finishing touch.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don&rsquo;t touch your makeup frequently.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Carry your makeup essentials for a quick touch-up.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So? </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">how to glow at your next party</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? I believe it is clear now. However, though it is easy to get instant results with modern makeup products, following simple beauty hacks regularly really matters. Again, we usually focus on holiday parties and tours. But this is also the time to concentrate on building up good habits for our health. Continuing these habits can bring long-term benefits for our skin, hair, nails, and overall health. Then glowing at any event in any season will not be a tension anymore.</span></p>', NULL, 'How to Glow at Your Next Party', NULL, 'holiday-makeup-how-to-glow-at-your-next-party.png', NULL, '2022-01-03 03:04:48', '2022-01-11 17:47:12'),
(50, 7, 'How to Monitor and Evaluate Remedial Massage Treatments Helps to Grow The Massage Career', 'how-to-monitor-and-evaluate-remedial-massage-treatments-helps-to-grow-the-massage-career', NULL, 'Basically, monitor and evaluating remedial massage treatments is a core unit of the diploma of remedial massage course. This course unit relates the skills and knowledge of an expert remedial massage therapist.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To get an <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">established career in the massage industry</a>, remedial massage is one kind of massage technique that has a great demand in the market. Along with relaxation and health treatments, the practices of remedial and other relevant massages directly contribute to the massage industry. Now, most massage therapists may or may not have the idea of a monitor and evaluating remedial massage. For them, it might be new as this is a completely new term, or you can assume an advanced version of remedial massage qualification.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Basically, monitor and evaluating remedial massage treatments is a core unit of the diploma of remedial massage course. This course unit relates the skills and knowledge of an expert remedial massage therapist. The competency of massage skills applies following State/Territory legislation or to meet the Australian and New Zealand code of practice to start a massage therapy centre. If you are eager to meet a new goal of your massage career, you have a good opportunity to make it more sufficient under your qualification.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Benefits of Doing Monitor and Evaluate Remedial Massage Treatments Professionally</strong><br /><br /></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Career Development</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you are done with your initial qualification of massage courses, and now you may want to build a sharp career into this. Then you can choose to get an <a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RPL in diploma of Remedial massage</a> and complete the monitor and evaluate treatment unit under the based course. In the long term, you may be able to get more solid works under the same industry with better earnings.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Periodic Course of Units</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thus, this course unit is a part of remedial massage qualifications. It may be possible for you to complete this course unit within a short period of time if you are compatible with the assessment requirement. This unit of the core is much more practical as this program include:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Workshops&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Drop-in sessions&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Peer mentoring&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Math\'s and writing resources&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Resume and career guidance.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Recognized Massage Therapist</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you fully complete the certificate or diploma in Remedial massage accredited qualifications. That time, you will be counted as a nationally recognized massage therapist. Some candidate also needs to evolute their recognition with more skills and an experienced one. For that, this unit of remedial massage course is perfectly fit and secured to get a therapist license.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (47).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Easy Entry and Enrolment Process</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Basically, no special recommendations or requirements are applicable for the enrolment process. Still, Candidates should maintain many follow-up things under the government educational policies. Anyone with a suitable position and skills can easily get the chance to pass the eligibility test. Even the enrolment process is very much handy and takes less time to get qualified.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Option to Start a Business</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Suppose you are done with your remedial massage treatment practice. You can apply for a trade license to open a massage therapy centre in your area. Not only can you get a great job, but you can also complete this academic training and skills assessment just to be a part of the business. You can get more facilities and options to start your own massage counselling centre in Australia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What are The Things Mainly Focused on Evaluate Remedial Massage Course?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The factors are considered when determining the need for adjustment to treatment plan based on the client evaluation outcome&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>The presence of complicating factors: anatomical, medical, biomechanical, psychological</li>\r\n<li>The practitioner characteristic: size, shape, biases</li>\r\n<li>The patient characteristic: size, flexibility, age, and psychosocial</li>\r\n<li>The stage of degeneration: dysfunction, instability, degeneration</li>\r\n<li>Clinical effect desired: Mechanical, Neurological, thermodynamical, hemodynamic, lymphatic, psychological</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Assessment Requirements for Monitor and Evaluate Remedial Massage Treatments (HLTMSG008) </strong><a href=\"https://training.gov.au/TrainingComponentFiles/HLT/HLTMSG008_AssessmentRequirements_R1.pdf\"><strong>(Source)</strong></a><strong> </strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Performance Evidence</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The nominee must exhibit evidence of the capability with the achievement. The studies are outlined in elements and performance criteria in a different department and manage tasks. <strong>The candidates must provide the evidence that they have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Conducted the activities summarised in the implementation criteria of this unit during at least 200 hours of massage under client consultation position.</li>\r\n<li>Handled at least 50 remedial massage assessments and therapy sessions - clients can be both include males and females from different stages of age with assorted methods.</li>\r\n<li>Monitored and evaluated treatments provided to at least 5 different clients with at least 2 therapies per client.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Knowledge Evidence</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The candidate must demonstrate the fundamental learning required to actually conclude tasks outlined in elements and implementation<strong> standards of this unit, operational tasks and manage contingencies in the context of job responsibilities. This contains details of permitted and ethical considerations (national and state/territory) for monitoring and evaluation:&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Children in the workplace</li>\r\n<li>Codes of conduct</li>\r\n<li>Duty of care</li>\r\n<li>Informed consent</li>\r\n<li>Mandatory reporting</li>\r\n<li>Practitioner / client boundaries</li>\r\n<li>Privacy, confidentiality, and disclosure</li>\r\n<li>Records management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>(Assessment Requirements for HLTMSG008 Monitor and evaluate remedial massage treatments Date this document was generated: &copy; Commonwealth of Australia, 2021 Skills IQ)</strong></h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Work role boundaries</li>\r\n<li>Working within the scope of practice</li>\r\n<li>Offering patience that requires referral to a medical practitioner</li>\r\n<li>Work healthy and with safety precautions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (48).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Assessment Conditions</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Skills must have been confirmed in the workplace or in a simulated environment that echoes workplace conditions. The following conditions must be needed for this unit:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Use of suitable facilities, equipment, and resources, including:&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><strong>Client information &ndash; case history, treatment plan </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Private consultation area </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Adjustable height massage table </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Towels/sheets for draping </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Oils/balms </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Hot/cold packs </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Administerial supports</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not just for being a good massage therapist, but also, you can make your move into a good one while you have opportunities. This unique course, \'monitor and evaluate remedial massage treatments, helps grow the massage career on a decorative level. You can get lots of potential skills and knowledge while completing the units of this massage course. But before that, you may require to complete all the essential assessment requirement terms and conditions to meet the qualification.</p>', NULL, 'Monitor and Evaluate Remedial Massage Treatments', NULL, 'monitor-and-evaluate-remedial-massage-treatments.jpeg', NULL, '2022-01-11 03:29:49', '2022-01-12 17:12:36'),
(51, 7, 'Let\'s Make a Quick Look at The Important Hair Cutting Tools and Products Used in A Saloon', 'let-s-make-a-quick-look-at-the-important-hair-cutting-tools-and-products-used-in-a-saloon', NULL, 'Hairdressing and taking care of hair is more tension-free now.', '<p>Important haircutting tools and products are not many. Barber or hairdressers have been <a href=\"../../blogs/how-can-hairdressing-be-more-advanced-in-the-future\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">providing hair shaping services</a> since the earliest time. And, they used to need some basic tools. These are those tools without which a hair salon cannot run. But these days we can see various tools at the modern salons. Experts have invented many updated machines and products for hair. So, hairdressing and taking care of hair is more tension-free now.</p>\r\n<p>Again, as the essential equipment is only a few, you can easily find those out. Standard products come with different materials and prices. So, starting a salon business is also possible with less capital. Today, we will talk about such necessary things used in a salon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Some of the Important Hair Cutting Tools and Products Used in a Saloon&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s see some of the important hair cutting tools a salon needs to keep in their working desk-</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Comb &amp; Hairbrush</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (60).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Comb and hair brushes are two common and essential items at any salon. They come in different sizes and shapes. A quick comb before a haircut helps to arrange any tangled hair. For curly hair, a wide-tooth comb is good. And for different hair cutting, thinner combs are also useful.</p>\r\n<p>Again, hairbrushes are also for different haircuts, styles, and coloring purposes. Hairbrushes are made of different materials. But as a cutting tool, professionals use combs much.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Hair Clippers</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This tool is necessary for short hair cuts. Normally cosmetologists keep various sized clippers. It helps to do fades and military haircuts. Clippers work like scissors but have sharpened comb-like blades. It is available in both electrical and manual mechanisms. The advantage is that it can cut hair all the way close to the skin smoothly. Professionals sometimes also use it to trim beards.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Hair Cutting Scissors</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (57).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Every hair salon keeps different kinds of hair cutting shears or scissors. It is a must-have tool without which you cannot even cut your own hair. But all scissors are not for hair. Haircutting scissors have hooks. These kinds of big handled and good quality shears give comfort and ensure precise cutting. Scissors also need regular maintenance for the best service.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Thinning and Texturing Shears</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>These two tools look similar but have differences in function. Thinning shears give a cut softer Look after scissor works. You can do away with excess weight from hair with the help of smaller teeth.</p>\r\n<p>Texturing shears help to add more volume and texture to a haircut. It works well&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>on thick hair but is useful for all hair types. It has wide teeth and significant gaps between teeth.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Trimmer</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (58).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Trimmer tool helps to trim your hair perfectly. It has a small width and has two or more sliding blades. This small tool also gives precise cutting to style facial hair. There are different trimmer types, including beard, hair, ear and nose trimmers, and so on. And their blades are different too. Trimmer is a standard device that you can find at hair salons.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Dryers</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (59).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hairdryer and blow dryer machines are similar and ease the process of haircutting. If you visit a salon for a cut, but your hair is still wet, you cannot have a good haircut. Also, professionals want to do shampoo before a cut if necessary.</p>\r\n<p>To dry wet hair, experts prefer hair dryers. The purpose of the blow dryer is also the same, but it is mostly used for styling hairs. It is also used in other body parts.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Straight Razor</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Every salon keeps quality and handy razors. This tool removes hair quickly and adds a texture to the cut. Along with traditional razors, there are also many types of modern razors. For example, straight razors have interchangeable blades. Its ergonomic finger design is user-friendly. Experts operate this kind of balanced tool at salons for perfect hair cutting and shaping.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Sectioning Clips</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Sectioning clips help to section hair before highlighting, dry cutting, or styling. Don\'t confuse it with fashion clips; these are different. It works by holding a large amount of hair at a time without falling. This process supports a faster, easier way to work. Good clips never slip, slide or leave marks on the hair. So, this small item is really useful for professionals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Now we will discuss 5 products that are needed to be available in any hair salon:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Shampoo</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (56).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>An excellent haircut starts with a really good shampoo. A good barber or hairdresser prefers to shampoo if your hair is oily. It is difficult to cut dirty or oily hair precisely. Again, clean hair shows the exact and neat shape after any cut. So, you can consider this as a necessary product. And, almost every salon wants to keep a shampoo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Water Bottle</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A water bottle is a simple but important thing a hairdresser or barber needs. This handy product helps them to mist the hair lightly. And it helps throughout the process of cutting and shaping hair properly. Again, some bottles come with continuous spray features, which are more helpful.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Split End Remedy</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Split ends are irritating. That is why hairdressers snip them off and use good remedies nowadays. Though it is not mandatory and depends on the customer\'s choice, it is useful. They first put the scissors down, apply the remedy on the splits and seal them. A good quality remedy also cures your frayed follicles. And any cut suits best on smooth hairs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Last Words</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Now you know the basic and Important hair cutting tools and products. We know that hair is an important part of people\'s personalities. And they like to shape it not to look perfect but for a neat and healthy look. Barbers have been doing great jobs for years in this field. Again, many of us also prefer to cut our own and dear ones\' hairs at home. So, knowing the necessary tools\' names and their functions helps a lot.</p>\r\n<p>However, we should remember that regular haircuts <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-get-healthy-hair-6-professional-tips-for-hair-treatment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">promote healthy hair growth</a>. It stops the spread of split ends through the strands. So, don\'t ignore your hair; take care of it routinely. And, we have mentioned that <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-set-up-a-mobile-hairdressing-business-in-australia\">opening a hair salon</a> with the essential tools is also not expensive. If you have such a plan, know the items you need and start your journey.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Important Hair Cutting Tools and products', NULL, 'important-hair-cutting-tools-and-products.png', NULL, '2022-01-23 09:52:43', '2022-01-23 10:27:52');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(52, 7, 'Best Trendy Holiday Makeups for Your Next Party to Look Stunning', 'best-trendy-holiday-makeups-for-your-next-party-to-look-stunning', NULL, 'If you want to know how to glow at your next party, then read the last line of this article. Here we described some party-ready tricks and techniques in detail for preternatural glow makeup.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The festive mood is floating upon us, especially in December to January. To attend a weekend party or holiday get-to-gather, you may <a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-become-beautiful-from-head-to-toe-step-by-step-guides\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">prefer to look amazing</a> among all the guests. It is great to have some self-esteeming while you are at a party. It is not wrong to have a slight glow and sparkle while you are walking on the party floor. To look more confident, add a little extra shine on your face or art your eyes with smoky shades, or you can excuse for more makeup to look bright while clicking photos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Personally, I like Kim Kardashian as her makeup sense is world-class, and she is a sensation influencer for every age of women while it is the matter of makeup. Let\'s see some beauty experts what they said about <a href=\"../../blogs/modern-makeup-trends-for-your-preference\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">makeup trends</a>. Once Pat McGrath said, \"Creativity is your best makeup skill, don\'t be afraid to experiment.\" and \"Beauty is power, and makeup is something that really enhances that; it\'s a woman\'s secret.\" &ndash; Stated by Charlotte Tilbury.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So, understanding your <a href=\"../../blogs/beauty-tips-and-recommended-products-to-take-care-of-dry-skin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">needs and preferences</a>, you may want to look perfect while putting your makeup and overall outfits to appear in winter or summer parties. If you want to know how to glow at your next party, then read the last line of this article. Here we described some party-ready tricks and techniques in detail for preternatural glow makeup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Some Trendy Makeups about How to Look Bright at Your Holiday Party</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Soft Sculpting&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (67).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Soft-sculpting is the soft contouring method for natural-looking cheekbones. Soft-sculpting is applicable to refill the area of standard contouring. It\'s a subtler, more diffused take on the trend that should blend gradually into the skin. So that you may look fresh-faced while still maintaining some description.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Lip Lift Techniques&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (76).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/lip-lift\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Lip lift techniques</a> are one of the trendy lip art designs nowadays. This technique mainly prioritizes the upper line and the lower line of the center of the lips. Lipstick colour also applies on the inside lip of the outer top and bottom corners. Additionally, this makeup creates an illusion of the taller lip to look flat, smooth, and bold while it can generate an intuition of the face focused.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Activate A Luminous Glow&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (75).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For getting a natural or luminous glow, one can use an emollient moisturizer. After preparing the skin with the moisturizer, put some light lapping foundation to set the makeup longer. Some makeup artist suggests this tent is best for any trip or corporate program. When you activate a luminous glow, it will keep the makeup tone alive for around 8 hours. For a natural shinning, use a featherweight liquid foundation or something smooth like Tinted Moisturizer, which will blend seamlessly into the skin for subtle, nearly imperceptible coverage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sculpt and Highlight Slowly&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (72).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To apply to sculpt and highlight, use a tapered contour and turn your brushes a little relaxed. Always grab a powder formula that\'s not too warm or bright-toned. Experts recommended using wetting a highlighter brush before dipping it into a powder highlighter, such as his Soft Glow formula, and applying that softly on the high planes of the face. All time\'s best face artist Dedivanovic says, \"Now that everyone knows how to contour and it\'s become part of their everyday beauty routine; people realize that you can achieve a sculpted look with a lot less makeup,\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Smoke The Eyes Effortlessly</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (71).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Let\'s make your holiday plan with smoky eyeshadows. Use straight to creamy metallic shades over your eye\'s lids. Master metals eye colour palette pigments can be modified with a pro mixing liquid for creating molten, foil effect or smoky shadows. It can be bold or thin to blend into lids to have smoky effects based on the user preferences.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sparkly Purple Eyes&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (74).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nothing feels quite as festive as sparkles, and that\'s true of any colour. Implement superpowered shimmer into your holiday makeup look with a pretty purple eye shadow (or two, for depth and dimension) that has a glistening, nearly metallic finish &mdash; we love E.L.F.\'s Liquid Glitter Eyeshadow in Purple Reign for achieving this effect. And to make it last? \"Apply lid primer to lock shadow and liner in place,\" Bryant says. Keep the rest of the look neutral, and consider a warmer lip and blush like Dua Lipa did to create an interesting contrast with the cooler purple tones.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Classic Red Lips&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (70).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Red is one of the colors most closely associated with Christmas, so no one will ever fault you for incorporating it into your holiday-party look, especially if you opt for a classic red lip and otherwise low-key makeup. Anya Taylor-Joy went with Rouge Dior Ultra Care Liquid Lipstick in 999. Dior\'s most famous shade of red wears a wash of champagne eye shadow to add some shimmer to the look while still letting her lips be the focus of the look.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Glint Those Eyes&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (68).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wet a dense eyeshadow brush, then dab it into a silver shimmery eye shadow before applying it to the very inner corners of your top eyelid. Then blend outwards with glint shades of a niche colour or multiple tones. Apply those bright glints to look more catchy because your eyes are an important line of your beauty.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Natural Minimal Makeup Look&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (69).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not everyone likes dramatic, bold, and loud makeup, especially for daytime looks and occasions. That\'s where natural makeup glance comes in. It uses a light base to give you an even tone, with subtle colors to accentuate the features. It makes you look \'all peaches and pinks,\' just like you are blushing. It\'s the perfect makeup look when you want to look great, but not all made-up. It has the benefit of making you look flawless while not distracting from your natural features.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who doesn\'t want to look great on a special occasion? If it is a year-end party or any wedding ceremony, then why not make yourself more attractive and spotted among others. You may think having a good outlook, and a lovely dress can always make you the center of attraction. But trust me, putting in some makeup, and extra efforts can hold a good position along with nice outfits. So, you can <a href=\"../../blogs/holiday-makeup-how-to-glow-at-your-next-party\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">follow those mentioned makeup</a> tricks to look stunning to attend a party.</p>', NULL, 'Trendy Holiday Makeups for Party', 'Let\'s not wait to check back while you have opportunities to look gorgeous with your party gaze. We make it easier for you with some easy and trendy holiday makeup for the party.', 'best-trendy-holiday-makeups-for-your-next-party-to-look-stunning.png', NULL, '2022-01-25 15:03:19', '2022-01-25 17:40:30'),
(53, 7, 'Best Marketing and Event Ideas for Hair Salons in Australia', 'best-marketing-and-event-ideas-for-hair-salons-in-australia', 5, 'For every small to big business owner investing in marketing for better promotion is worth it now. Innovative strategies and plans for salons do successful promotion in such fields.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Like other business owners, <a href=\"../blogs/top-10-famous-celebrity-hairdressers-with-biography\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">intelligent hair salon owners</a> nowadays seek different </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">marketing and event ideas for hair salons in Australia</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Yes, we can see the effect of marketing everywhere. For every small to big business owner investing in marketing for better promotion is worth it now. Again, social media platforms are becoming the best medium for digital marketing. Innovative strategies and plans for salons do successful promotion in such fields. To ensure the best services, owners also take help from service providers.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Moreover, physical events for promotional purposes are also influential. There are opportunities for paid promotions for businesses and products in current events. <a href=\"../blogs/how-to-set-up-a-mobile-hairdressing-business-in-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hair salons in Australia</a> promote their services at such events. They also arrange contests and other activities to attract customers.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This article will give you some practical promotional ideas for a hair salon.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Best Marketing and Event Ideas for Hair Salons in Australia</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (81).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Virtual Marketing Ways</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The virtual world is now the best place to promote almost any product. Below are some different tactics to help attract new clients-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>A Good Website</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An up-to-date and well-designed website is a great way to promote any product. It shows your product as clear as a precise haircut gives at first look. Having a website is a smart way to display your products, give offers, and sell them. Readers get details through blogs, check product prices, and see images for ideas.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Again, <a href=\"https://quadque.tech/seo-in-website-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">good search engine optimisation (SEO)</a> benefits a website greatly. It allows you to identify what clients\' interests are. And you can target people to find suitable salons and services. Moreover, good SEO helps rank a website and raise brand value. And you can run google ads to bring new clients into your business too.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Social Media Pages</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are various social media platforms today. And people, especially youngs use, follow, or keep ideas about the new trends. From entertainment to business promotion, these media are performing exceptionally. So, if you are a salon owner, try to create your official page on Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, and others. You can post regular salon updates there. Effective posts of a salon may include tips, offers, working videos, new styles, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Again, a virtual page allows you to target your required audience. You can even boost your posts for better engagement. Thus a page helps to attract new customers. And it speeds up the process of receiving messages, comments, and reviews.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (82).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Take Help From A Influencer&nbsp;</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Social media content creators are playing excellent roles these days. Different influencers have different fan bases on various social platforms. These people usually make entertaining social issues and related content. But as they hold many followers, they are good at marketing too. An influencer has the power to affect the purchasing decisions of people. The reason is their authority, knowledge, status, or relationship with their audience.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Collaborating with an influencer can help to achieve a salon\'s marketing objectives. You can create youtube content short videos of your works according to your budget. Also, you can simply promote your brand name through an influencer. It is a proven marketing strategy now.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Physical Marketing Ways</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (83).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salons owners can invent and run any promotional idea in the salons. Again, there are also other places where they can physically advertise a salon or products. Let\'s see some of the ideas-</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arrange a Contest</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Invent uncommon and interesting contest ideas and invite customers to participate. The contest may be like this- \'tell your seven friends to visit our shop or like our page and get a free haircut.\' Design and organise this type of contest and let people win the gifts. Running contests is not only helpful to advertise a business but also to hold existing customers.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Collaboration with other Business</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Joint ventures give good results to promote your salon business in different places. You can partner with any local business and promote one another. This is actually beneficial for both the business. Again, influencers sometimes promote a business offline. As they visit many social events, they can help in this regard. So, if you can offer them benefits, a salon influencer can also help you.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Create Professional Business Cards</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Raising a business name can be easy through professional cards. It represents a company\'s services, values, and more. And, it is one of the smart and quick ways to inform people. Situations where you don\'t have time to explain or write business information, cards talk there. So, this is a great offline marketing path. You will practically observe the results through new customers and communications.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Attending Networking Events</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a modern hair salon owner, you should attend social and national events. Nowadays, staying connected and updated with new things are important. If you can visit events, you will gather ideas while telling people about your brand. Also, you can meet valuable persons with whom you may collaborate or get ideas from them. So, try to participate in events to expand your network in the market.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Become An Traine</strong></h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-4q3C6vSsE4\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have experience and confidence in your expertise, start offering training. You can offer short-term free training and long-term paid training. This type of session is also an effective way to raise any brand value. Today, expert hairdressers are highly respected and paid globally for their work and knowledge. For example, in Australia, qualified hairdressers through <a href=\"../faq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Recognition of Prior Learning (RPL)</a> are demandable. And, the best course is <a href=\"../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SHB30416 - Certificate III in Hairdressing</a>.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are the standard and most effective </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">marketing and event ideas for hair salons in Australia</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> we have found. We can recommend following everyone who is a new starter or an old owner. Besides, delivering quality service promotion is important for any business today. Sometimes, hair salon owners find it challenging to implement marketing plans. And, it\'s different from any other e-commerce business marketing. But if you follow the particular tricks and strongly apply them, you can get the result. Don\'t forget; you can do it with a small budget. There are many ideas among them; some even don\'t require any investment. So, don\'t hesitate to start your journey of hair salon marketing with confidence. Go forward and turn your hard work into solid benefits. </span></p>', NULL, 'Marketing and Event Ideas for Hair Salons in Australia', NULL, 'best-marketing-and-event-ideas-for-hair-salons-in-australia.png', NULL, '2022-01-29 18:22:33', '2022-02-01 19:44:21'),
(54, 7, 'French Braid vs Dutch Braid Waves: Which is Best?', 'french-braid-vs-dutch-braid-waves-which-is-best', NULL, 'Many of us desire wavy hair but are concerned about causing damage to it by using hair products. Continue reading to know how to get these waves naturally.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\'s true to assume that wavy hair is on-trend, whether it\'s <a href=\"https://www.thehairstyler.com/celebrity-hairstyles/jennifer-lawrence\">Jennifer Lawrence\'s bob wavy hair</a> or Margot Robbie\'s glossy shoulder-length waves. So, if you have naturally wavy hair or not, there are multiple wavy hairstyles that you can give a try. You can flaunt this trendy, sleek wavy hair look in no time with hair styling tools and products. But what if you\'re concerned about causing damage to your hair by using so many chemicals and appliances only to attain the waves you want daily?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If that\'s the case, try French braid or Dutch braid hairstyles, which will give you natural waves without the use of any hair tools or products. The question remains, however: Which is best for you: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">French Braid vs Dutch Braid Waves</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keep scrolling to have a detailed idea about which is best between </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">French braid vs Dutch braid waves</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>French braid&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (8).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is nothing quite as sophisticated and elegant as a French braid. However, French braid weaving is a simple process despite how sophisticated it appears. Each part should have a strand of hair added before braiding. There you have it, you have mastered the basics of a classic french braid.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Dutch braid</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (9).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a Dutch braid, the strands are crossed under another hair strand instead of over. It may appear difficult to a novice, but it is fairly simple! Almost any hair length will work with a Dutch braid except for really short hair.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>French Braid vs Dutch Braid waves</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">French braid creates delicate, gorgeous S waves in your hair with little to no volume. Use a nice hairspray to keep your hair in this lovely style for a long period.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, from the dutch braid, the waves in your hair take on a z pattern. If you leave the braid like this for a while before undoing it, you\'ll end up with large voluminous waves in your hair.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>How to get these waves</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To understand how the waves through these braids are achievable and which is better: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">french braid vs dutch braid waves</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you must first learn how to do these braids properly.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Steps to follow for french braid waves</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (11).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Start by brushing your hair. If your hair is frizzy at this point, use a hair serum to smooth it out. It\'s now entirely up to you whether you want to keep your hair damp or dry while creating French braids.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, if you\'re doing the French braid to get gorgeous waves without damaging your hair with a hair curler, do it with wet, unconditioned hairs. It will give you a stunning hairstyle overnight.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Begin by collecting a sizable portion of hair from the upper center of your head. To achieve a flawless braid, all of the hair sections should come from the same area. Nevertheless, the position on the head where your braid begins does not influence the length of your braid and the waves.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By moving your finger down through the hair sections, divide the hairs into three groups. Two of the three portions are held in one hand, while the third is held in the other. Begin braiding by crossing the right strand to the center, followed by the left strand to the center. And while doing these crossovers add some new hairs to each part every time.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As you progress with your braiding, when you find yourself running out of hair, continue the standard braiding method and finish the braid with a ponytail holder. Keep this braid for 1-2 hours and then undo it to see the phenomenal waves your hair has got without even using the curlers.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Steps to follow for Dutch braid waves</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (10).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To get the gorgeous volume from the Dutch braid, begin by detangling your hair in the same manner as the French braid. Then divide the diameter of your head into three sections. The right strand should be held in your right hand, while the other two should be held with your left.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Take the hair strand of the right hand and cross it under the middle hair strand. Then cross the hair strand of the left hand under the new middle hair strand. The important thing to observe here is that the strands are going beneath rather than over the other strands.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Repeat this procedure until you reach a point on your neck where you can no longer add a new hair section. Finish the hair braiding with a ponytail holder. Keep this braid for a fair amount of time and then undo you. You have your gorgeous voluminous waves.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Which is best?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you\'re wondering which one is the best of </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">French braid vs Dutch braid waves,</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> there is no single answer that applies to everyone. Both the hairstyle needs some time to skill at it and get those effortless waves depending on individuals. Again, if you prefer the volume in your hair that comes from a Dutch braid, then French braid light waves are not for you.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">French braid creates gorgeous natural-looking waves that go perfectly with any outfit on any occasion. In the long run, though, it protects your hair from heat damage. Furthermore, it keeps hair nice and tidy for days when you don\'t want your hair to mess up your face every time a breeze flows by. On the other hand, a Dutch braid adds bouncy voluminous waves in a way that a French braid can\'t. It gives you an easy-to-do, attractive hairstyle for a certain occasion. So take some time to consider how you\'d like to see your hairstyle on that particular day, and then select which one you should do.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hair and braids have been a great combination for eons. French and Dutch braids are two of these braids that have slain the hair industry for quite a long time. When each of these braids is left on for a set amount of time, it gives different waves to hair. But, before picking between </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">french braid vs dutch braid waves</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, consider your hair texture, type, and the events you going to attend with this hairstyle. Put a little hair spray on your hair and dress it up with some hair accessories for a look that seems effortless. You are all <a href=\"../blogs/how-to-get-healthy-hair-6-professional-tips-for-hair-treatment\">set to have a good hair day</a>!</span></p>', NULL, 'French Braid vs Dutch Braid Waves', 'Many of us desire wavy hair but are concerned about causing damage to it by using hair products. Continue reading to know how to get these waves naturally.', 'french-braid-vs-dutch-braid-waves.jpg', 'French Braid vs Dutch Braid Waves', '2022-02-28 03:40:57', '2022-03-24 05:02:33'),
(55, 7, 'How long does it take for acne scars to fade: The Ultimate Guide', 'how-long-does-it-take-for-acne-scars-to-fade-the-ultimate-guide', NULL, '\"How long does it take for acne scars to fade away?\" most people are curious about this. But these acne scars are easily treatable with proper medical care.', '<h1><strong>How long does it take for acne scars to fade: The Ultimate Guide</strong></h1>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the most common skin problems that both men and women face is acne problem. This lifelong problem usually starts at the teenage days and continues to adulthood. Some even suffer from it throughout their whole life. However, having acne or pimple is not the real problem yet. The actual problem starts when they leave an acne mark or spot on the face. Acne scars leave permanent marks on the skin and sometimes discolor the skin to the point that it does not match the actual skin color. This leaves us with the question of how long does it take for acne scars to fade or do they ever go away. Unfortunately, some people mix things up and think that acne marks and acne scars are the same. However, the acne mark disappears within three to six months and gets better when the skin changes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the other hand, acne scars leave a permanent mark on the skin. That can mean a hole in the skin, leaving scars similar to chickenpox, big red spots known as keloids. Fading acne scars is a much debatable issue on which some claim it fades naturally, and some do not.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>What Causes Acne Scar</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/what causes acne scar\" alt=\"what causes acne scar\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acne scar is caused by the permanent damage to the skin. Therefore, it is advised not to touch the acne or poke it in any way. Some gentle pokes today can lead to some permanent damages tomorrow. Apart from this, due to acne healing in which collagen takes part, sometimes it does not get enough time to heal one on which another acne appears, leaving a mark. Collagen helps the skin heal, which produces more than enough in some cases that later turn into a pit or hole. Acne damages the tissue of skin damage, leading to a permanent mark.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Types of Acne Scars</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Types of Acne Scars\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several types of acne scars. Having a better understanding of these or how they act will help one identify and treat them accordingly. Here are the acne scars that one should be careful about:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Rolling Scars:</em></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The long term acne issue causes rolling scars in one type of acne scar. This scar is more round and has a sloppy edge on the skin. Rolling scars are the most common type of acne scar.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Boxcar Scars:</em></strong><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boxcar scars have more sharp edges and are difficult to treat. In addition, the depth of this scar is more distinct from one another. Boxcar scars are more in an oval shape.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Icepick Scars:</em></strong><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Icepick scars are shaped in a pointy way. Sometimes they look like open pores with a more deep hole in the skin. This type of scar occurs where the skin is more on the thinner side.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Raised Scars:</em></strong><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The raised scars have occurred when the acne are healed, and while in the process of healing, excessive collagens are gathered on the surface of the skin where a lump is created that appears to be red.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Discoloration:</em></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Scar discoloration happens when the scar is healed but it leaves a dark permanent mark on the skin. However, discoloration is not as bad as the other acne scars but still unbearable for the person.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Keloids:</em></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Keloid scars are the same as raised scars, but the difference between a keloid scar and the raised scar is that a keloid scar occurs with overgrowth of collagen tissue to cover up the acne and is bigger than the actual wound.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Does Acne Scars Get Faded Away Naturally?</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acne scars are much hard to fade away naturally. Acnes are resistant and prone to cause serious damage to the skin resulting in the acne scar. However, some acne scars fade away eventually when the skin changes, which is not the case for many acne. Deep cut acne scars tend to stay longer on the skin. People use many types of home remedies to treat acne scars and some work. Depending on the skin, home remedies may not work on the scars. So, people can never say with full confirmation that acne scars fade away naturally or with home remedies.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Right Way to Treat Acne Scar</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Right Way to Treat Acne Scar\" alt=\"Right Way to Treat Acne Scar\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The way to treat acne scars is different for each type of scar. Therefore, it is best to take advice from the dermatologist for expert opinion. Discoloration scars get better within a few months and are not hard to treat. Treating acne scars with professional experts brings out the best result. The procedures that are used in acne treatments are:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Laser Treatment: </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Laser treatments are one of the most common procedures to treat acne scars. Laser treatments do not take much of the time, but the healing after that tends to be more cautious.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Injections:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Injections are also used to treat the acne scars. Repeated injections treat the acne scars with medicine that helps smoothens the skin while softening the excessive collagen filled spots.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Fillers:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The gaps caused by the acnes are treated through filler pushed on the skin. Fillers fill the hole and make the uneven skin smoother. Fillers can be both permanent and temporary on the skin.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Surgery: </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Along with the other procedures, surgery is also used to treat acne scars. As acne scars are tougher to treat, through surgery, the skin gets tightened or increases the tissue or decreases to make the healing process better.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chemical Peel:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> In a chemical peel, a chemical solution is applied on the skin, which reacts to exfoliate the outer layer of the skin and increases the growth of a new one which gives a better appearance.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>The Final Verdict</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acne scars are surely tough to treat. There is no correct answer to how long does it take acne scars to fade as it depends on the type of skin and method used for treatment. It can take from months to years for these to fade. With the expert suggestions and proper treatment, acne scars will fade away, but that should never be the case for one to feel ugly or not pretty. Everyone is beautiful and should be proud of that. Acne scar is nothing but some blemishes on the skin that are treatable with proper care and medicine.</span></p>', NULL, 'How long does it take for acne scars to fade away', '\"How long does it take for acne scars to fade away?\" most people are curious about this. But these acne scars are easily treatable with proper medical care.', 'how-long-does-it-take-for-acne-scars-to-fade.jpg', NULL, '2022-03-07 16:35:56', '2022-03-28 06:58:19');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(56, 8, 'Does olive oil naturally lighten hair? 8 Ways to Naturally Lighten Hair at Home', 'does-olive-oil-naturally-lighten-hair-8-ways-to-naturally-lighten-hair-at-home', NULL, 'Does olive oil naturally lighten hair? well, In this this article must help you to know the best 8 ways to naturally lighten your hair at home.', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You may use olive oil to improve your hair and scalp\'s health and condition. Olive oil with extra-virgin&nbsp;is somewhat superior to regular olive oil. However, it won\'t have a big effect on the results. With olive oil, you can nourish and strengthen your hair from the root to the tip. It has the ability to stop hair from falling out and thinning. There may be an instantaneous effect on the way light reflects off the strands when olive oil is generously smeared on any color of hair, from lightest blonde to deepest black. But this article must help you to know the best 8 tips to naturally lighten your hair at home.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>8 ways to Naturally Lighten Hair at Home</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Researching a wide range of web literature and interviews with hair experts, we came up with a list of tips for enhancing your hair color at home. To achieve the lightest hair possible without using chemicals, we figured out these&nbsp;substances in your kitchen might make a major impact.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Lemon Juice</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lemons are likely to be in your refrigerator right now. To lighten the&nbsp;hair, you\'ll need plenty of lemon juice, so begin juicing!&nbsp; If you want to lighten your hair at home, this is the best and quickest method. All you need is a little bit of daylight. When activated, lemon juice might lighten your hair. Lemon juice softens and brightens your hair.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To begin, you can add two teaspoons of lemon juice to a cup of water and see if it works. Spray the solution on your hair and let it air dry. After your hair is dry, you can sleep with the mixture in it overnight for best results.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Honey</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/use honey.jpg\" alt=\"honey\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Honey, a natural antibacterial skin care component, may also be a fantastic hair-lightening agent. It\'s certainly already on your cosmetics counter. This is best for those with naturally blonde or light hair.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One tablespoon of cinnamon and one tablespoon of olive oil go into the fourth cup of raw honey in this hair mask. You may also apply one tablespoon of water to your paste if it is too thick. Before using, let the mixture settle for an hour.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Using Baking Soda</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Natural hair lightening can be achieved with the baking soda that is used in banana bread. The only concern is, it is necessary to use hydrogen peroxide in order for the baking soda to work properly. To generate a paste-like consistency, combine the two ingredients in a small bowl.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apply the mixture to your hair&nbsp;after putting it in a glass or plastic container. Using this method, you may get a variety of hair color effects. When applying, it\'s easy to regulate due to its uniformity.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Cinnamon</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cinnamon does more than enhance the flavor of your chai latte. When combined with honey and water, it has the potential to lighten your hair. You can experiment with it on its own, but for the best results, combine all of the components. Cinnamon aids in the activation of honey\'s naturally occurring hydrogen peroxide residues.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add lemon juice, water, and honey to a thick consistency to make cinnamon more effective. After that, apply the mixture to your hair after mixing it in a dish. Let it rest for 30 to an hour after you\'ve saturated your strands. After washing and drying, apply a conditioner.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Apple Cider Vinegar</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Apple Cider Vinegar.jpg\" alt=\"Apple Cider Vinegar\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using apple cider vinegar to slightly lighten your hair and remove oil and dirt from your scalp is a great way to jumpstart hair development. The vinegar in apple cider also aids in the detangling and defuzzification&nbsp;of the hair. It\'s an all-around winner in the hair care arena.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mix equal parts apple cider vinegar and water. Using a spray bottle, lightly mist the hair. Rinse gently and apply conditioner after completely soaking your hair for half an hour.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Sea Salt</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The roots of your hair can benefit from home-made sea salt treatments. It may not be as severe the first day, but if you continue to use sea salt, you may see a noticeable change. Mix sea salt and hot water together. Spray the solution on your hair when it has cooled. When you\'re ready, give it one last rinse to get rid of it.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Use Chamomile</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chamomile tea can be an effective lightening therapy for brunette hair. This would produce a tone shift that would be more apparent in very well environments or in the sunshine itself. It\'s less harsh than&nbsp;other natural products, making it softer.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boil chamomile like tea first. Then, wait for it to cool down before using a spray bottle to put it on. Make sure to cover your hair for at least 30 minutes&nbsp;after you\'ve saturated it with the product. If your hair is dry, you can use&nbsp;hair mask to condition it.</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Vitamin C instead of Lemon</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Vitamin C instead of Lemon.jpg\" alt=\"Vitamin C instead of Lemon\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The active component, vitamin C, can be used instead of the lemon juice if you want a more subtle flavor. If you want to eliminate mineral buildup from your hair, vitamin C is a great alternative to lemon juice. Spray your hair with a mixture of a crushed vitamin C tablet or&nbsp;vitamin C powder and water. Allow your hair to naturally lighten over the course of the night by wearing a shower cap.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusions</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now&nbsp;you know how to safely and naturally brighten your hair overnight at home, you can take advantage of all the options available to you. Natural substances are indeed the way to go when having strong, healthy hair. Prior to resorting to chemicals like bleach, there are various solutions available. Your hair will look sun-kissed and lustrous without all the damage and breakage from harsh chemicals thanks to these natural lightening suggestions. These hair recipes are a great place to start!&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Does olive oil naturally lighten hair? well, In this this article must help you to know the best 8 ways to naturally lighten your hair at home.', 'ways-to-naturally-lighten-hair-at-home.jpg', NULL, '2022-03-24 09:00:05', '2022-03-28 07:45:30'),
(57, 8, '10 Ways to Create the Perfect Salon Interior', '10-ways-to-create-the-perfect-salon-interior', NULL, 'Are you going to design your first salon? Here are some ideas to create the perfect salon interior. Check now!', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When it comes to designing the inside of your salon, we realize that you want to maximize the space available to you. You should consider the interests of your consumers and staff while designing a salon to ensure that it is pleasant, elegant, and relaxing. A well-chosen decor and salon style may accomplish a variety of tasks, from establishing your brand\'s identity to creating a pleasant environment for your consumers. We made this article for you to know the best 10 ways to create the perfect salon interior.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>10 Best Ways to Create the Perfect Salon Interior</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Consider A Beautiful  Floor.jpg\" alt=\"Consider A Beautiful Floor\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Think About the Functionality First</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\'s quite simple to get carried away with small salon decoration ideas, but always keep in mind that salon design for narrow areas should prioritize utility. Effective space management is critical for tiny hair salons, home beauty enterprises, boutique hair salons, or even one-chair salon concepts. Your salon\'s design should be functional for both you and your customers.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Make Your Reception More Exceptional</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We know the initial impression is permanent! What do your customers initially see? The lobby. You want this room to feel comfortable and welcoming. That\'s why salons with sufficient space typically have luxury welcome and waiting spaces furnished with comfy chairs are very important. However, given the size constraint, it is advisable to pick a smaller reception desk that can accommodate a computer or tablet. This desk can be placed at the salon\'s entrance.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Additionally, you can give a couple of comfortable chairs and some magazines. One thing to keep in mind is that the furniture you pick should be small and complement the atmosphere of your salon!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Consider A Beautiful Floor</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The architecture of your salon is vital, so take the time to create a functional floor plan. Consider the location of your washing area if you are operating a hair salon. It should ideally be located in a separate portion of the salon from the rest of the clients. When you\'re getting your hair cleaned and massaged, you want to be entirely relaxed and unobserved. Assure that you respect your client\'s privacy by separating this area. Ensure that any pipes connecting them are concealed to maintain a professional and fashionable appearance for your clients. If you own a beauty salon or a hair salon that offers beauty treatments, aim to have treatment rooms accessible for more private services like waxing. If you\'re limited on space and can only fit one area, consider where therapists may be located around the salon, such as the nail bar.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Keep Natural Looks to Your Salon</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (1).jpg\" alt=\"salon\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nature is at the top of the list of what\'s popular in terms of smaller hair and small beauty salon design ideas. Consider flesh tones and textures, a quiet salon atmosphere, and a pro-environmental posture. Apart from protecting the environment, eco-friendly small hairdressing salons and beauty companies also appeal to a rising number of socially concerned clientele.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Color Adjustment</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When researching tiny salon design ideas, it\'s good to examine the psychology of color. Your color selections send subconscious messages to your clients, have a significant impact on brand identification, and can affect purchase behavior. Pink is associated with sincerity, blue with trust, and green with excellence.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Make A Corner for Photoshoot</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After your customers have experienced your superior services, you may provide a spot for them to take selfies and encourage them to share their post-service photos. Acquire their assistance in tagging your salon for more social media success. You may utilize wall art to convey your brand\'s message, showcase your colors, and act as a stunning backdrop for Instagram images.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Consider A Mobile Salon</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Mobile Salon.jpg\" alt=\"Mobile Salon\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are more things to think about when you have a salon on wheels. It\'s clearly important&nbsp;that nothing in your salon moves when the car is in motion, and it\'s also worth noting that less is absolutely more in this circumstance, since space is more constrained than in other compact salon layouts. So, a mobile salon is a great idea to attract your audience.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Nail Salon Inspiration</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When designing a nail shop for a tiny space, classic style is an excellent method to keep customer conversation focused on the detailed design and limitless color possibilities of your manicure work, rather than on the walls. Choose a spectrum that complements each shade of nail polish and make sure your surfaces are acceptable for the all-important hand selfies.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Make Your Salon Like a Studio</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A studio salon is an innovative concept that enables you to operate your own salon without the hassles or costs associated with beginning a traditional salon company. You have the option of customizing your area to complement your salon\'s brand. It\'s an excellent choice for a new salon. You don\'t need a great number of seats to operate it, and it can easily be done in a small space.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Save Time and Money with Home Salon</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to work from the comfort of your own home while simultaneously saving money on salon expenditures, a home salon is an excellent option! By operating a home salon, you may significantly reduce your monthly expenses on rent, power, water, and personal travel. The most critical step is to evaluate your area. When you know how much room you have, it\'s much easier to select the most appropriate salon equipment for the space.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusions</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several salon design ideas that you may use even on a small budget. The examples covered in this article demonstrate that when it comes to creating a salon with a small&nbsp;space, simplicity is important. Simplicity and a basic style perform very well in small spaces. After considering your target population and deciding on an interior design style, you\'ll have a better idea of the colors and themes in which to design your salon. Consider which flooring and lighting options are ideal for your salon, and ensure that comparable themes run throughout the main floor and smaller rooms to maintain a beautiful design.</span></p>', 'create the perfect salon interior', 'create the perfect salon interior', 'Are you going to design your first salon? Here are some ideas to create the perfect salon interior. Check now!', 'create-the-perfect-salon-interior.jpg', 'create the perfect salon interior', '2022-03-29 14:21:15', '2022-03-31 13:11:34'),
(58, 8, 'How to get permanent residency in Australia as a Massage Therapist', 'how-to-get-permanent-residency-in-australia-as-a-massage-therapist', NULL, 'Do you want to know about how to get permanent residency in Australia as a Massage Therapist? Click now to know more about this!', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage Therapy as a career has grown in popularity in Australia in recent years due to the benefits of reduced academic admission requirements, a high employment rate, and the option to relocate to Australia! Massage Therapists are included on the Short-Term Strategic Occupations Skills List (STSOL), which opens up many top-tier immigration paths for obtaining Permanent Residency in Australia. As a Massage Therapist, you can immigrate to Australia. We have compiled all of the necessary information for obtaining PR in Australia as a massage therapist in one post. Let&rsquo;s have a look.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong>Why A Massage Therapist?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (41)\" alt=\"Why A Massage Therapist\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Australians appreciate health care, therefore means that employment demand in this sector&nbsp;is high in Australia. According to Job Outlook Australia&rsquo;s database, the number of persons employed as Massage Therapists (as a primary occupation) increased significantly throughout the four periods from 2018 to 2022. By 2025, the need for Massage Therapists is estimated to reach 18,000 persons. Additionally, each state has a higher-than-average employment rate for Massage Therapists.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The massage sector is not only expanding but also provides several work prospects in Australia. Massage Therapists are most frequently employed in the following areas:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clinics for&nbsp;massage.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facilities for the elders.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Health Services.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Spa services.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facilities or hospitals dedicated to palliative care.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong>Massage Therapists in Australia ANZSCO Code</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Australia has two \'Demand Lists for Occupations\'. Each profession on the MLTSSL and STSOL is issued an immigration number, and the code for Massage Therapists wishing to immigrate to Australia is 411611. This is often referred to as the ANZSCO Massage Therapist Code. If you\'re considering emigrating to Australia as a Massage Therapist, you\'ll find that your abilities are in high demand. The STSOL list is a Superior List for Australian Immigration, which implies that your visa is not employer-restricted. In Australia, you may take control of your own fate. You do not need to have a job in Australia to apply. The Massage Therapist Skilled Visa is all about you, your abilities, and how you will contribute to the Australian economy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong>Qualifications Needed to Work as a Massage Therapist in Australia</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (42)\" alt=\"Qualifications Needed to Work as a Massage Therapist in Australia\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order to practice massage therapy in Australia, one must have a level of education that is comparable to Skills Level 2 on the Australian Qualification Framework, according to ANZSCO. Skill Level 2 occupations have a skill level comparable to one of the following: AQF Associate Degree, Advanced Diploma or Registered Diploma. A minimum of three years of relevant experience can be used in place of the official credentials outlined above. Formal education may not be sufficient in many cases; necessary work experience and/or on-the-the-job training may be required. This is the most important part to get your work experience before you apply in Australia as a good massage therapist. Let&rsquo;s have a look at some criteria that should be vital in this case.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Am I Eligible?</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once you\'ve met the professional requirements for ANZSCO, it\'s time to calculate your overall points to immigrate yourself as a massage therapist.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Age Points to immigrate to Australia as a Massage Therapist</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">18 &ndash; 24 years = 25 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">25 &ndash; 32 years = 30 points.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">33 &ndash; 39 years = 25 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">40 &ndash; 44 years = 15 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Age 45 = No longer qualified but may still qualify for permanent residency under the TSS Visa.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">English Language Ability Points for Massage Therapists in Australia</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Excellent = 20 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Medium = 10 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Basic = 0 points</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work Experience Points for coming in&nbsp; Australia as a Massage Therapist</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 to 5 years = 5 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5 to 8 years = 10 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">8 years + = 15 points</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qualification Points to Emigrate to Australia as a Massage Therapist</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PHD = 20 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Degree = 15 points</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trade Qualification = 10 points</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We will always submit for Permanent Residency through the State Sponsored visa class, you may add an additional 5 or 10 points, or an additional 15 points for a regional application.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Come to Australia With Your Skills Assessment</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (43)\" alt=\"Massage Therapist in Australia\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Assessment of your capabilities certifies and acknowledges all of your abilities, credentials, and experience in your home country, allowing you to begin working in Australia and get any necessary local licenses and registrations. If you want to come to Australia as a massage therapist, you should get a complete certification on precisely the massage therapist course. &nbsp; This course will teach you how to do remedial massage, which involves the use of massage, stretching, and other methods to enhance wellness, wellbeing, and relaxation. You\'ll acquire the theoretical expertise you\'ll need to evaluate your client&rsquo;s soft tissue dysfunction and handle others that have a particular need.&nbsp;This is the way that will help to get you PR.</span></p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Expression of Interest EOI</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After getting a good Skills Assessment, you may submit an Expression of Interest, which adds you to a pool of applicants interested in migrating to Australia as a Massage Therapist. Therefore, it is important that you provide the best possible case in order to earn an invitation to apply for your official skilled visa.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>The Formal Application</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After getting an invitation to apply, the final phase of your PR&nbsp;to Australia as a Massage Therapist is to submit a formal application to the Department of Home Affairs. Security checks and medical examinations are essential at this point.</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong>Conclusions<br /><br /></strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage therapy has become more popular in Australia in recent years, owing to the advantages of lower academic entry requirements, a high employment rate, and the possibility of relocating to the country. You should be able to gather all of the information you want from this article in order to obtain PR in Australia.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Do you want to know about how to get permanent residency in Australia as a Massage Therapist? Click now to know more about this!', 'how-to-get-permanent-residency-in-australia-as-a-massage-therapist.jpg', NULL, '2022-03-31 19:22:42', '2022-04-19 04:05:42'),
(59, 8, '10 Quick Suggestions for Massage Therapy Tips: Client\'s Do\'s & Don\'ts', 'massage-therapy-tips', NULL, 'Are you going to take your first massage therapy? Have a look at this blog, we gathered top massage therapy tips for you.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage therapy is beneficial for both health and well-being. It is like a piece of art. If done improperly, it could cause damage. On the other hand, a massage done by an expert with the proper knowledge can be a rejuvenating experience and makes one feel younger. Getting the most out of a massage therapy session is something that many massage therapists advise their customers to do. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let\'s take a look at all of the many suggestions that clients could have.&nbsp; After reading this blog, customers should be able to understand the do\'s and don\'ts during the massage therapy.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>5 Do\'s Activity - During Your Massage Therapy</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (44)\" alt=\"Activity During Your Massage Therapy\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are some activities you should follow before and after your therapy. Let\'s have a look at 5 do\'s activities for your massage therapy tips.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Do Therapist\'s Homework<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage therapists may provide their client\'s homework assignments that include stretching, strengthening, movement-based exercises, and muscular help. The goal of giving client\'s homework is to show them how to take care of themselves so that their massages are more effective and result in longer-lasting health benefits. So, you should follow your homework strictly.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Do Increase Intake of Fluids<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make sure to drink enough water to maintain your body\'s circulation. Drinks with a lot of sugar or caffeine will dehydrate you and impair your health in the long term. After a massage, don\'t consume any alcohol!<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Do Check in Daily on Changes and Shifts<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Those who are more conscious of their bodies will be able to appreciate the benefits of massage. Make a note of any bodily changes you notice or feel so that you may share them with your therapist at your next appointment. Massage therapists must be aware of how their clients\' bodies respond to their efforts since each individual experiences touch in a unique way.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Be Open About Your Body Condition<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To get the most out of your massage, it\'s essential to tell the therapist why you\'re there and what you hope to achieve. What you know about your medical history is critical. Every one of these things is important: surgeries; ongoing problems; illnesses or pains; pregnancies; accidents; shattered bones. Allergy information is also important, especially if there are any oils or lotions you can\'t use.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Do Research<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do some research about your needs.&nbsp;&nbsp;Because there are so many different kinds of massage and bodywork, you should have some concept of what you\'re searching for before you begin your search. Make an effort to learn more about the many massage therapists in your region. You may find out what kind of massage treatment is given by visiting websites, sending them an email, or giving them a call.&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>5 Don\'ts Activity - During Your Massage Therapy</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (45)\" alt=\"Don\'ts do this During Your Massage Therapy\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are the activities you should avoid during your massage therapy. Let\'s have a look at 5 don\'t activities for your massage therapy tips.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Don\'t Take Shower Immediately<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many of our clients tell us they immediately get into the shower once their massage is over, mostly to remove the oil. In my opinion, this is a major oversight. To put it another way, the essential oils are just heated up during the massage, and it takes another hour for them to be absorbed into the cells of the skin. Instead of getting in the shower right away, wait an hour.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Don\'t Shower with Hot Water<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After a lengthy and relaxing massage, it\'s tempting to rest in a hot bath. You shouldn\'t even try with this. Using hot water on a sore muscle simply serves to add to the problem. Pain might be relieved by bathing your feet in ice water. Instead, take a warm bath or shower.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Don\'t Strenuous Activity Outside<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A one-hour massage is a perfect way to relax both your body and mind. Instead of waking them up, it\'s preferable to let them remain in that condition of rest. Muscles can be harmed by engaging in any physical activity, such as working out at the gym, swimming, or participating in hard sports. You can do some light sports though.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Don\'t Eat a Heavy Meal After a Massage<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Honestly, getting a massage makes you crave food. This is due to the increased blood circulation, which kick starts your whole body\'s functions, including your digestive system, into high gear. On the other hand, a large meal will only leave you feeling lazy, overstuffed, and lethargic instead of energized.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Don\'t Forget to Drink Water<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you don\'t drink&nbsp;water after a massage treatment session, this is what happens: Massage dehydrates you, which slows down your lymphatic and blood circulation. When the lymphatic system, in particular, isn\'t doing its job, you end up with toxic buildup, which defeats the goal of a purifying massage. So, always be hydrated by drinking water.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusions<br /><br /></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The therapist and the client must be able to communicate openly. This is very important to know the best things before taking your massage.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This blog will assist you in determining the best suggestions for clients before they undergo massage treatment.</span></p>', 'massage therapy tips', 'massage therapy tips', 'Are you going to take your first massage therapy? Have a look at this blog, we gathered top massage therapy tips for you.', 'massage-therapy-tips.jpg', NULL, '2022-04-18 12:36:47', '2022-04-20 16:48:18'),
(60, 8, '8 Best Things Every Hairdresser Should Do Every day', 'best-things-every-hairdresser-should-do-every-day', NULL, 'Do you want to know what you should do every day for a hairdresser, then this article is for you?', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Having a career as a hairdresser gives you the ability to affect people\'s lives in many ways. Your social life and personality are shaped in part by your work as a hairdresser. They may be more enthusiastic about their career and social life if they have a fresh appearance and feel. As a good hairdresser, every day, you should maintain a perfect routine to improve and be consistent in your work. This blog includes the 8 best things every hairdresser should do every day.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>8 Things Every Hairdresser Should Do Every Day<br /><br /><br /></strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Look at these suggestions to move forward yourself as a good hairdresser. If you can maintain these things, then it will smooth your career as a hairdresser.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Maintain Good Customer Relations</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design\" alt=\"Maintain Good Customer Relations\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A friendly attitude is required at all times by a hairstylist. As a hairstylist, you are expected to welcome and converse with your customers. It\'s important to find out what your customer genuinely wants in a hairstyle throughout your talk. If you want to show that you care about your client\'s lifestyle, you might inquire how long they want to spend on their hair styling and grooming each day. Customers will return if they get the impression that you are actually interested in what they have to say.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Be Professional, Well-Dressed, And Smart<br /><br /></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Making a good impression relies heavily on your own appearance. Having a professional appearance not only helps you create a good first impression on coworkers and clients but it also improves your performance. We perform better when we appear and sound like our characters. Your salon will have a dress code; however, there is generally flexibility for your own personal style within that code. Of course, your hair is an important part of your appearance, and it must be flawless.&nbsp;You are a walking billboard for yourself, your salon, and the industry.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Clean And Sanitize Saloon Daily</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (2)\" alt=\"Clean And Sanitize Saloon Daily\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hairdressing courses may teach you how to properly sanitize your tools and work area. If you don\'t already, do it, you\'ll soon get into the habit of doing so. Maintaining a clean work environment is essential for both safeties and for making a good impression on your customers.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Check Your Appointment Book<br /><br /></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hairstylists need to manage a full schedule of appointments. Every morning, you must check your appointment book to see which clients are coming in. If you\'ve noticed that particular hairstyling clients haven\'t seen you in a while, you could wish to phone them and extend an invitation to return. You can maintain your appointment schedule by staying in touch with your clients.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Focus On Your Salon\'s Brand</strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Untitled design (1)\" alt=\"Focus On Your Salon\'s Brand\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If your salon has a brand, it\'s important to its long-term success. It is your job as a salon employee to know, promote, and maintain the salon\'s brand, and you play a major role in doing so. In order to succeed in the hairdressing industry, you need to establish a distinct identity for yourself.&nbsp; You should be able to tell how your customers feel about your brand based on how often they return. Your whole online presence should reinforce the message you\'re trying to communicate. Every day, keep your focus and your brand front and center and inspire your team to live up to it.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Get Feedback<br /><br /></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The opinion of your customers is most important. Confidence is a fundamental building element of self-esteem, and it is necessary for the well-being of humans. In the workplace, feedback from your clients, coworkers, and bosses not only tells you how you\'re doing, but it also provides your job with a sense of purpose. Do not hesitate to ask your customers what they think about your service and whether they would be willing to fill out a feedback form.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Keep Accurate Records</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We know tips&nbsp;are part of a hairstylist\'s compensation package. Your records should show how much money you\'ve made each day, not just from hairdressing appointments but also from the sale of items at your hair salon. In order to keep track of your entire revenue, save all receipts and update your record daily for tax purposes.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Learn Everyday</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The greatest way to become a superb hairdresser is to continue learning. The world\'s wealthiest people understand this: you should never stop learning. Learning is vital for development and success. Therefore, each day, you may learn something new about hairdressing and salon management that will help you be more productive. You can also do some courses to boost yourself. </span><a href=\"../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Certificate III in Hairdressing </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">course can help you to know more.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Final Words<br /><br /><br /></strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is no shortage of opportunities for creative expression in the world of hairstylists, who spend their days moving from client to client creating works of art. Although hairdressing will be a major part of your daily duties, you will also be expected to do a variety of other jobs that are just as important to your success as styling hair. From this article, you can know the appropriate knowledge about your everyday routine as a good hairdresser. Here we gathered the 8 best approaches you must do every day if you consider yourself a good hairdresser.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Best Things Every Hairdresser Should Do Every day', 'Best Things Every Hairdresser Should Do Every day', 'Do you want to know what you should do every day for a hairdresser, then this article is for you?', 'best-things-every-hairdresser-should-do-every-day.jpg', NULL, '2022-04-25 18:33:42', '2022-05-11 19:09:06');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(61, 8, 'What Should Be on Your Resume for A Massage Therapist Job?', 'what-should-be-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job', NULL, 'Do you want to make your resume for a massage therapist job? This blog is for you.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you\'re currently enrolled in or just finished a massage therapy program and&nbsp;looking for a job&nbsp;as a massage therapist, the time has come to design your resume. As with any other job, you\'ll need a resume to apply for massage therapy positions. This section will include your previous education and associated massage courses, as well as any relevant skill sets and job experience. A well-written Resume will expand your work chances and assist you in landing your desired massage therapy position. If you\'re ready to apply for a massage therapist position, use these recommendations to help you enhance your resume. In this blog, we expressed the necessary information for you that will build your resume for a massage therapist job more strongly.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Choose The Best Format<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The greatest resume headers will elevate your resume to the next level. Make sure&nbsp;that your contact information is up to date. The titles of your resume sections should assist the recruiter in navigating the resume. Verify that it is easy to read. Select the appropriate font size for your resume. Avoid too decorative fonts. Avoid cramming your resume with unnecessary content. Consider white space to be a friend. Submit your&nbsp;resume in PDF format. Only use the doc file type if your company requires it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Write a Resume Objective or Summary<br /><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/therapist-resume.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br />Start your massage therapist resume with a professional profile. This quick paragraph acts as an introduction to the recruiter and allows you to briefly introduce yourself to them. There are two ways to structure a resume profile: a resume summary and an objective statement. How do these two compare? Licensed massage therapists with more than two years of experience might benefit from a resume summary. It emphasizes a person\'s previous work and achievements. An entry-level massage therapist\'s resume should include a resume objective. Rather than focusing on your academic achievements, it&nbsp;focuses on your abilities. Finally, make an effort to include a few more numbers. In this manner, your resume\'s effect will be maximized.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Add Duties and Responsibilities<br /><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/massage-therapist-duties.png\" alt=\"duties and responsibilities\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br />It\'s important to grasp your new job\'s duties and responsibilities in order to personalize your resume appropriately. As a massage therapist, you must demonstrate your ability to select the appropriate massage technique for each client and to communicate effectively with them about the therapy they require and why. Consider the following frequent massage therapy roles and responsibilities while writing your resume:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Collaboration with clients and development of specific targeting plans.</li>\r\n<li>Keeping track of treatment records.</li>\r\n<li>Recognize health problems that necessitate a referral to a different healthcare provider.</li>\r\n<li>Using caution when dealing with injured patients.</li>\r\n<li>Confidentiality and sensitivity when it comes to a client\'s medical history.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding which muscle groups to target.</li>\r\n<li>Keeping the massage room clean and adhering to good hygiene.<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Identify The Best Skills for Your Resume<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Start by compiling a comprehensive list of your skills for use on your Resume. It should incorporate both soft and hard talents, as well as technological strengths. Return to the job advertisement and make a list of all the talents specified. Examine your own talents list to determine what abilities you possess. These are the ones on which you should concentrate your resume. Select up to ten of your greatest talents and organize them into a section titled \"essential skills.\" Distribute your skills evenly across your resume. Finally, ensure that these are also mentioned in your resume profile and job description. Here you can find the top 5 skills that are suitable for your job. You can also include many skills rather than these mentioned five.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Adaptability</li>\r\n<li>Customer service</li>\r\n<li>Bodywork</li>\r\n<li>Deep tissue massage</li>\r\n<li>Aromatherapy massage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Besides, if you want to get a professional skill certificate, then have a look at the <a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u>HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</u></a> course. It will boost your skills more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Add Education and Work Experience<br /><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/education-and-work-experience.png\" alt=\"education and work experience \" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br />This section should emphasize your massage therapist\'s education and training. Indicate the name of the training center, and the training/degree title attained, and the dates of attendance for each. Other education, such as a university degree, can&nbsp;be included&nbsp;if it is related to massage therapy work. If you feel that you need more certification, then you can take a course from <a href=\"../../\"><u>Noble Training Academy</u></a>. NTA offers <u>HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</u> course for you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Your professional experience should be listed chronologically, beginning with your most recent employment. Include past employers\' names and locations, employment dates, and job titles held. Describe your tasks in action words and include some&nbsp;accomplishments and awards. If you have five or more years of experience, just provide your degree, the name of the institution, the location, and the year of graduation. On the other hand, if you&nbsp;lack experience, you may choose to include information about your extracurricular activities, academic achievements and awards, and relevant coursework.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusions<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The resume of a massage therapist is usually short and covers&nbsp;essential skills and training in massage treatment. You should&nbsp;include any relevant training or education on your resume and any transferrable abilities you have that will be useful in your new position. This blog summarizes all the necessary information that will help to build your resume for a massage therapist job.</p>', 'Resume for A Massage Therapist Job', 'Resume for A Massage Therapist Job', 'Do you want to make your resume for a massage therapist job? This blog is for you.', 'what-should-be-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job.jpeg', NULL, '2022-05-07 17:46:28', '2022-05-11 19:06:32'),
(62, 8, 'A Complete Guide About Salon Sanitation and Hygiene', 'complete-guide-about-salon-sanitation-and-hygiene', 6, 'Want to Know about salon sanitation and hygiene? Let\'s get inside to know the details.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every hairdresser and beauty professional is aware of the necessity of cleanliness in the workplace. It is an important factor in every operation and service performed in your salon, and achieving the highest level of cleanliness will enhance your client\'s experience and help reduce the spread of germs, bacteria, and infection. It will also increase your company\'s reputation and ensure that clients continue utilizing and suggesting your services. Now is the moment to deliberate how to keep your customers feeling secure, at peace, and informed about your efforts to improve sanitation and hygiene. This article explores a complete guide about salon sanitation and hygiene.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sanitize Your Towel Regularly<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong><img src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/sanitize-your-towel-regularly.png\" alt=\"Sanitize Your Towel Regularly\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Towls should be used just once per customer. Be careful to follow this rule. To reduce the spread of germs between clients, this is the best option. Do not re-use salon towels that haven\'t been washed. To get <a href=\"https://www.webmd.com/parenting/ss/slideshow-clean-up-germs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">rid of bacteria</a>, use hot water and a strong detergent in your salon\'s washing. At 100&deg;C, bacteria are destroyed, while detergent-based cleaning is most effective at 60&deg;C. When the towels are totally dry, take them from the dryer. Avoid leaving towels on the floor at all costs.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hygiene Your Workplace</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/hygiene-your-workplace.png\" alt=\"Hygiene Your Workplace\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Germs may be transferred to your workplace, which is a no-brainer. Disinfectant wipes should be used routinely to clean surfaces, doorknobs, and tables, and protocols should be put in place to assure this. Make sure they\'re thrown away in a trash can. Cleaning salon floors on a regular basis are important since they gather hair, nails, and other debris. Floors should be cleaned on a regular basis to prevent accidents due to slippery surfaces. Please remember to clean up after yourself and dispose of any food that may have gotten on your dishes and silverware if you eat in the salon rest area.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clean Couches and Chairs</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong><img src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/clean-couches-and-chairs.png\" alt=\"Clean Couches and Chairs\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A cut or scrape that isn\'t covered by plaster or bandage should be taken care of to avoid cross-infection, but most salon furniture is made of vinyl or PVC, which is easy to clean. Besides, a Couch roll can be used to keep salon chairs and sofas from becoming infected with germs. Because ethanol-based disinfectants can weaken the wood and cause cracking and crumbling, they should be avoided at all costs. This allows bacteria to settle in and reproduce.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keep Hygiene Tools and Instruments</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Always sterilize devices between clients to avoid cross-client infection. An autoclave should be used to sterilize cuticle nippers, scissors, and tweezers before use. Warm water and detergent should be used to properly clean bowls, plates, and other salon supplies. When using a disinfectant, always follow the manufacturer\'s directions. Before drying, make sure to thoroughly rinse your equipment in freshwater to eliminate any residue. Store salon and spa tools in clean, dry containers or UV cabinets once they\'ve been disinfected. Bacteria can build up on surfaces if they aren\'t cleaned on a regular basis.</span></p>\r\n<h2>Keep These Products in Your Saloon<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/a-complete-guide-about-salon-sanitation-and-hygiene.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /><br />This is the time to focus on what items you may utilize in your salon in order to maintain the highest standards of sanitation.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Disposable gloves:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> <br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether doing waxing, manicures, or pedicures, it is advisable to use disposable gloves. Because they are disposable, gloves will protect your skin from harsh cleaning solutions and other toxic substances and prevent cross-contamination. After usage, they should be peeled off and thrown away.<br /><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Barbicide disinfectant:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> <br /><br />Barbicide disinfects grooming devices and salon items that are not appropriate for autoclaving, including as brushes, combs, and plastic instruments. Mix water and Barbicide in a measuring cup before pouring into a jar. Always follow the product\'s directions to ensure that you use it safely and dispose of it properly while wearing vinyl gloves. It&nbsp;offers a full selection of sprays, wipes, and equipment to make it simple to deliver the highest level of cleanliness.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Autoclaves and sterilizers:<br /><br /></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Autoclaves and sterilizers are required in salons because they are the only assured technique of destroying bacteria on metal equipment and instruments. Before placing your equipment in an autoclave, you must ensure that all debris has been removed by washing them properly. You will then be able to utilize the autoclave, which normally takes 20 minutes to finish. An automated medical autoclave can sanitize in only 11 minutes for increased efficiency.<br /><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Anti-bacterial hand gel:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Anti-bacterial hand gels are&nbsp;like Vines and Mundo, which are vital for both the client and the therapist, and will guarantee that your hands are clean both before and after treatment.<br /><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Disinfectant wipes:</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> <br /><br />Wipes are an efficient and rapid method for cleaning surfaces and equipment. The Mundo multi-surface cleaning wipes are a practical and inexpensive option for disinfecting several surfaces, including PVC and vinyl. These aldehyde- and phenol-free wipes are a must for any hectic professional atmosphere and make your hygiene routine more convenient.<br /><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conclusion<br /><br /></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maintaining a high level of cleanliness in your salon is important for protecting yourself, your clients, and the general public. A clean, sanitary, and safe location can inspire confidence, encourage continuous business, and prevent difficulties such as cross-contamination, germs, and viruses. This blog explores the way of protecting your salon from germs and bacteria. Follow these suggestions about salon sanitation and hygiene to make a perfect salon.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'A Complete Guide About Salon Sanitation and Hygiene', 'Guide About Salon Sanitation and Hygiene', 'Want to Know about salon sanitation and hygiene? Let\'s get inside to know the details.', 'complete-guide-about-salon-sanitation-and-hygiene.jpeg', 'complete-guide-about-salon-sanitation-and-hygiene', '2022-05-11 14:40:40', '2022-05-17 22:04:08'),
(63, 7, 'How Massage Can Help Improve Your Post-Workout Recovery Routine', 'how-massage-can-help-improve-your-post-workout-recovery-routine', 6, 'Getting a massage after working out can help you recover faster and lower your chance of injury.  From this article, you\'ll learn about how massage can help improve your post-workout recovery routine.', '<p>Getting a massage after working out can help you recover faster and lower your chance of injury. Have you ever had sore muscles a few days or even weeks following a workout? There is always the possibility of overuse injuries or Delayed Onset Muscle Soreness (DOMS), even among seasoned athletes. If you want to get the most out of your workout, whether you\'re a professional athlete or just a gym-goer, you should include sports massage in your post-workout regimen. From this article, you\'ll learn about how massage can help improve your post-workout recovery routine.</p>\r\n<h2>The Most Common Post-Workout Symptoms and Injuries</h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/post-workout\" alt=\"Post-Workout\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anyone, even the most accomplished athletes, can suffer from a <a href=\"https://www.webmd.com/fitness-exercise/guide/workout-injuries-prevention-and-treatment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">workout-related injury</a>. A sports injury may happen to anybody, regardless of age or fitness level.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Following an exercise, the most common injuries include:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tightness and stress in the muscles</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pain in the knee</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pain in the lower back</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shin splints.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wrist dislocation sprain</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pain and discomfort in the elbow</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tendinitis</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pain or stiffness in the hips and shoulders</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Plantar Fasciitis (also known as a foot sprain)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All of these post-exercise symptoms indicate that you have sustained an injury due to overuse, bad technique, or failure to properly warm- up and cool down before and after exercising.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recovery-Enhancing Types of Massage<br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"../../public/blogImages/enhancing-types-of-massage\" alt=\"Enhancing Types of Massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Immediately following a workout or an accident, massage can help alleviate discomfort and inflammation. Combining sports massage with remedial, deep-tissue, and relaxation massage is the most excellent way to speed recovery after a workout. Post-workout, various forms of massage can assist reduce physical stress and soreness while also promoting mental well-being.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Remedial<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The goal of <a href=\"../blogs/how-can-the-remedial-massage-therapy-effects-physically-and-psychologically\">remedial massage</a> is injury prevention and the improvement or rehabilitation of muscular mobility and movement patterns. The success of deep tissue massage, trigger point treatment, myofascial release, and stretching in remedial massage will considerably reduce muscular discomfort and speed up the recovery process.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deep Tissue<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To eliminate lactic acid and alleviate muscular knots and tenseness, deep tissue massage addresses the muscle\'s fascia. The massage therapist will use slow, continuous strokes to deliver deep pressure to those inner muscles and flexible tendons that surround the joints. Adhesions will be removed, the discomfort will be alleviated, tension will be reduced, and muscle healing time will be accelerated.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sports Massage<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sports massage treatment cures and prevents a variety of common sports-related ailments. In order to fix muscular strains, it incorporates a variety of massage and manipulation methods. A sports massage\'s style will be determined by the nature of your condition and specific requirements. Soft tissue massage, deep tissue massage, and whole-body massage are all popular forms of sports massage.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Relaxation<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order to relieve stress and tension, the gentle, rhythmic motions of a relaxation massage are employed. Sportspeople can really benefit from a therapeutic massage like this one. Reducing the tension and anxiety that comes along with training and competing can aid in recuperation. Relaxation massages can also assist in soothing the body and mind and alleviate any anxieties or concerns you may have about your injury or the time you will be out of the game.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Advantages For All<br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"../../public/blogImages/advantages-of massage\" alt=\"Advantages of massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are various advantages to utilizing the aforementioned post-workout recovery massage techniques. From pain management to enhanced flexibility and performance, these are some of the ways massage may help you recover from a hard workout or injury:<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase Blood Flow and Nutrient Delivery to Injured Tissue<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The post-workout recovery <a href=\"https://www.livescience.com/34910-massage-benefits-immune-system-100908.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">massage boosts</a> oxygen and nutrient supply to the muscles by improving blood circulation. Muscle and tendon lengthening and healing are both aided by a healthy blood flow. A massage immediately following a strenuous workout will help dislodge any clots or blockages that may have formed.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduce Muscular Spasms and Pains<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reducing muscular discomfort and weakness, as well as inflammation, can be accomplished by receiving a massage immediately following exercise. Massaged muscles have a 20% to 40% probability of returning to their pre-injury state. Post-event and post-workout DOMS can be alleviated by massage. After a workout, a massage can help alleviate DOMS by easing muscular tension and reviving blood flow to the muscles.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Expanded Range of Adaptability<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sporting performance may be enhanced by using post-workout recovery massage to increase mobility and flexibility. Massage facilitates the lengthening and elasticization of soft tissues, allowing for a greater range of motion, flexibility, and performance. Keep your muscles and joints moving at their fullest effort without risking injury or strain by keeping your body flexible.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduces Recovery Time &amp; Risk of Injury<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage can speed up muscle regeneration after exercise, allowing for a quicker return to normal activity. Keeping the muscles pliable and fluid with a massage after an exercise can help lessen the likelihood of injury in the future. The tightness and shortening of muscles following an exercise or an injury might increase the likelihood of inflammation or pain. Releasing tension and increasing blood flow will help release the muscles. Stretching and movement will be more fluid and less likely to cause damage as a result of the muscles being lengthened and returned to their natural design.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Relaxation<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"../../public/blogImages/Relaxation\" alt=\"Relaxation\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massages of all kinds relieve tension in the muscles and ease tension in the head. Muscles relax from a tense, tense condition into a peaceful, relaxed state when they are massaged. Physiologically, this causes the body to reach a state of heavy relaxation and improved well-being. Relaxing massages can help you recuperate after an exercise by relieving muscular tension, lowering stress levels, and minimizing chronic pain. Massage induces the release of feel-good hormones in the body, which promotes relaxation and aids in recovery.<br /></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Last Words<br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are new in the gym or a seasoned athlete seeking a faster and more efficient recovery regimen, a regular sports massage may be extremely beneficial to your general health and wellness. From this blog, you must learn the necessary information regarding the improvement of massage after your post-workout recovery routine. If you are interested in learning more about massage treatment, you can enroll in <a href=\"../diploma-in-remedial-massage\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</a>. This course will also provide you a professional certification.<br /></span></p>', 'How Massage Can Help Improve Your Post-Workout Recovery Routine', 'How Massage Can Help Improve Your Post-Workout Recovery Routine', 'Getting a massage after working out can help you recover faster and lower your chance of injury.  From this article, you\'ll learn about how massage can help improve your post-workout recovery routine.', 'how-massage-can-help-improve-your-post-workout-recovery-routine.jpeg', NULL, '2022-05-16 22:13:58', '2022-06-27 22:52:29'),
(64, 8, '5 Marketing Ideas for Massage Therapists in Australia', 'marketing-ideas-for-massage-therapists-in-australia', 6, 'If you want to know about marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia, you can try the 5 marketing ideas discussed in this article.', '<p>You will find fewer things more relaxing than receiving a good massage in this world. As people appear to be more stressed-out than ever, services like massage therapy are required more than ever. As a result, the amount of massage therapists in Australia has significantly increased over the past 2 decades.</p>\r\n<p><br />It signifies that there is more competition now than before, and you have to boost your marketing game to remain ahead of the competition. But, it is a very challenging task. The odds are that if you do not get a regular flow of clients coming to you, you will not feel very relaxed yourself.</p>\r\n<p><br />Also, for someone who is an expert in delivering feel-good experiences and releasing stress to their customers, getting stressed isn\'t a healthy option. Regrettably, no one has so far created an analytics program to show precise numerical data quantifying the cost savings and health benefits that can be accomplished via a program of standard massage therapy.</p>\r\n<p><br />Don\'t worry; we have got your back. There could be a lot of marketing ideas out there, but when it comes to bringing more clients for <a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\">massage therapists</a>, you have to apply the 5 <strong>marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia</strong> discussed here.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Find Your Niche</strong></h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/find-your-niche\" alt=\"Find Your Niche\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>Enticing the correct audience to your massage therapy practice is very crucial, and finding your niche aids you in marketing to the correct audience. Do not be frightened to specialize, and then get benefits from that specialty by networking with the health care specialists to obtain customers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Determine and establish your target market as per your interest, area of expertise, etc., and your potential customer\'s lifestyle demands, interests, habits, demographics, or lots of other factors. It can aid in narrowing down your marketing approach to a particular group of people and building a primary customer base.</p>\r\n<p><br />If you could get all the tasks you might handle working with pregnant women, sports injuries, elderly patients, fibromyalgia patients, or any other specialty customers, then you don\'t have to do competition with fancy day spas providing relaxation massages.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Publish Your Own Blog</strong></h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/publish-your-own-blog\" alt=\"Publish Your Own Blog\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>You do not have to be the best writer to publish your own blog. In your blog, you can provide your customers more value by sharing informative and relevant info regarding massage therapy, your own philosophies, and regular tips to acquire well-being and better health. It will help you to keep those customers on your books for the long haul.</p>\r\n<p><br />You can publish articles about the newest discoveries in homeopathic medicine, the benefits of massage therapy on health, beneficial stretching exercises, and dietary suggestions. You can also post articles regarding massage therapy courses like the <a href=\"../diploma-in-remedial-massage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</a>. If you have recognition of prior learning in this course, then you can write elaborately about this course.</p>\r\n<p><br />Also, having <a href=\"../../blogs/how-rpl-influence-job-demand-in-beauty-therapy-industries-in-australia\">RPL in the massage therapy industry,</a> you might know the importance of this kind of course. You can share that importance and also let people know about the importance of having RPL in massage therapy before entering this industry.</p>\r\n<p><br />In addition, let people know that if people come from other countries to Australia as massage therapists, they need to have RPL on these kinds of <a href=\"https://www.nta.nsw.edu.au/\">courses</a> before they can start their practice. Publishing a daily blog will aid in boosting your site\'s local search results, and people will know you as an expert in the field.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Provide Package Deals</strong></h2>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/blogImages/package-deals\" alt=\"Package Deals\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>It is the most important thing you need to do. When customers can gain a discount by paying for lots of services upfront, everyone wins. They get an excellent deal, and you receive the funds in the bank account. You can consider joining forces with a salon or spa in the same locality to provide mutual discounts or relaxing spa packages.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Create Your Individual Brand</strong></h2>\r\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/individual-brand\" alt=\"Individual Brand\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>If you want to win the race against other massage therapists, reveal your personality, and you will strengthen relationships with your customers. Keep in mind that the aim should be to connect with your customers, not to collect. Try a professional and friendly tone to separate your massage therapy business from other businesses. It will also make people think you really care about your customers.</p>\r\n<p><br />Although it is crucial to establish yourself on normal social network sites such as Facebook and Twitter, you also have to go into more photo-centric sites such as Instagram. As people say, a picture\'s value is a thousand words. Photos can make an impression stronger and more long-lasting than just sending emails.</p>\r\n<p><br />So, post your services on a <a href=\"https://www.business2community.com/digital-marketing/8-digital-marketing-platforms-entrepreneurs-love-02039144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">digital platform</a> and share them across various social media channels such as Instagram, Facebook, Linkedin, and Twitter. Connect contemporary humor, attractive pictures, and real-time events to stay timely and relevant. Also, you can post instructional videos on your social media channels. They will benefit you as they have a visual element along with the content.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Join Industry Events</strong></h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/industry-events.png\" alt=\"Industry Events\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /><br />As a qualified massage therapist, you have to join industry events to expand your network. Businesses that keep up to date with the massage therapy industry trend and promote themselves do much better compared to those businesses that don\'t.</p>\r\n<p><br />Be in continuous communication with classmates, professors, and former trainers so that they can inform you of forthcoming industry events. Find out what is going on in this community and industry and attend it. Even if you can participate in just one industry event every 6 months, join it as it\'s better than nothing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\r\n<p><br />Massage therapy is everything regarding connecting with your clients and giving them a happier and healthier life. It\'s precisely how your massage therapy marketing needs to be. The more you recognize your clients and their requirements, the better the marketing of your massage therapy business will be.</p>\r\n<p><br />No matter what business you are in, enticing new clients always has to be at the top of your mind. Luckily for you, the massage therapy business lends itself to various creative marketing tactics. We are hopeful that after trying the <strong>marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia</strong> listed above, you can see more customers booking your appointments.</p>', 'marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia', 'marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia', 'If you want to know about marketing ideas for massage therapists in Australia, you can try the 5 marketing ideas discussed in this article.', 'marketing-ideas-for-massage-therapists-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2022-05-22 15:15:47', '2022-06-08 22:06:57'),
(65, 7, 'Can Massage Therapy Help with Curvatures of the Spine?', 'can-massage-therapy-help-with-curvatures-of-the-spine', 4, 'A human being faces so many physical problems in his life. Some of the problems can be cured and some of them are very hard to cure. Today we will talk about a human physical problem and one of its solutions. The problem is the curvatures of the spine.', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A human being faces so many physical problems in his life. Some of the problems can be cured and some of them are very hard to cure. Today we will talk about a human physical problem and one of its solutions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The problem is the curvatures of the spine. We will let you know that massage therapy can help with curvatures of the spine. Before telling you that in detail, let me give you some basic information on this topic.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The spine is the vertebral column of our body. There are four curves in our spine. They are known as curvatures. Four curvatures are Cervical Curvature, Thoracic Curvature, Lumbar Curvature, and Sacral Curvature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The curvatures are vital parts of our body. Because it dictates the proper posture of the human body. They help the spine to absorb the stress and pressure from body movement and gravity.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They increase the flexibility of the human body. So you can understand how vital the curvatures are. But there can be problems with the curvatures. The problem is known as Scoliosis. Now we will know more about that in detail. Let\'s jump into it.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Massage Therapy for Scoliosis</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/massage-therapy-for-scoliosis\" alt=\"Massage Therapy for Scoliosis\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When a person suffers from <a href=\"https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/scoliosis/symptoms-causes/syc-20350716\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">scoliosis</a>, he faces some difficulties with the curvatures of his spine. The spine starts to curve one side. So it becomes difficult for him to move flexibly. Getting rid of this massage can help. Massage is a good treatment for the human body. Generally, massage offers so many benefits for the human body. The benefits of massage are-</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increase Blood Flow</span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/increase-blood-flow\" alt=\"Increase Blood Flow\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we all know massage is a good thing for our body. Massage increases the blood flow. In our body blood flows to the muscles and tissues. When anybody massages your body, the blood can flow easily to the muscles and tissues. So it is a vital thing for our body.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stretches Tight Areas<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/stretches-tight-areas\" alt=\"Stretches Tight Areas\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sometimes our muscles or other</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;body parts become tight. It makes us uncomfortable. So massage can stretch the tight areas of the human body.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Relieves Pain<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/relieves-pain\" alt=\"Relieves Pain\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sometimes we feel pain in our several body parts. It happens because of workload. Getting rid of this massage can help you. When you take a massage, you will feel relaxed. This is so good for your body.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better Sleep<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/better-sleep\" alt=\"better-sleep.png\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sleeping is so necessary for the human body. If you don\'t sleep properly, then you can not work. Sometimes we can not sleep properly. Massages help the human body to be relaxed. Then you can sleep well. So for better sleep, massage is a good thing.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are some benefits of massage. If you want to get rid of Scoliosis, then massage therapy can help you. There is no permanent cure for scoliosis, unfortunately.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But there are some manual treatments for scoliosis, like physical manipulation, massage therapy, etc. Massage therapy can make your body relaxed and flexible. There are several types of massage therapy. The therapist provides you with these massages according to your needs. Now let\'s know more details about these massages.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Swedish Massage<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Swedish massage is a common massage. There are some special things to do with your body like tapping, kneading, long strokes, shaking, etc. This is very helpful for the human body.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deep Tissue Massage<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is another amazing massage for the human body. This is also known as neuromuscular therapy. Sometimes the blood doesn&rsquo;t flow properly to the tissues. This massage helps us to increase the blood flow to the muscles and tissues.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Myofascial Release<br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Myofascial release massage focuses on opening up the tight areas. If there are any tight areas in your body, it will help it to loosen up. This also supports the muscles.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Cranial-sacral Therapy</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This is a vital massage for the human body. It helps us to balance the spine. It also allows us to improve the overall function of our bodies. It mobilizes the restricted tissues around the spine.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Thai Yoga Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../public/blogImages/thai-yoga-massage\" alt=\"Thai Yoga Massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This massage is also known as Thai massage for scoliosis. This massage is based on traditional yoga and Ayurveda. This massage can be fully clothed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Does Massage Therapy Work?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We have discussed the basics of Massage therapy. Now we will know that massage therapy can help with curvatures of the spine. We already know that the problem of the spine is called Scoliosis. There is no clinical treatment for scoliosis. But a small number of clinical studies say that massage therapy can help with the curvatures of the spine.</p>\r\n<p>You can take help with several massages like deep tissue massage, soft tissue massage, myofascial massage, etc. These massages help you to get rid of scoliosis. There are some appropriate times to do massage therapy. There are several studies that tell us to do massage therapy twice or thrice a week.</p>\r\n<p>If you do two or three sessions per week for 6-12 weeks, then it will improve your curvatures so much. According to studies, scoliosis massage helps you in many ways. It releases the pain. It also increases the range of motion and it reduces the curve of the spine. If you take massage therapy, it will help with curvatures of the spine and it will improve the blood flow rate in your body.</p>\r\n<p>You should take advice from a doctor before you do <a href=\"../../blogs/massage-therapy-tips\">massage therapy</a>. Because you should do it in the right way, otherwise it can be harmful to your body if you can not do it properly. Massage therapy works to reduce the curve of the spine and reduce back pain. So if you are suffering from scoliosis, you should try this.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Final Words</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>After reading this article you know that can massage therapy help with curvatures of the spine. Some clinical studies have found that massage therapy can help with the curvatures of the spine. But it is not sure that it will work for everyone with scoliosis. But massage reduces body pain and increases mobility. It also helps us to relax our muscles. So regular massage can help a scoliosis patient to feel better overall. &nbsp;But more research is needed to know about the success rate of massage therapy. <a href=\"../../\">NTA</a> offers certified courses in the beauty industry that you can rely on you can check it.</p>', 'Can Massage Therapy Help with Curvatures of the Spine?', 'Can Massage Therapy Help with Curvatures of the Spine?', 'A human being faces so many physical problems in his life. Some of the problems can be cured and some of them are very hard to cure. Today we will talk about a human physical problem and one of its solutions. The problem is curvatures of the spine.', 'can-massage-therapy-help-with-curvatures-of-the-spine.jpeg', NULL, '2022-06-07 22:34:45', '2022-09-20 17:15:00');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(68, 7, 'Some Basic Skills Required For High Paying Beauty Industries Jobs In Australia', 'some-basic-skills-required-for-high-paying-beauty-industries-jobs-in-australia', 2, 'If you want to know some basic skills required for high-paying beauty industry jobs in Australia, then this article has all the things that you need to know.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The beauty industry is very famous and is growing quicker than ever. This fame is no wonder, given the huge number of influencers on social media endorsing different treatments and products. People want to feel nice about themselves, and beauticians aid them in achieving their aesthetic goals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are almost hundreds of different occupations you can get into in the beauty industry this year. These include department stores, hairdressing salons, day spas, beauty salons, and more. They all have dissimilar pay grades and need different training.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is expected that Australia\'s beauty industry will grow over the next few years, with an estimation of 3%-4% growth until 2025. Also, in the beauty industry, you can get full-time, part-time, contracted, or casual jobs. It means that this career path might work well around your children and family and fit in with other responsibilities.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Growth is occurring across all professions in the beauty and personal care sector. The biggest growth projected in the beauty industry is for beauty therapists, with a 20% increase in demand projected by 2024.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So, if the concept of making people feel gorgeous inside and out excites you, then remain with us and check out <strong>some basic skills required for high-paying beauty industry jobs in Australia</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Skills Required For High Paying Beauty Industries Jobs In Australia</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/beauty therapist\" alt=\"beauty therapist\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Different skills are needed for different jobs in the beauty industry of Australia. In the below guide, we will check out the skills required for high-paying beauty industry jobs in Australia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Makeup Artist</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/makeup-artist.png\" alt=\"makeup artist\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In Australia, no formal qualifications are required to become a makeup artist. Still, if you are looking for a makeup artist job, it is strongly suggested that you go through any kind of formal training and get a nationally recognized certificate. It is essential if you are looking to begin your own business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The average hourly salary of a makeup artist is $19-$77, and the average yearly salary of a makeup artist is $40k-$155k. The basic skills you require to be a good makeup artist are:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Good eye for color</li>\r\n<li>Imagination</li>\r\n<li>Creativity</li>\r\n<li>Skilled in makeup and design application of prosthetics and cosmetics</li>\r\n<li>Decent communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Good issue-solving skills</li>\r\n<li>Artistic</li>\r\n<li>Adaptable and flexible</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of several skin types, facial shapes, and which products suit what events</li>\r\n<li>Time management</li>\r\n<li>Good stamina to stand and work for a long time</li>\r\n<li>Reliable</li>\r\n<li>Has the capability of thinking on their feet</li>\r\n<li>Attention for detail</li>\r\n<li>Punctuality</li>\r\n<li>Able to work within the budget and a strict timeline</li>\r\n<li>Persistence</li>\r\n<li>Good hand-eye coordination</li>\r\n<li>A continuous learner to stay updated with existing techniques and trends</li>\r\n<li>Able to work in a team or independently</li>\r\n<li>Patience</li>\r\n<li>Has the capability of working well under pressure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beauty Therapist</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/beauty-therapist.png\" alt=\"beauty therapist\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Someone with a diploma in beauty therapy or a <a href=\"../../certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy\">certificate IV</a> in beauty therapy can become a beautician in Australia. The training and qualification a candidate will receive will aid them in deciding what kind of beauty treatments they can offer. To be a successful beauty therapist, you need to have empathy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is because you might be dealing with clients often who have issues with their looks and are searching for help and advice. Outstanding interpersonal skills are needed, as is a high level of personal presentation. Also, it is important to have good attention to detail. Administration skills, including cash handling, appointment setting, and record keeping, are advantageous. On average, the entry-level position as a beautician has a yearly salary of about $50,000.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Experienced beauty therapists will soon begin to earn a yearly salary of about $60,000 &ndash; $70,000. If you are promoted to the position of salon manager, you can earn $70,000 &ndash; $80,000 yearly.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage Therapist</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/massage-therapist.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage therapists mainly work in spas and sports therapy clinics. Their main tasks contain massaging muscle tissue to facilitate quick recovery and aid relaxation. The first step to getting a massage therapist job is to complete a Certificate IV course in Massage. This certificate is a nationwide recognized beginner-level massage therapy course.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a result, there are no prerequisites. You can complete it as a beginner, so it is a great start for anyone seeking a career in massage therapy. On average, the salary for massage therapists is $54,000-$56,000 per year. Generally, you will need the following skills to become a massage therapist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Decision-making skills</li>\r\n<li>Physical strength and stamina</li>\r\n<li>Empathy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tattoo Artist</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/tattoo-artist.png\" alt=\"tattoo artist\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tattoo artists do permanent artwork on their clients\' bodies by the use of ink and specialized tattoo equipment. However, they do not just stick to the typical body art. Through training, tattoo artists are able to tattoo permanent eyebrows and more. The average cost of a permanent eyebrow tattoo ranges from $400- $800.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you want to become a tattoo artist, the first thing you need to do is practice your art skills. Your art skills have to be up to an excellent standard before you can go any further in this profession.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After all, your art will be on individuals\' bodies forever. You will require a tattoo license to legitimately tattoo professionally, and taking on an apprenticeship or completing a course is essential. The average salary of a tattoo artist is $87 per hour and $65K per year.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Final Verdict</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The 4 fashion and beauty careers discussed in this article are some of the most popular in Australia and across the globe as well. In these careers, you can work in a variety of settings, either as company staff, as a solo freelancer, or as a part of a team, which means your earnings aren\'t restricted to the status quo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are interested in getting into any of the attractive careers discussed in this article, it is about time to arm yourself with the skills needed to pull the task off. Hopefully, this article on<strong> some basic skills required for high-paying beauty industries jobs in Australia</strong> will help you to do that.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Some Basic Skills Required For High Paying Beauty Industries Jobs In Australia', 'Skills Required For High Paying Beauty Industries Jobs In Australia', 'If you want to know some basic skills required for high-paying beauty industry jobs in Australia, then this article has all the things that you need to know.', 'skills-required-for-high-paying-beauty-industries-jobs-in-australia.png', NULL, '2022-07-24 22:02:51', '2022-09-20 17:08:09'),
(69, 7, 'What is Required on Your Resume for a Massage Therapist Job?', 'what-is-required-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job', 4, 'What Should Be On Your Resume For A Massage Therapist Job? Many of the candidates don\'t know the answer. So they can\'t make a proper resume and they don\'t get any job. Here I will tell you the answer to this question.', '<p>When you apply for a job you have to submit a resume to the authority. A resume is a summary of your life. There will be information about your education, your skill, your experience, and so many other things. The chances of getting a job depends on the resume. The resume has to be up to mark to show your ability to the authority. Nowadays<a href=\"../../blogs/how-to-become-a-remedial-massage-therapist-in-australia\"> massage therapy</a> is a popular job in Australia. People like to have massage therapies to relax. So the number of customers in this sector has increased. The job vacancy also increased.</p>\r\n<p>To get a job as a massage therapist you have to make a resume properly. But what should be on your resume for a massage therapist job? Many of the candidates don\'t know that. They can not make a proper resume for a massage therapist job. That\'s why they don\'t get the job. In this article, I will tell you how you can make a proper resume for a massage therapist job. There are some qualities a massage therapist must have. We will also discuss that. I will tell you which qualification a massage therapist should have. You can add these qualifications in your resume if you have. Now let\'s jump into the details.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Qualities And Skills A Successful Massage Therapist Have</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/massage-therapist-role\" alt=\"Massage Therapist skills\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To join as a massage therapist, you must submit a proper resume to the authority. Then you can get the job if you have these qualities and skills. So these should be in your resume for a massage therapist job. The qualities and skills are given below.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Academic Qualifications</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The basic thing of a resume is the academic qualification or educational qualification. If you have higher educational qualifications, it will help you to get the best massage therapist job. So if you want to be a massage therapist, you should study in this sector. So that you can learn everything about massage therapy. To become a<a href=\"../../diploma-in-remedial-massage\"> certified massage therapist</a> you need to study. There are so many vocational institutions. There are facilities for massage therapy training. You can learn everything about massage therapy like best massage techniques, the benefits of different types of oils, how to relieve pain, anxiety and so many things. You can learn about anatomy in higher courses. It doesn&rsquo;t take long to complete these types of courses. Usually it takes five months to complete a massage therapy course. After completing a course, you will get a certificate. You can mention it in your resume. It will help a lot to get a job.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Communication Skill</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/Communicate\" alt=\"Communication\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>When you give a massage to a client, you need to talk to him and you need to be gentle. So your communication skill must be up to the mark. Then if you work in a popular tourist area, then you have to talk with international clients. So if you know more than one language, it will be an advantage for you. You have to be good at English, as it is an international language. Many clients like small talks during the massage. So you should have some idea about it. Sometimes you have to tell them about the benefits of massage therapy. So you should know how to tell that.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Flexibility</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You have to be on your feet most of the time throughout the day. So you have to be physically flexible. So you should do exercises daily. If you are physically flexible, then you can do good in this job.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Experience</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Experience is a precious thing. The authorities always prioritize the candidates on the basis of experience. Because if a candidate has done the work before, he can do his best now. After completing your massage therapy course, it\'s good to work in a small parlor. So you can gain a lot of experience from it. You can mention it in your resume in the experience part. It will help you to get the job easily. It will also help you in your work. You can do the work more efficiently. So your client will be happy too. So experience is a mandatory thing you must keep in your resume. This is what should be on your resume for a massage therapist job.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Maintain Hygiene</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/keep in clean\" alt=\"Maintain Hygiene\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hygiene is a vital part of this job. You will meet so many clients every day. So you must keep your hands and the massage table clean and hygienic. Sometimes you have to come closer to the clients during massage. So you must brush your teeth. Make sure you are showered and you wear clean clothes. You can use deodorant too. It will make the client happy. So you must maintain hygiene in a massage therapist job.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Awareness</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You have to be aware of this job. As you have to deal with the human body, you must be aware. Awareness is a must in this job. If you have knowledge in anatomy, that will help you. Sometimes you need to give a massage to a person who has pain or who is pregnant. So you must be aware of the pressure you are using on their body parts. You need to understand the difference between pressure that causes more damage and pressure that heals. If you don\'t be aware, then it can cause serious injury. So you have to be careful during the massage.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Final Words</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Massage therapy is a rising business in the whole world, especially in tourist areas. So the job opportunity in this sector is increasing day by day. So if you want to apply for any job as a massage therapist, you need to submit a resume. What should be on your resume for a massage therapist job? In this article, we have discussed that. We told you about the qualities of a massage therapist. So when you make your resume, you can use this in your resume. But you must achieve these qualities first. Then you can get a job as a massage therapist easily.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'what-is-required-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job.png', NULL, '2022-08-05 23:49:14', '2022-09-20 17:06:14'),
(70, 7, 'How to Answer the Top Massage Therapist', 'how-to-answer-the-top-massage-therapist', 4, 'Finding a reputable massage therapist is not simple. First off, a lot of superb masseurs operate their own modest studios and parlors. Second, while anyone can talk about delivering a nice massage, not everybody is truly capable of doing so.', '<p>Finding a reputable massage therapist is not simple. First off, a lot of superb masseurs operate their own modest studios and parlors. Second, while anyone can talk about delivering a nice massage, not everybody is truly capable of doing so.</p>\r\n<p>If you apply for this position, the situation gets better. It won\'t be tough to pass this interview if you have a license and possibly some experience as well-perhaps even a few months or years.</p>\r\n<p>You will normally only be asked the most fundamental questions during an interview, such as your experience, motivation, availability, and compensation expectations. The owners of massage parlors may occasionally ask you to provide a massage as part of the recruiting procedure (at least, this occurs frequently in Europe).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Tell us about your professional background</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/professional-background\" alt=\"professional background\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The only experience that matters is the one involving massage. Mention all the many kinds of massages and therapies you\'ve provided to clients and talk enthusiastically about them. Show potential employers that you enjoy your work by interacting with clients and assisting them with their physical needs (and perhaps also their minds).</p>\r\n<h2>What should you do if you are just beginning this adventure, though?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Even the most seasoned massage therapists had their first employment at some point. Additionally, the scenario is not always negative for the employer&mdash;perhaps they will find a fantastic masseur in you, and they won\'t have to pay you as much as they would for a seasoned therapist.</p>\r\n<p>Talk about your workout schedule and the massages you provided while undergoing it. Every experience is preferable to none. It is still an experience, even if you simply massaged your parents or your lover at home. Inform them that the massages you provided to your clients were always well received.</p>\r\n<h2>What about this profession most inspires you?</h2>\r\n<p>TEST</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/profession\" alt=\"profession\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Pay attention to the small, everyday victories that make you happy. Things like restoring someone\'s entire range of motion or curing back pain&mdash;almost everyone has experienced it at some point in their adult lives. Having a positive dialogue with the customer and feeling good about the work you\'ve done make excellent interview answers.</p>\r\n<p>Hiring managers are aware that you cannot be a great therapist unless you are passionate about what you do. Prove to them that you enjoy massaging and that your labor has value. You are inspired to give every day your all because of this goal.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>What makes you want to work here?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Try to locate information about the spa, hotel, hospital, or massage parlor that speaks to you as you read about it. Perhaps you have years of experience receiving the same kind of massage or you believe in the therapeutic <a href=\"../../blogs/remedial-massage-vs-deep-tissue-massage-know-which-is-better\">benefits of the specific massage</a> they provide.<br />Or the location has a stellar reputation and numerous five-star ratings online.</p>\r\n<p>Perhaps you prefer to go there alone and feel at ease there. Give them a good justification for why you applied for the job with them rather than some other organization in the neighborhood. Of course, you may also highlight the compensation package, the work schedule, and the location of the job as additional factors that, in light of your other obligations, make this a suitable offer for you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>What salary goals do you have?</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../../public/blogImages/salary-goals\" alt=\"salary goals\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A challenging question, particularly if you are applying for a position in a spa, hotel, or another similar setting where you are unsure of how many massages you will actually provide each day. Although you may be busy from morning till night, there may also be slow days when you will converse with the receptionists and physiotherapists because there won\'t be much to do.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>My recommendation is to discuss either an hourly rate or a set fee for each massage. Inquire of your buddies (other masseurs) about their salaries and employment agreements. You should have a clear notion now.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, if you won\'t be the only masseuse employed there, you might choose a straightforward choice. Describe how thrilled you will be to earn as much money as other therapists in the area (or a little bit less, considering that you are just starting the job).<br />When are you available? Are you able to work on weekends? Do you mind working into the evening?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The typical working hours of this employment are one of its drawbacks. After work, in the evening, and on the weekends, people get massages. You will work primarily in the afternoons, nights, and on weekends unless you seek for a position in a hospital or a medical clinic.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Communication abilities are crucial</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>During an interview with you, hiring managers watch a number of things. Do you give them your full attention? Are you direct in your speech? Can you listen well? Do they appreciate your conversations?</p>\r\n<p>In the twenty-first century, clients need more than just a massage. They like conversing with the massage therapists and occasionally share their happiness and grief with them. This position requires excellent communication skills, therefore if you can\'t show them in the interview that you have such abilities, they won\'t hire you. Keep that in mind and make it clear that you\'re a pleasure to be around.</p>\r\n<p>You can be asked additional questions during your massage therapist job interview.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Describe the most challenging customer you\'ve ever massaged for us.</li>\r\n<li>Which massage is your favorite, and why?</li>\r\n<li>What part, in your view, does client communication play in this role?</li>\r\n<li>When did you go above and above for a client? Please describe.</li>\r\n<li>What do you think is the most challenging part of this job?</li>\r\n<li>What do you picture as a typical day like in our salon, spa, hotel, or clinic?</li>\r\n<li>How long do you hope to work at this position?</li>\r\n<li>Why should we pick you over the other candidates for the job?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>One of the simpler job interviews is for a massage <a href=\"../../blogs/what-is-required-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job\">therapist position</a>. There won\'t be many applicants for the job, and the questions you\'ll be asked about your experience, drive, availability, and client-communication skills will be mostly straightforward.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Nevertheless, you shouldn\'t undervalue the employer meet. Be ready for the questions, and don\'t forget to show that you have good listening skills and are enthusiastic about the position. I hope your interview goes well!<br />&nbsp;</p>', 'How to Answer the Top Massage Therapist', 'How to Answer the Top Massage Therapist', 'How to Answer the Top Massage Therapist? Finding a reputable massage therapist is not simple. First off, a lot of superb masseurs operate their own modest studios and parlors. Let\'s find out the answer.', 'how-to-answer-the-top-massage-therapist.png', NULL, '2022-08-20 23:31:46', '2022-09-18 09:11:00'),
(71, 7, 'Top 10 Healthy Massage Techniques Around The World', 'healthy-massage-techniques-around-the-world', 4, 'If you want to know about Massages Around The World, then this article is the perfect guide for you.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For many decades, people have been using massages as a relaxation and healing technique. According to different organizations\' reports, there are over 65 different kinds of massage techniques in the world. Many of these massage techniques originated from ancient civilizations, including Japan, China, India, Greece, and Egypt, and were executed to induce many different bodily responses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Every massage technique offers a different cultural and historical experience. Massage is more than aroma and oils. It is generally the power of touch. Consumers want massages for a variety of reasons, just as there are several massage types to choose from.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For instance, 30% of consumers who have taken a massage in 2022 said that it was a portion of a treatment plan prescribed by any medical provider, according to a report. In the meantime, other consumers took massages for pain management or pain relief, stress reduction, relaxation, or pampering.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For consumers, the finest <a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/blogs/can-massage-therapy-help-with-curvatures-of-the-spine\">massage therapy</a> option may depend on their final goals for undertaking bodywork. As there are so many different kinds of massage in this world, it can be hard to understand the dissimilarities in massage therapy techniques without having a complete overview.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To help you, we have listed the best 10 different <strong>Massages Around The World</strong> that you may want to know about in a massage therapy school or encounter as a consumer.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Top 10 Healthy Massage Techniques</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Acupressure Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/acupressure massage\" alt=\"acupressure massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Acupressure is an ancient Chinese healing technique that\'s thousands of years old. It inspired modalities like Shiatsu and is considered identical to acupuncture without the use of needles. Acupressure is effective at healing tension-related health conditions like headaches, muscle aches, backaches, sinus issues, eye strain, arthritis, neck pain, and tension because of stress.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In this massage technique, gentle yet forceful pressure is applied to the acupuncture sites on your body using the elbow, hand, or fingers to trigger the body\'s natural self-healing capabilities.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Swedish Massage</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Swedish massage, which is also called a classic massage, is possibly the most common kind of massage. Per Henrik Ling, a professor of physiology at the University of Stockholm, established this massage technique in the 1800s.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Swedish massage aims to release muscle tension to promote stress relief and relaxation. The good thing about this massage technique is that it\'s pretty versatile and can be done with hard pressure or light, vigorous or gentle, which all relies on the client\'s choice.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shiatsu Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shiatsu massage, also known as finger pressure massage, is a type of acupressure bodywork that originated in Japan. In this type of massage therapy, the masseuse uses thumbs, palms, and fingers to stimulate energy flow and your body\'s attempts to heal itself.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is also the ideal treatment for improving blood circulation and loosening up muscles. There are many other advantages as well, including decreasing tension and stress, improving signs of insomnia, and easing constipation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ayurvedic Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/ayurvedicmassage\" alt=\"Ayurvedic Massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ayurvedic massage is a 5,000 years old healing technique that was established in India. It is a system of entire body healing that checks a person spiritually, physically, and emotionally, including a combination of yoga, massage, meditation, diet, and herbal remedies. This type of massage technique improves blood circulation, offers relaxation, rejuvenates the body, and eliminates toxins.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aromatherapy Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aromatherapy is a type of massage technique that originated in ancient Greece, Egypt, and Italy. By using lotion containing essential oils or massage oils, this massage aims to promote greater relaxation and healing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">During this kind of massage technique, the client inhales the particles of these extremely concentrated plant oils, which are reported to promote psychological well-being and enhanced relaxation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sports Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the name suggests, sports massage is excellent for athletes or anybody who has a physically demanding lifestyle. This massage technique applies firmer pressure, and the focus of it is on the effect of sporting activities on the muscle groups, joints, ligaments, tendons, and soft tissues.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The massage therapist might incorporate stretching to help athletes get well from injury, boost their flexibility, and avoid future injuries.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Balinese Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Balinese Massage is a type of classic Indonesian massage technique that blends influences from different cultures like China and India. Also, it has frequently been linked to Ayurveda. This type of massage is commonly used for relaxation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">However, it can also help relieve aches, pains, and soreness, loosen tight muscles, ease breathing problems, sleep disorders, and migraines, reduce anxiety and stress, and improve overall well-being.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thai massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thai massage combines stretching techniques with gentle pressure to decrease stress and increase energy. Thai massage requires clients to lie on the floor and take part more actively in stretching and assisted yoga postures than several Western massage techniques, which call for passively lying on a table.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The advantages associated with Thai massage contain reducing stress, boosting energy levels, combating fatigue, and increasing blood circulation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Champissage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Narendra Mehta invented Champissage, and this massage technique is based on the ancient Indian head massage known as Champi, which has been practiced for more than a thousand years. It relieves stress, aches, insomnia, and pains, rebalances energy flow in the body, and promotes hair growth. Champissage also provides a deep sense of calm, peace, and tranquility.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hot Stone Massage</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/stone-massage\" alt=\"hot stone massage\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the name suggests, hot stone massage is a massage technique that is performed by placing heated stones made of volcanic rock on your body so that the stones\' weight and heat will help to relax and warm the body\'s muscles. It lets the massage therapist apply deeper pressure without inflicting discomfort. The benefits of this type of massage include pain management and relaxation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conclusion</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage can be a method for you to feel well mentally, physically, and emotionally. You can check out different forms of massage and various massage therapists to get the best form of massage and the best therapist for you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Always communicate your intentions and expectations with your chosen massage therapist, and don\'t be afraid to voice any concerns. If you have any health issues, talk to your doctor before obtaining any form of massage. We hope that this article on Massages Around The World has helped you choose the best form of massage.</p>', 'Top 10 Healthy Massage Techniques Around The World', 'Top 10 Healthy Massage Techniques Around The World', 'If you want to know about Massages Around The World, then this article is the perfect guide for you.', 'healthy-massage-techniques-around-the-world.png', NULL, '2022-08-26 03:19:43', '2022-09-20 17:04:14'),
(72, 7, 'What Equipment Will You Need for Your Massage Business to Start?', 'what-equipment-will-you-need-for-your-massage-business-to-start', NULL, 'What equipment will I need for my massage business? If you are looking for the answer to this question, the answer is here. You need some must-have equipment to start your business.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Body massage is necessary for our body. As people are knowing the benefits of massage day by day, they are heading towards it. So the massage parlour business is growing in Australia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the number of customers is increasing, so the job vacancy for a massage therapist is also increasing day by day. The job vacancy of a massage therapist is predicted to grow more than 20% in 2023.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are so many world-class universities in Australia. They give you the chance to study massage therapy courses. So after completing your study in massage therapy courses, you can work as a massage therapist as there is a<a href=\"../../blogs/what-is-required-on-your-resume-for-a-massage-therapist-job\"> job vacancy</a>. After gaining experience from your work, you can start your own business. That will be more profitable. But there is some equipment necessary for a massage business.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Here, I will tell you about the equipment you need. So, you might have the question to know \'What equipment will you need for your massage business to start?\' I will tell you the details about the essential equipment to buy before starting the business. So let\'s jump into the details.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Best 06 Essentials Equipment you need for Your Massage Business to Start</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage Table</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/massage table\" alt=\"massage table\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you are looking forward to opening your own massage business, you need to arrange some equipment for the massage parlour. The most vital equipment for a massage business is a massage table. You can not run a massage business without a massage table. Because when you give the massage to your client, he has to lay down on the table. So it is a must. So, first of all, you need to buy a massage table.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">But what kind of table should you buy? You should buy a portable massage table so that you can move it around. If it comes with a bag, that is good too. You can take it anywhere with you. A massage table is a very small thing in this business. But it is so important that you can\'t start without it. You should bring a comfortable massage table for your business so that the clients don\'t feel bad. After bringing the table to your business, you have to bring some more equipment for your business. You can bring them as your business grows.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Covers &amp; Towels</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/towels\" alt=\"towels\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">People do massage for their relaxation. A client will enjoy the massage when you put him in a comfortable position. When you do the massage, you can use towels to cover your client. So you need to buy towels. As you need to ensure maximum comfort for your client, you must use high-quality towels.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Using towel clients can get rid of lotion or oil left on their body after the massage. You can use robes before and after the massage. After the massage clients will feel relaxed. Then they might not want to put on their clothes. So they can put on towels and rest there. They can have tea or coffee in their robes. When you buy your towels and robes make sure these are comfortable. So buy soft and plush towels.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oil, Lotion &amp; Cream</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/oil-lotion\" alt=\"oil-lotion\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before starting a massage business we can think, what equipment will I need for my massage business? Oil, lotion, and cream are one of the most important pieces of equipment for a massage business. These things are used for decreasing friction. Before the massage, therapists apply these things to the body of the client.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">These are not only for decreasing friction but also used for therapeutic benefits. Sometimes customers can be happy if you keep different types of cream, oil, and lotion. If you keep varieties then they can choose their favourite from those. And of course, make sure you use the best quality product which comes without any side effects.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Music</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage is basically for relaxation. So people come to massage parlours to relax physically. To get rid of tiredness. So you must treat your client nicely. He must feel comfortable during the massage. For that, you can keep a music device in your massage parlour. So buy the best music device. You can play soulful, relaxing songs while doing a massage. Hearing those songs, customers will feel relaxed and comfortable in your massage parlour. You can use WiFi in your parlour so that they can play their favourite music easily using the internet.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Information Resources</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Massage is so beneficial for the human body. Different types of massage have different benefits. So it is necessary to know the benefits before having a massage. Many of the customers don\'t know that. So to inform them of the benefits of a massage, you can keep books, leaflets, etc about the benefits of body massage. So the clients can know the benefits of different massages and they can decide which one is suitable for them. And also you can keep a menu card, where will be all the pricing of different massages.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cleaning Products</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/cleaning-products\" alt=\"Cleaning Products\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You must keep your massage parlour nit and clean. Because massage has to be done in a <a href=\"https://www.sahealth.sa.gov.au/wps/wcm/connect/public+content/sa+health+internet/clinical+resources/clinical+programs+and+practice+guidelines/infection+and+injury+management/healthcare+associated+infections/prevention+and+management+of+infections+in+healthcare+settings/environmental+hygiene+in+healthcare#:~:text=Environmental%20hygiene%20encompasses%20effective%20cleaning,fluid%20spills%2C%20waste%20and%20linen.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hygienic environment</a>. As it is for the client&rsquo;s relaxation, if the environment is ugly your client can feel uncomfortable. So make sure you clean your massage parlour regularly. For that, you need cleaning products. So make sure you buy cleaning products when starting a massage business. You should also keep sanitisers to sanitize your hands before applying massage to the client. Make sure you use perfume and wear clean clothes. So that the client doesn&rsquo;t feel uncomfortable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Final Words</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before starting a massage business you could question yourself \"What equipment will I need for my massage business?&rdquo;, from where to buy and all that. Considering those concerns, I have tried to give you the proper instruction through this article. Hope you will have a great understanding of this article and start your own business at any time. As the massage business is profitable and in demand in Australia. But make sure you buy all the equipment mentioned in this article before starting your business. Otherwise, you can not serve your clients based on market demand.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'What Equipment Will You Need for Your Massage Business to Start?', 'What Equipment Will You Need for Your Massage Business to Start?', 'What equipment will I need for my massage business? If you are looking for the answer to this question, the answer is here. You need some must-have equipment to start your business.', 'equipment-will-you-need-for-your-massage-business-to-start.png', NULL, '2022-08-28 23:18:21', '2022-09-20 17:01:24');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(76, 7, '4 Tips to Help You Choose a Business Diploma Course Based on Your Skills', 'tips-to-help-you-choose-a-business-diploma-course-based-on-your-skills', NULL, 'Want to choose a Business Diploma course but don\'t know where to start? We have got the solution! Check out the 4 tips for choosing the perfect business diploma.', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Business Diploma Course is a popular study option in Australia. Did you know that having a Business Diploma and the right skills can help you start an awesome career? With this certification, you can become an Office Manager, Program Coordinator, or even a Senior Administrator.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are pretty high-demand jobs. For example, Program Coordinator jobs will grow by 8.2% in the coming 5 years, according to a recent estimate. However, you may get confused when you are looking for a specific course. Don&rsquo;t worry, we\'re here to support you! Let&rsquo;s reveal 4 tips to help you </span><strong>choose a Business Diploma course based on your skills</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is a Business Diploma?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-edmond-dant&egrave;s-4344860.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Business Diploma is a qualification that can help students and job seekers develop certified business skills. This fantastic certification can provide you with more academic and employment opportunities. Courses are suited for both newcomers and experienced individuals. So you can expect to learn exciting new skills while honing your existing ones.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several types of Business Diploma courses. A course can be designed on broad topics or it can focus on specific expertise. All courses have common topics like:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Workplace communication&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Managing meetings&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People management&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Critical thinking&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Project management&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Budget and Finance&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the other hand, you can go for a specialised diploma in subjects such as:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Supply chain&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Leadership&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quality auditing and compliance&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital design&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online or hybrid options are available alongside physical classes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Why Choose a Business Diploma Course?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will have amazing career opportunities with a Business Diploma. This qualification can land you a job as a:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Office Manager&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Executive Officer&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Program Coordinator</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Executive Assistant&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Senior Administrator&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What&rsquo;s more amazing is that these professions have healthy growth rates in the Australian job market. You can also apply for more specific positions with a specialised Business Diploma.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You should obtain a diploma qualification because:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your skills will be recognised&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can learn new skills&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improve your existing knowledge&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better reputation in the industry&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can pursue more advanced qualifications in the future<br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4 Tips for Choosing a Business Diploma Course Based on Your Skills&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-anna-shvets-5325104 (1).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, we\'ll present 4 tips to help you </span><strong>choose a Business Diploma course based on your skills</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Let&rsquo;s go through each of the four tips.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Set Your Career Goals&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We highly recommend you prepare a career plan before enrolling in any course. Without clear planning, you will waste valuable time. Solid objectives will ensure better decisions and fewer mistakes in your career. We suggest doing the following:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose one or more industries that interest you&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make a list of the companies and positions you&rsquo;d love to work at&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write an outline of your future goals&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensure that your goals are achievable, measurable, and clear&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make a list of the required courses&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don&rsquo;t forget to keep alternative options&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Follow Your Passion&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before selecting a particular diploma, it&rsquo;s important to identify your passion. Ask yourself questions like:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Which topic interests me the most?&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Am I comfortable studying the topic and working with it?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Does the course motivate me to learn more about the subject?&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Can I come up with creative ideas in this field?&nbsp;<br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nothing is worse than being stuck with a course or career you don&rsquo;t like. Your productivity will gradually decrease in this case. Hundreds of talented employees in Australia quit or switch jobs every year. A common reason is that they didn&rsquo;t follow their passion.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will come across high-paying jobs that require a Diploma in Digital Design. But you may be someone who loves leading a team rather than drawing pictures. If so, a Diploma of Business (Leadership) could be a better choice for you.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Broad Skills vs. Specialised Skills&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As mentioned before, a Business Diploma course may cover a specialised skill or a broader field. You can choose a specialised course to work in a specific role like supply chain or accounting. For more generalised managerial positions, consider choosing a regular Diploma of Business. Your choice will mostly depend on personal preference, your passion, and your abilities.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Suppose you are efficient at making calculations. But your weakness lies in communicating with others. You can either go for a Diploma of Accounting based on your strength. Or you can work on your weaknesses through a Diploma of Marketing and Communication. Enrolling in a foundational course before a diploma will also help you identify your natural skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Portfolio and Skills Development&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Australian institutions often partner with reputed business organisations while teaching a Business Diploma Course. You should choose such a course because it will provide you with practical industry experience. You will get to see real-life applications of business theories. This experience will enrich your portfolio as well.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is useful for learning practical work-related skills as well. Working with partner companies is like having a sneak peek of industry secrets and processes.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Business Diploma Course in Australia&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Numerous reputed organisations all over Australia offer Business Diploma qualifications. However, remember two things before enrolling in a course:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The certificate and the organisation are both recognised by the authorities. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Consider the cost and time (A course will cost you around $300 every month. The course duration is usually 12 months)&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;<br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contact different RTOs (Recognised Training Organisations) and other institutes before making a decision. Do not hesitate to discuss the course plan, costs, and other alternatives.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conclusion&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So there you go! These were our 4 tips that will be very useful for your career journey. We hope that the information will assist you to </span><strong>choose a Business Diploma course based on your skills</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Just make sure that you study something that you love and get a recognised qualification. We wish you all the best!&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Choose a Business Diploma Course Based on your Skills', 'Want to choose a Business Diploma course but don\'t know where to start? We have got the solution! Check out the 4 tips for choosing the perfect business diploma.', 'choose-a-business-diploma-course-based-on-your-skills.png', NULL, '2022-09-18 04:20:22', '2022-09-20 16:59:45');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(79, 7, 'The Importance of Nationally Recognized Qualifications for Beauty Therapists in Australia', 'importance-of-nationally-recognised-qualifications-for-beauty-therapists-in-australia', NULL, 'Are you planning to enter into the exciting world of beauty therapy? If so, let us discuss the importance of qualifications for beauty therapists in Australia.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">It&rsquo;s no surprise that beauty standards and norms are changing all over the globe. Trending beauty concepts like body positivity and </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">skinimalism</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> are spreading like wildfire! Skin care and grooming are among the top social media trends.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">This massive popularity of beauty care content on TikTok and Instagram means one thing: beauty therapists are more popular than ever! The job has become a highly sought-after career path. So, we&rsquo;re getting a lot of questions about the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">qualifications for beauty therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There is little to no formal requirement for becoming a beauty therapist in this country. So, you may wonder if you should obtain a qualification in the first place. You may have queries regarding various courses as well. Let&rsquo;s clear up this confusion and understand the importance of nationally recognised qualifications for this profession.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Who is a Beauty Therapist?&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty therapists are professionals who apply a variety of techniques to treat different body parts of their clients. Beauty therapy is non-medical in nature. It mostly works externally on skin and hair. Therapists will frequently use premium grooming products and devices.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty therapists can be classified into different types based on individual expertise. For example, hair stylists are best for hair grooming. You can even find more specialised places like head spas. Head spas are well-known for their relaxation services.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-gustavo-fring-3985328.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"822\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Why Beauty Therapists Have Become So Popular</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Exciting trends are transforming the beauty care industry. The attitudes and habits of the population are changing as well. For example, men are taking grooming and skin care routines more seriously. Gone are the days when only women dominated the client base of beauty therapists. As a result, the scope and reach of this art have greatly expanded.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Some common sources of modern beauty trends are:</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Influencers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">International pop culture (K-pop and J-pop)&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Celebrities (Movies, sports, music, and web series)&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Product reviews on social media&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Stories and hashtags (TikTok and Instagram)&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty products available online</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The number of Australians who regularly visit parlours and spas is growing. Today, virtually all generations from different backgrounds are using some kind of skin care. More people are consulting therapists to improve their appearance for events or daily life. Others visit these professionals to try out a trending makeover.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">For these reasons, the demand for skilled beauty therapists is very high. Jobs are generally well-paid with a comfortable work environment.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">A Typical Visit to a Beauty Therapist</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Generally, a visit to a therapist can be broken down into </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">3 stages</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">. Let&rsquo;s take a look.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">A Client Initially Contacts the Parlour or Spa&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There are many ways a client will come to know about a place. Influencer check-ins, reviews, and promotional campaigns are a few things that can make a business popular. Then the client may call the business or visit the place in person. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty therapists have to provide amazing customer service in a polite and welcoming tone. Clients get basic information about available services from them. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Booking an Appointment&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">An appointment can be booked online or over the phone in most places. The availability of appointments depends on how busy the business is.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Getting the Service&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The client then meets the beautician and talks about his or her requirements. After listening to the client, the therapist will discuss treatment options, recommendations, and tips. Depending on the issue, the therapist may perform: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Grooming services like hairdressing and pedicures </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Face or body treatments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Hair removal services&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Makeovers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Relaxation techniques like massage&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Premium services using modern technology&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /></span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"><br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">The Importance of Recognised Qualifications for Beauty Therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/blobid0\" alt=\"\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">As you can see, there are several responsibilities for a beautician. A well-rounded practitioner can work with multiple techniques and tools. It can be very difficult to learn about beauty therapy without enrolling in a course. Therefore, we highly recommend obtaining a qualification in the field. Let us now explain the main reasons.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">An Opportunity to Learn More&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">To be qualified, you usually have to complete a course over a period of time. A course will be divided into multiple topics or units of competency. A beauty therapy course will teach you about common skills like manicures, hair colouring, facials, massages, etc. You will also learn about advanced treatments that use lasers, microdermabrasion, and chemicals.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">A qualified professional is much better equipped to work in the job market.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">It Ensures Safety</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Qualified therapists are better informed of hygiene standards and safety regulations. They know how to properly operate the tools and apply the right products. Accidents and errors are less common. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Your Skills are Recognised</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Having a qualification means that your skills have been assessed and compared with established standards in the country. This means that you\'re a recognised and certified professional in the field. As a result, your reputation will increase in the job market. Qualified beauty therapists will get better jobs and more clients.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Finish Work Faster and More Effectively&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">A qualification will enrich your skills and capabilities. You can experiment with creative and fresh ideas. Your overall work will be faster and more precise as well.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Starting Your Own Salon or Spa</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Some regions in Australia will require you to have a qualification like a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy to open a parlour or spa business. Therefore, getting qualified will help you in the long run.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Specialised Roles&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">You will need advanced qualifications for specialised roles like dermal therapist or cosmetic injectables nurse. The Bachelor of Dermal Sciences is a prerequisite for these positions.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">So there are amazing job prospects after obtaining a beauty therapy qualification in Australia.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/pexels-gustavo-fring-3985344.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Types of Qualification</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There are many different courses in Australia that can prepare you for a career in the beauty industry. The most popular options are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Diploma in Beauty Therapy (Course duration: Approximately 6 months)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy (Course duration: Approximately 1 year)&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Bachelor of Dermal Sciences (Course duration: Approximately 4 years)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /></span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Short courses (Specific beauty care skills)&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Are you interested in a certificate or diploma course in beauty therapy? If you are, check out the RTOs in Australia. RTOs or Recognised Training Organisations are certified organisations that can help you get formal training and qualifications.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Conclusion&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty therapy is a very enjoyable and lucrative profession. You get to create creative routines and see the smile on your client&rsquo;s face.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The demand for skilled beauticians will keep increasing everywhere. So it&rsquo;s important to have nationally recognised </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">qualifications for beauty therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">. Always remember to choose a certified institution for getting qualified.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'Qualifications for Beauty Therapists in Australia', 'Are you planning to enter into the exciting world of beauty therapy? If so, let us discuss the importance of qualifications for beauty therapists in Australia.', 'the-importance-of-nationally-recognized-qualifications-for-beauty-therapists-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2022-09-20 16:33:19', '2022-09-22 06:04:08');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(80, 7, 'Top 6 Career Tips for Beauty Therapists in Australia', 'career-tips-for-beauty-therapists-in-australia', NULL, 'If you dream of building an amazing career in the beauty industry, this guide is for you! Introducing top 6 career tips for beauty therapists in Australia.', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Who doesn&rsquo;t love a glow up? Australians definitely do. Every year, the </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">beauty spending of an Australian woman</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> can reach a whopping $3,600! With a few tips, you can build an amazing career in this field. Let&rsquo;s discuss some important </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">career tips for beauty therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">If you enjoy giving beauty advice to others, becoming a beauty therapist can be an exciting and rewarding journey. Like any other expertise, you need to develop some qualities and qualifications. The job also involves a great deal of creativity.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Demand for Beauty Therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Australians are spending more money on beauty products than ever. Beauty and grooming practices have become a norm across all genders and generations. New fashion and beauty trends are popping up every week thanks to social media.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">This growing popularity of beauty care means one thing: huge demand for beauty therapists in Australia. To give you an example, the hair removal market alone will </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">grow to $1,131.8 Million by 2027</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">. So you can easily understand why beauty therapist jobs are so lucrative.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Basic Responsibilities of a Beauty Therapist</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There are many different services a typical beauty therapist will offer. Depending on individual skills and experience, a practitioner can have more specialised roles as well. For example, there are therapists who deliver laser treatments only. However, most will have common duties like:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Understanding every client&rsquo;s requirements</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Providing regular grooming services like pedicures and manicures</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Delivering skin/hair treatments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Selling products&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Providing customised services&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">A beauty therapist may also be responsible for transaction processing and administration.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Career Tips for Beauty Therapists in Australia&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">To be successful in this industry, you should have the right mix of creativity and skills. The beauty business is highly competitive. Therefore, you need certain qualities to stand out. Let&rsquo;s look at the top 6 career tips for this profession.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Develop Your Communication Skills</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Having good interpersonal communication skills is essential for this job. On a normal day, you have to welcome your clients to the salon. You should make them feel comfortable with your words. You need to communicate effortlessly with your clients to understand their requirements and issues.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Every client will be different. Give extra suggestions if needed. Always remember to be polite with them and provide top-notch customer service.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Create Innovative Concepts</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">As a beauty therapist, you have to work with the latest techniques and trends. But you also need to know how to add your own ideas to the mix. Always keep experimenting with original concepts. Your unique skincare routine may just become the next big hit!&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Observe other practitioners online to learn about their techniques and approach. You&rsquo;ll be surprised at the ideas you can develop this way. Some beauty care professionals even get inspiration from trending sources like Anime or video games! Putting on makeup like fictional characters has been a social media trend for quite a while.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Be Patient and Pay Attention to the Details</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">A single session of hair styling or skin treatment can take over an hour to perform properly. To avoid any accident or mistake, you need to have a clear focus. Therapists should be attentive while working with intricate details. You may be required to stand for extended periods of time during your shift.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Being patient and attentive is crucial for perfecting the use of various beauty care products, tools, and methods.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Be Passionate and Learn Proactively&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">In the dynamic world of beauty therapy, you should have a strong motivation to learn about new ideas and techniques. The possibilities are endless if you are passionate enough!&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">You should proactively study the beauty standards across different cultures and nations. Study the historical fashion movements. You can learn about many interesting things from these sources.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Use a Social Media Strategy&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Social media platforms like TikTok and Instagram are popular choices for a growing number of beauty therapists in Australia. Individuals from Generation Z rely heavily on these apps for skin care routines and fashion trends.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty business owners are regularly using hashtags, influencers, and product review clips to promote their products and services. This approach will keep getting more popular. Therefore, you should be well-informed about this strategy. Study available techniques like SEO, ad promotions, and tagging to better promote your business on social media.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty Therapy Qualifications</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Recognised qualifications can be a great addition to your resume. Having a qualification also means that your beauty therapy skills are certified. There are numerous interesting courses in Australia that can get you qualified. Some qualifications cover a wide range of skills. Others are more specialized. Some of the popular courses are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Diploma in Beauty Therapy&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Diploma in Remedial Massage&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate III in Hair Dressing&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The length of each course will vary. You will need around 6 months to obtain a Diploma in Beauty Therapy. A Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy may require twice that duration.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Before choosing any qualification, learn more about its course content and job prospects. We highly suggest obtaining a qualification. Doing so will greatly develop your competence and reputation.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty Therapy Qualifications at RTOs&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Recognised Training Organisations (RTOs) in Australia provide the aforementioned beauty therapy qualifications. RTOs are an amazing place to get qualified or receive training. These organisations specialise in certifying an individual&rsquo;s skills. They also have provisions for international students.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Conclusion&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">You now know the top </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">career tips for beauty therapists in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">. By following these tips, you can get a high-paying job in this wonderful industry.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Skilled beauty therapists are in great demand. You can even pursue specialised roles such as spa therapist or salon manager with the right qualifications and proactive learning. Undoubtedly, it&rsquo;s an excellent career path!</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'Career Tips for Beauty Therapists in Australia', NULL, 'top-6-career-tips-for-beauty-therapists-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2022-09-21 12:14:30', '2022-09-22 06:03:47');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(81, 7, 'Why You Need a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia', 'why-you-need-a-certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy-in-australia', NULL, 'Let’s understand the benefits of obtaining a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia! We will explain the important details and applications of this qualification.', '<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Do you know how much Aussies spend every year on buying beauty care items? The answer will surprise you: it&rsquo;s an incredible $22 billion! Innovative beauty products and therapies have been historically popular in every major region of the country. As a result, more Australians are becoming interested in working in this industry.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Beauty therapy is not strictly regulated in Australia like other professions. However, you will come across several qualifications for this skill. A popular choice is Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy. Comparing this qualification with other options can be confusing. So let&rsquo;s learn more about the importance and the course content of a </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Do Beauty Therapists Have High Demand?&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">According to a recent Australian government report, beauty therapist jobs are growing rapidly. Official projections estimate that there will be 42,400 workers in this sector by 2026. Clearly, these jobs are among the most exciting employment opportunities in the country.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Besides the booming business and decent pay, beauty therapist roles are also female-friendly. Moreover, you will definitely love this profession if you prefer sedentary work with little physical labour but a lot of creativity. Therefore, these jobs are in good demand among employers and job seekers alike.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Common Beauty Therapy Qualifications&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Before diving into the details, we should identify the various courses related to beauty therapy in Australia. The most common qualifications are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Diploma in Beauty Therapy </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Diploma of Salon Management&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">For the specialised position of dermal therapist, you can pursue the following advanced courses:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Advanced Diploma in Skin Therapy </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Bachelor of Dermal Sciences&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Some institutions also offer short courses. These courses are great for testing the waters. The shorter format introduces you to basic concepts like make-up application and eyelash services. You can try a short course to see if the work appeals to you.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There are additional qualifications for other related skills as well. Certificate III in Hairdressing and the Diploma in Remedial Massage are two good examples. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The Benefits of a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">There are many advantages to being qualified in the job market. This is true for the beauty therapy sector as well. As mentioned earlier, there is little to no formal requirement for becoming a beauty therapist in Australia.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">However, many well-known businesses will have qualification requirements for hiring. Obtaining a qualification will certainly give you an edge in this competition. Let&rsquo;s see the benefits of a qualification like Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Better and Higher-paying Jobs&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Hundreds of candidates apply at reputed salons every year in Australia. Better remuneration, a quality environment, and valuable work experience are a few reasons why these salons attract so many applicants. These places often ask for at least a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy or an equivalent course.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /></span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Better Service Quality&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">To obtain a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy or a similar qualification, you have to go through structured coursework. You will learn about various techniques and tools used in a salon or parlour. You&rsquo;ll learn how to operate them properly and safely. So the quality of your work and efficiency will greatly improve.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Your Skills Are Certified&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certified professionals will assess your abilities and skills in a recognised course. After successful completion, your skills will be certified or proven as compatible with industry standards. Your reputation will also increase with a certification.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Better Ideas&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Completing a course will enrich your knowledge of beauty therapy. You will learn a lot from popular examples. This will allow you to create new ideas and experiment with your creativity. This step is crucial to becoming successful in this business.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"2\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Starting a Business&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The local authority may have qualification requirements if you want to start a beauty therapy business. For example, a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy is mandatory for opening a beauty therapy business in the Northern Territory. Before you decide to open a salon or spa, contact the relevant local authority for more details.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">What Will I Learn in the Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy?&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">In this course, you will learn about diverse beauty treatment topics like:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Facial treatments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Waxing services&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Pedicures and manicures&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Massages&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Make-ups&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"5\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Advanced techniques like laser treatments&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">You will also learn about useful concepts like basic business transactions and using online tools.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Many institutions will provide apprenticeships along with the course. You will work under an experienced beauty therapist as an apprentice. This practical approach will help you to apply different methods in a real-life setting. Therefore, we highly suggest having this experience.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Course Length of a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy<br />&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Completing a Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy takes around a year. In comparison, the duration of a Diploma in Beauty Therapy is shorter (around 6 months). On the other hand, it can take around 4 years for a Bachelor of Dermal Sciences degree.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">The length of any course will depend on the institution and your progress.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /></span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">RTOs and the Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Reputed Australian RTOs or Registered Training Organisations can help you to get qualified with a </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">. Please take a look at the RTOs if you are planning to build a career in the beauty industry.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Final Words&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Obtaining qualifications can be an amazing starting point for a career in the Australian beauty industry. Hopefully, our guide has helped you better understand the importance and benefits of a</span><strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> Certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Now you can better decide if this qualification is right for you. Always remember to choose a recognised institution for any course or training. Best of luck!&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'certificate IV in Beauty Therapy in Australia', NULL, 'why-you-need-a-certificate-iv-in-beauty-therapy-in-australia.jpeg', NULL, '2022-09-28 12:15:07', '2022-10-04 04:00:49');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(83, 7, 'An Overview of the Demand for Hairdressers and 07 Important Hairdresser Skills', 'demand in the hairdressing industry', NULL, 'Qualified hairdressers are in high demand in the hairdressing industry. Let\'s learn more about this job\'s demand and the most important hairdresser skills.', '<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Did you know that there is a huge demand for skilled hairdressers and hair stylists in Australia? The country is a melting pot of various cultures from all over the world. There are numerous trendy hairstyles for people from all age groups. &nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">As a result, salons require skilled people. It&rsquo;s no surprise that qualified hairdressers are in high </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">demand in the hairdressing industry</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. In this article, we&rsquo;ll discuss this demand and the important skills needed for the job. So let&rsquo;s learn more about hairdressing!&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Why Qualified Hairdressers are in High Demand in the Hairdressing Industry?&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Demand for Hairdressers and Important Hairdresser Skills.jpg\" alt=\"Demand for Hairdressers and Important Hairdresser Skills\" width=\"733\" height=\"473\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">The grooming industry was hit hard during the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">COVID-19 pandemic</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. But now the situation is on its way to recovery. But now the situation is on its way to recovery. There are many new job openings for hairdressers in every state. Thanks to the rise of social media platforms, different fashion trends, including new haircuts, have become popular throughout Australia.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">After the lockdown, spending on grooming services like haircuts increased by </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">15.4%</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> in the country. This was a finding in the latest report from the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Australian Bureau of Statistics (ABS)</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. So the demand for qualified hairdressers will keep increasing in the future.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Where Will I Work as a Hairdresser?&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">There are various types of businesses that employ hairdressers. The majority of employers in this industry are from:</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Salons&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Spas&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Beauty parlours&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hotels and resorts&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Depending on the position, you have to provide several services to a range of clients. Some openings will have better pay than others. Certified individuals with strong skills will definitely have more priority.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">7 Important Hairdresser Skills</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Important Hairdresser Skills\" alt=\"Important Hairdresser Skills\" width=\"731\" height=\"470\" /></span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We are often asked questions regarding the most important hairdresser skills. There are certain skills that will definitely increase your </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">demand in the hairdressing industry</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. So now&nbsp;we will discuss </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">7&nbsp;important hairdresser skills</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> that you should develop for this career. &nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>1. Passion for Continuous Learning&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You should have a strong passion for learning for this job. As mentioned before, there are new styles and trends in hair due to the boom of social media. You should be aware of these fashion trends. Many clients will ask you for trending haircuts. So you should know how to cut hair in the most popular styles. Some of the ways you can learn more about this art are: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"5\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Observe the influencers and grooming professionals online&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"6\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Connect with other hairdressers and hair stylists&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"7\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Visit different salons and parlors </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"8\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Study new techniques and methods&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>2. Customer Service&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">As a hairdresser, you have to politely listen to your clients and provide them with the haircutting and styling services they need. This is one of the main skills in this sector. Some of the benefits of great customer service are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"9\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will retain more customers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"10\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can create long-term loyalty and trust&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"11\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Existing clients will spread positive word-of-mouth&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"12\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Better reputation in the industry&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>3. Professionalism&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Good professionalism lies at the core of good hairdressing service. It will help you to have a good image where you work. You won&rsquo;t be able to progress in this sector without being professional. Some of the important things in the workplace are: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"13\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Maintain punctuality and discipline&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"14\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Respect the privacy of your clients and co-workers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"15\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Be proactive and have a positive attitude &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"16\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Maintain safety and hygiene while working&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>4. Creativity&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will work with various colors, styles, and techniques. Therefore, having a creative mind will definitely help you stand out in this field. Creativity can help you create your own technique. So don&rsquo;t be afraid to try out new ideas. We suggest doing the following to come up with creative ideas: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"17\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Experiment with different tools and products&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"18\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Study local and international hair styling methods&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"19\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Try to create original concepts&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"20\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Attend workshops and keep yourself updated&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>5. Teamwork and Communication</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You have to work with a team of hairdressers, hair stylists, and other experts in this job. You often have to collaborate with them to find the perfect solution for the client. That&rsquo;s why you should focus on teamwork and interpersonal communication skills. Some of the benefits of good teamwork and communication are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"21\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can accurately identify the client&rsquo;s requirements&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"22\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">The team can address these requirements more effectively&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"23\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Better delivery of services&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"24\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Close cooperation with the co-workers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>6. Patience&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hairdressers have to be very patient to ensure quality service. They have to stand for extended time periods to arrange the hair, wash it, etc. So you should develop patience for this job. There are many advantages to having this quality:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"25\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can ensure customer satisfaction&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"26\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You won&rsquo;t rush your work and will avoid mistakes&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"27\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Better quality of work</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"28\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can adapt to the physical aspects of this job&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>7. Sales Skills</h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Sales skills are necessary for success as an employee, a business owner, a team leader, or a manager. You can attract more clients with better sales skills. So to compete with other businesses, you should have these skills. Let\'s take a look at how these skills will help you: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"29\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Promoting your own business or service&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"30\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Find new business opportunities&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"31\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Increase the sales of hair grooming products&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"32\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Developing effective sales campaigns&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">Ways to Improve Your Hairdresser Skills&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Enrolling in a recognized course is one of the best ways to improve your expertise. There are several </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Recognised Training Organisations (RTOs)</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> in Australia that offer comprehensive courses such as the </span><a href=\"../certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">SHB30416 - Certificate III in Hairdressing</span></strong></a><span data-contrast=\"none\">. Successfully completing a course will help you learn valuable techniques and certify your skills.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">Conclusion<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hairdressing can be a very creative and fun job. With the right qualifications and personal qualities, you can do very well in this industry. Having a nationally recognized qualification will greatly increase your </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">demand in the hairdressing industry</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. Keep learning with passion and try new techniques. You will certainly become an awesome hairdresser if you do these! &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'demand in the hairdressing industry, hairdressing industry', 'demand in the hairdressing industry', 'Qualified hairdressers are in high demand in the hairdressing industry. Let\'s learn more about this job\'s demand and the most important hairdresser skills.', 'an-overview-of-the-demand-for-hairdressers-and-07-important-hairdresser-skills.jpg', NULL, '2022-10-16 12:39:27', '2022-10-26 06:11:35');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(84, 7, 'Our Top 06 Tips on How to Write a Proper Hairdresser Resume', 'How to Write a Proper Hairdresser Resume', NULL, 'A properly formatted resume is a must-have for anyone working in the beauty industry. Let\'s go through the top tips for making a good resume for a hairdresser job.', '<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">According to a </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2022</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> study by </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Zety</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">, only </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2%</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> to </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">3.4%</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> of all job applications are successful in landing a job. The results of this study were found after analysing more than </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">133,000</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> resumes. It&rsquo;s very clear that there is a huge competition. Therefore, you should develop a good resume for any sector, including the beauty and grooming&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Writing a resume can be a daunting task for many job seekers. We&rsquo;ve also been getting many queries about resumes. So today we will list our top tips for making a good </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">resume for a hairdresser job</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span class=\"TextRun SCXW69780184 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-AU\" xml:lang=\"EN-AU\" data-contrast=\"none\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW69780184 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"heading 1\">3 Reasons Why a Good Resume is Important in the Beauty and Grooming Industry</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span class=\"TextRun SCXW69780184 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-AU\" xml:lang=\"EN-AU\" data-contrast=\"none\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW69780184 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"heading 1\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW69780184 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Beauty and Grooming Industry\" alt=\"Beauty and Grooming Industry\" width=\"732\" height=\"477\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Before we dive into the tips, let&rsquo;s discuss the importance of a resume in the beauty and grooming industry. A solid reputation for your skills is mandatory for building a career. A proper resume is one of the best ways to highlight your expertise. Therefore, all hairdressers should make good resumes for more career prospects and newer opportunities.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Let&rsquo;s take a quick look at why recruiters in the beauty and grooming industry look for quality resumes.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">1. They Provide a Quick Description of the Candidate&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Usually, salons receive hundreds of job applications for every opening. So hiring managers want to go through your skills and experience quickly. A properly written resume provides these details in a concise manner. Hiring managers should be able to identify your expertise efficiently. This will save them time and they will know if you are a good fit for the position.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2. They Make a Good Impression&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">A solid resume with the right skills and qualifications can make a very good impression on employers. A list of your top hair grooming clients and projects will definitely bring you high-paying job offers.&nbsp; </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">3. They Express the Enthusiasm of the Candidate&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Excellent resumes are great storytellers. They show your inner desire and enthusiasm for the industry in just one or two pages. As a hairdresser, you need to have a passion for your work. Therefore, resumes are a fantastic way to inform employers about your interest in the field. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW256804236 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-AU\" xml:lang=\"EN-AU\" data-contrast=\"none\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW256804236 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"heading 1\">Top 06 Tips for Making a Good Resume for a Hairdresser Job&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW256804236 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Tips for Making a Good Resume for a Hairdresser Job\" alt=\"Tips for Making a Good Resume for a Hairdresser Job\" width=\"733\" height=\"474\" /></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You should know about the importance of good resumes by now. A quality resume has certain features that help it stand out. So let\'s go through the 06 tips for making a good </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">resume for a hairdresser job</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">1. Include the Skills that the Recruiter Is Looking For&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You should prepare a resume that highlights your hairdressing skills in a clear manner. If you have a lot of experience, it&rsquo;s best not to list all of your skills in your application.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We suggest you focus on the following:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Trending and high-demand skills&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Meeting the employer&rsquo;s expectations&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Making multiple resumes if needed&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Brief summary of each skill&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Accuracy and transparency of information&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2. Mention Both Soft and Hard Skills&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You should have a diverse mix of skills on your resume. Hard skills will reflect your technical expertise in hairdressing. Soft skills are general skills that are important for the workplace. Both are equally important. We often see resumes that show little to no soft skills. Try to avoid this.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Let&rsquo;s take a look at some of the most common hard skills in a hairdresser job:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Cutting hair in different styles</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Coloring the hair</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259,&quot;335559991&quot;:360}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hair and scalp treatments</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259,&quot;335559991&quot;:360}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the most common soft skills are:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Interpersonal communication&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Ability to work in a team&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Professionalism at work</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">3. Include Relevant Qualifications and Licences&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You should mention your certifications and licenses in the resume. This could be a game-changer. This industry has no formal entry requirements. However, a recognized qualification can add huge value to your portfolio. You can consider pursuing a qualification like the </span><a href=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/certificate-iii-in-hairdressing\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">SHB30416 - Certificate III in Hairdressing</span></strong></a><span data-contrast=\"none\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">When including any qualification or license, don&rsquo;t forget about the following:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">The highest qualification will come first&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Full course title and its code&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Learning outcomes of the course&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">A brief description of the details of your licence&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Be careful about the dates&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">4. Highlight Your Work Experience in the Industry&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Remember to always add relevant work experience. This section will demonstrate your practical ability and industry exposure. Many experienced candidates make the mistake of just mentioning the job titles. As a result, the hiring manager cannot accurately assess the candidate or know much about their previous responsibilities.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Therefore, our suggestions are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Talk about the key duties of your previous jobs</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Connect your skills with your experience&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Use numbers to describe your performance output&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Mention significant career achievements</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Include referrals from previous supervisors&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">5. Use an Appropriate Style of Language</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hiring managers reject a large number of job applications due to various silly mistakes. You should be careful about these errors. There are many different styles and formats for resumes online. But remember that there is no single correct style. The format of your resume will depend a lot on the position you&rsquo;re applying for.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can follow these recommendations for better writing:</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Avoid using jargon and difficult words</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Convey the information in a clear tone</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">The language should be polite but to the point</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Try not to write a very long resume</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"5\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Avoid repetitiveness (recruiters don&rsquo;t like this at all!)</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">6. Prepare a Cover Letter Along with the resume&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">A cover letter is an additional document usually attached to the resume on a job application. It is basically a letter addressing the recruiter that summarises your qualifications, experience, and career interests. Many job seekers tend to avoid making it. But a nicely formatted cover letter will make you look a lot more professional. </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">To write an awesome cover letter, you should remember to:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Show why you are suitable for the applied position&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Mention your technical knowledge and expertise</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Demonstrate your passion for the art of hairdressing</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Talk about how you can contribute to the business&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Prepare a number of templates for different applications&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Conclusion&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We hope that you will find our 06 tips for writing a good </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">resume for a hairdresser job</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> useful. Remember to always work on your techniques and learn new ones.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Be aware of the latest hair grooming trends and products. With the right combination of creativity, skills, and experience, you can build an awesome career in this field. Best wishes!</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'resume for a hairdresser job ', 'resume for a hairdresser job ', 'A properly formatted resume is a must-have for anyone working in the beauty industry. Let\'s go through the top tips for making a good resume for a hairdresser job.', 'how-to-write-a-proper-hairdresser-resume.jpg', 'How to Write a Proper Hairdresser Resume', '2022-10-17 15:40:55', '2022-10-25 14:00:00');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(85, 7, 'Top 07 Benefits of Having a Vocational Qualification', 'benefits of having a vocational qualification', NULL, 'A vocational qualification can have a very positive impact on your career. Let us learn more about the value of a vocational qualification in Australia.', '<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Vocational training programs and qualifications are becoming very popular in Australia. Many students are enrolling in these courses. We have been getting many questions regarding these qualifications.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">So today let&rsquo;s understand the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">value of a vocational qualification</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> in Australia. We&rsquo;ll discuss the 07 benefits of having these certifications.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong>What Is a Vocational Qualification in Australia?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Vocational Qualification in Australia\" alt=\"Vocational Qualification in Australia\" width=\"731\" height=\"487\" />&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Vocational qualifications are nationally recognised qualifications. You can obtain this qualification after successfully completing a </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">VET (Vocational Education and Training)</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> program. These courses are known for teaching practical skills in the concerned industry. Vocational qualifications are highly valued by companies all over Australia.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">07 Benefits of Having a Vocational Qualification&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Now we will discuss some of the benefits of vocational training. So let us take a quick look at the 07 benefits of having a vocational qualification.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">1. Better Technical Knowledge&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You have to study a wide range of topics to obtain a vocational qualification. You will be assessed by experts through various tests. These rigorous assessments will better prepare you for the workplace. Through a vocational qualification, you will have sound technical knowledge of the field.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">The main advantages of having better technical knowledge:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Properly use the techniques and tools at work&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Quick understanding of the tasks and assignments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Solve challenging issues in the workplace&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Develop new strategies and plans&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2. Learn Practical Skills&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Most institutes collaborate with industry partners while delivering the courses. So you will get the practical experience of working in a real-life setting. This approach is very effective in giving the students an overall understanding of the workplace. Through this practical experience, you will learn a wide set of skills very quickly.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the pros of developing practical skills:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Effectively apply theories in real-life situations&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It will increase your employability&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Higher efficiency in the workplace&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Reduce accidents and other mishaps on the job&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">3. Enter High-Demand Industries&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Vocational certifications have great value in many high-demand industries. For example, the beauty and grooming industries are growing rapidly in Australia. A beauty therapy vocational qualification can be your first step towards a career in this field. People from all over the country are pursuing vocational training for this reason.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Why high-demand industries are good for your career:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will have much better pay&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">There are numerous businesses and positions to choose from</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">A very positive impact on your portfolio&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">These industries have strong future growth&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">4. Better Career Opportunities&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">One of the main reasons for the popularity of vocational training in Australia is that it can lead to better career opportunities. If you develop the right skills and portfolio through this training, you won&rsquo;t have to wait for a job. Right now, there is a huge skills shortage in Australia. Qualified individuals will certainly have more lucrative job opportunities.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the career benefits of having a vocational qualification:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">The potential of having many good job offers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Get a pay raise and other benefits</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Quick career progression through promotions&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Strong reputation due to certified skills&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">5. Pursue Higher Education</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Obtaining a vocational qualification will allow you to pursue higher qualifications. You can learn about more advanced topics and further increase your knowledge. So, this is a fantastic option for those who want to take their skills to the next level. Many students pursue a diploma after completing a certificate course.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the benefits of having higher qualifications:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Increased value in the industry&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Expert knowledge in the field&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Improve the technical skills related to work&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can apply for a more specialised position&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">6. Build Connections in the Industry&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Having strong connections is very important for a bright career in any industry in the 21st century. A recognised vocational certification will help you build these connections in the industry. As mentioned before, you have to work with industry partners in these courses. You will get to meet many professionals and thus increase your connections.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the advantages of having strong connections:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can find new opportunities&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Become a well-known person in your industry&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Learn new things from your connections&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Promotes a healthy and motivating environment&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">7. Open Your Own Business&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can even consider opening your own business after completing one of these courses. You can lead a more <a href=\"../../blogs/what-equipment-will-you-need-for-your-massage-business-to-start\">successful business</a> with a vocational qualification. This is because you will learn deeply about the industry\'s norms and trends. Therefore, we highly recommend vocational qualifications for those who want to open a new business.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">How vocational training can help your new business:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can run the business more effectively&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Properly monitor the business activities due to your knowledge&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Improve your promotional strategies</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Develop strong competitive strategies&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Nationally Recognised Vocational Qualifications&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Now that you know about the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">value of a vocational qualification</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">, let&rsquo;s look at some of the courses. There are several Recognised Training Organisations (RTOs) all over Australia that offer vocational qualifications. There are many options to choose from based on the industry and the level of difficulty. Examples of nationally recognised vocational certifications:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma in Remedial Massage&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">SHB30416 - Certificate III in Hairdressing&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Usually, diplomas are more advanced courses compared to regular certificate courses.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Conclusion&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We hope that you now have a clear idea of the benefits and </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">value of a vocational qualification</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. Before choosing any course, spend some time researching the program. Always remember to enroll in a recognised course at a recognized institution. This will ensure the validity of your qualification.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Choose a vocational training program to take your career to the next level!</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'value of a vocational qualification ', 'value of a vocational qualification ', 'A vocational qualification can have a very positive impact on your career. Let us learn more about the value of a vocational qualification in Australia.', 'benefits-of-having-a-vocational-qualification.jpg', NULL, '2022-10-24 08:51:36', '2022-10-26 06:09:30');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_slug`, `category_id`, `blog_summery`, `blog_details`, `meta_tags`, `meta_keys`, `meta_desc`, `thumbnail`, `thumbnail_alt`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(86, 7, '07 Top Reasons to Pursue a HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia', '07-top-reasons-to-pursue-a-hlt52015-diploma-of-remedial-massage-in-australia', NULL, 'Let\'s take a look at the HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia. Know the 07 reasons why this qualification is great for massage therapists.', '<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Do you want to become a massage therapist? The </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia </span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">is an amazing option for those who want to excel in this career. This course teaches advanced massage therapy techniques and methods. As a result, it has become a very popular choice among students all over Australia.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We have received many queries about message therapy courses. So let&rsquo;s discuss this message therapy diploma in detail. Let&rsquo;s go through the top 07 reasons why you should pursue this qualification.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">What is an HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://nta.nsw.edu.au/public/blogImages/Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia\" alt=\"Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia\" width=\"729\" height=\"472\" />&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">The </span><a href=\"../diploma-in-remedial-massage\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage </span></strong></a><span data-contrast=\"none\">is a nationally recognized diploma qualification in Australia. It&rsquo;s an advanced course for massage therapists in the country. In this course, students learn about a wide range of topics, including: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Different types of massage treatments&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Monitor massage therapy </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Musculoskeletal assessments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Maintain safety and hygiene&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Legal and ethical aspects of the job&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">There are various Australian </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Recognised Training Organisations (RTOs)</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> that offer this qualification.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">07 Reasons to Pursue an HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage </span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Now that you know about the course content, let&rsquo;s go through the top 07 reasons to pursue an </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. You will get a clear idea of why enrolling in this course can have many benefits for your career.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">1. High Demand for Qualified Massage Therapists&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">The massage therapy industry in Australia is growing at a very fast rate. There is a shortage of skilled massage therapists in the country. Therefore, businesses will be more than happy to hire qualified workers with the right skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Getting a recognized diploma in massage therapy has the following benefits: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Apply for a massage therapist position in a spa or salon&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Have an advantage over non-qualified therapists&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You have the opportunity to enter different types of businesses&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">2. Your Skills Are Recognised&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Getting an </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia </span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">will nationally recognise your massage therapy skills. Many businesses require candidates to have a recognized qualification. Therefore, you should consider this diploma if you are a massage enthusiast.&nbsp; </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Let&rsquo;s take a look at some of the pros of having recognized skills: </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will have more options when it comes to job openings&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will create more trust and reliability among your clients&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will be a recognized practitioner in the sector </span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">3. Better Knowledge and Expertise&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">In this diploma course, you will be taught about a wide range of topics related to business. Institutions usually partner with reputed businesses to deliver this course. As a result, you will get practical experience in applying your massage therapy skills. So your technical knowledge in massage therapy will greatly improve.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the core topics in the </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage </span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">are:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Different techniques of massage therapy&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Remedial massage treatments&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Assess the client&rsquo;s musculoskeletal condition&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">4. An Interesting Career&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">A career in massage therapy can be a very interesting one. You will get exposure to different types of businesses. You will closely work with your client to understand their massage needs. Making your clients feel comfortable and relieved can be a very rewarding experience.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Some of the reasons why the job outcomes of this diploma can be very interesting:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will have the option to join a spa, salon, or resort&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will meet professionals and clients from various backgrounds&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"5\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You have to develop solutions to the issues of different clients&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">5. More Career Opportunities&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will certainly have more career opportunities with this diploma. Your overall value will increase since this is an advanced qualification in massage therapy. As mentioned before, you will greatly develop your expertise in this diploma course. Therefore, we highly recommend this diploma for building a career in this industry.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">This diploma will develop your career in the following ways:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will have better job offers&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can get more job benefits, like a pay raise&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"6\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You may also get quick promotions based on your performance&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">6. Better Industry Connections&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">The </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> can be a great path to develop your industry connections. Having good industry connections is very important for progressing your career. A therapist with strong connections will certainly have an advantage over others in the field.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Let&rsquo;s look at some of the positive impacts of having industry connections:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will have new business opportunities&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It is good for personal branding&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"7\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can learn from more experienced practitioners&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">7. You Can Open Your Own Business&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Want to open your own spa or salon? Then we highly suggest getting this diploma. The </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> will teach you the art and the different aspects of the business. Therefore, you can consider getting this qualification for opening a massage therapy business.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">This diploma will help you in your dream of opening a new business in the following ways:&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You will learn about the basics of running a business successfully&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">You can develop impactful strategies for your business&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Create strong plans to have a good position in the competition&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 aria-level=\"1\"><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Conclusion&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">We hope that you now understand the benefits of having an </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">. This is a great qualification to take your massage therapy career to new heights.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Remember to choose a recognised organisation like a </span><strong><span data-contrast=\"none\">Recognised Training Organisation (RTO)</span></strong><span data-contrast=\"none\"> to enrol in this course. Work hard with passion and you will achieve your career goals in no time! Best of luck!</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'diploma of remedial massage in Australia', 'diploma of remedial massage in Australia', 'Let\'s take a look at the HLT52015 - Diploma of Remedial Massage in Australia. Know the 07 reasons why this qualification is great for massage therapists.', 'reasons-to-pursue-a-hlt52015-diploma-of-remedial-massage-in-australia.jpg', NULL, '2022-10-24 09:11:11', '2022-10-26 06:10:27');

